# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:15
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_21a82833:

    # "My alarm's beeping shatters the early morning quiet, and I find myself wondering where to find the motivation to rise."
    "目覚ましがピーッと鳴って早朝の静寂を破る。起きるためのモチベーションをどこから引き出すべきかと悩んでいる自分がいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:20
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_3ec95011:

    # "Class is still quite far off, but I agreed to run with Emi in the mornings."
    "授業にはまだかなり早いけど、笑美と一緒に朝練をする約束をしていたんだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:22
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_594405c7:

    # "Really, I'm not that interested in running as a hobby, or even as a possible life-lengthening exercise."
    "実を言うと、趣味としてのランニングにはあまり興味がない。それどころか、俺の延命のためのトレーニングとしてさえも。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:24
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_fe6629f4:

    # "However, I feel obligated to follow through on my promise to Emi yesterday, which is why I find myself throwing on some running shorts and a light tee-shirt."
    "でも、昨日の笑美との約束を守る義務があると思って、気づいたらランニング用の短パンと軽いＴシャツに着替えていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:29
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_483cec6e:

    # "The cool morning air caresses my face as the morning sunshine causes the dew on the grass to sparkle, nearly blinding me at first."
    "冷たい朝の空気が俺の顔を撫で、朝日の光が芝生の上の露にきらめいて、目がくらみそうになる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:31
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_5e2ba028:

    # "As I make my way down to the track, an ugly thought strikes me."
    "競技場へ足を運んでいる間、ふと醜い考えが俺の心の中をかすめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:33
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_3f7a60d1:

    # "What if this is some sort of joke that Emi's playing on me?"
    "もしこれが、笑美が俺をからかって言った冗談か何かだったらどうしようか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:35
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_ab3db926:

    # "Would that surprise me, really?"
    "いかにもありそうだよなあ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:37
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_fcdab8a7:

    # "Hell, I'd probably do it to the new guy, too."
    "ちくしょう、俺だって新入り相手なら同じことをするに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:39
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_6204dbfa:

    # "At the very least, I'm sure Emi and Rin made a bet on whether or not I'd actually show up."
    "少なくとも、笑美と琳は、俺が実際に現れるかどうか賭けをしているに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:44
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_4320967d:

    # "I feel a sense of trepidation as the track comes into view."
    "陸上競技のトラックが見えてきて、俺は恐ろしくなってくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:51
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d198e095:

    # emi "You're late!"
    emi "遅ーい！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:53
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_c07d115e:

    # "It would seem that Emi is already there. What a relief."
    "笑美はもう来ていたみたいだ。安心したよ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:55
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_37d890cc:

    # hi "Not according to my watch. We both are early, in fact."
    hi "時計狂ってるんじゃないのか。むしろ俺たち二人とも早く来たんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:60
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_5555e842:

    # emi "Damn. You've got me there."
    emi "ちぇっ。ばれちゃったか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:62
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_c5397b9a:

    # "Emi is sitting on the bleachers, decked out in her running gear, waiting somewhat patiently for me."
    "笑美はランニング用の義足を付けて、幾分根気よく俺を待ちながら観覧席に座っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:64
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_4dd68929:

    # hi "I'm glad you're actually here. I was afraid that this was a joke or something."
    hi "俺、笑美がここにいるのがマジで嬉しくてさ。冗談か何かだったんじゃないかと心配だったよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:69
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d2f11d33:

    # emi "Nah, I'd never make someone get up early for nothing."
    emi "ううん、あたしは意味もなく誰かを早起きさせたりしないもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:74
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_ff9109d9:

    # emi "Plus, Rin owes me 500 yen now. She didn't think you'd actually show up."
    emi "それに、琳には５００円の貸しができたからね。琳、久夫くんがここに来るって思ってなかったもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:76
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a7317081:

    # "I knew it!"
    "やっぱりな！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:78
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_e6b902c2:

    # "Nice to know Emi was on my side, at least."
    "まあ、少なくとも、笑美が俺を信用する側に賭けてくれたのはうれしい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:83
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_b6578c6f:

    # "Emi hops off of the bleachers and begins stretching out."
    "笑美は観客席から飛び降りて、ストレッチ運動を始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:90
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_de173781:

    # "She's remarkably lithe, almost like a dancer."
    "笑美は本当にしなやかで、まるでダンサーみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:92
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_421da9c2:

    # "I set out to stretch as well, but then realize that I don't exactly remember how to stretch properly."
    "俺も同じようにストレッチをしようとするけど、きちんとしたストレッチ運動の方法を覚えてないことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:94
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_90e64c2b:

    # "It's been ages since I stretched for anything, if you don't count my one stint at running last week."
    "先週のランニングのときをのぞけば、もうずいぶん長い間ストレッチなんてやったことがない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:96
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d14c1cbe:

    # "And even then, I don't think I actually stretched beforehand."
    "それにそのランニングのときだって、事前にストレッチなんてしなかったと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:98
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a2d7351a:

    # "The specter of my long hospital stay rises up again."
    "入院時代の悪夢がまた脳裏に甦ってくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:100
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_42ee91e3:

    # "I can't say I was all that active before the hospital stay, though, so maybe I'm just being morose."
    "もっとも、入院する前は活動的だったとも言えないし、単に俺自身が落ち込んでいるだけなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:105
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_678645dd:

    # "Emi giggles as she watches me stretch out."
    "笑美は、俺が体を伸ばすのを見てクスクス笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:110
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_287edf84:

    # emi "No no no Hisao, you've got to hold it for longer than that!"
    emi "そうじゃないよ久夫くん、もっと長く伸ばしてなきゃだめだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:112
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_4c1e8f9b:

    # hi "I'm trying! It kinda hurts a little."
    hi "やろうとしてるって！　ちょっと痛くてさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:117
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_35818951:

    # emi "Ha! That's because you're out of shape. You've got to get some flexibility in you, like this."
    emi "あはは、体がなまってるから痛むんだよ。もっと体を柔軟にしなきゃ、ほらこんな風に"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:122
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_9f92aaf8:

    # "To demonstrate, Emi reaches down and puts her head through her legs."
    "お手本を見せつけるかのように笑美は手を伸ばして前屈し、頭を足の間に通す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:124
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_5a7b7721:

    # "God bless you, Emi."
    "おいおいマジかよ笑美。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:126
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_583b5b8f:

    # hi "I see. Is that the sort of thing I should strive for?"
    hi "なるほど。俺もそのくらいできるように努力すべきってことか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:131
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d45ddbea:

    # emi "Of course! Flexibility is important for any runner. You'll be able to go faster the more you stretch out."
    emi "もちろん！　柔軟さはランナーにとってすごく重要なんだよ。ストレッチすればするほど、早く走れるようになるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:133
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_ca16796e:

    # "That makes no sense to me, but Emi seems to believe it's true."
    "俺にはさっぱり理解できないけど、笑美はそう信じているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:135
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_45fee0f2:

    # "With Emi's help, I manage to stretch myself out properly."
    "笑美の助けで、なんとかストレッチが形になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:140
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_b4082adc:

    # "I can't help but notice that when she thinks about how to explain things to me, her mouth scrunches up in concentration."
    "笑美が説明のしかたを考えるときに集中のあまり口をくしゃくしゃにするのが、つい目に入ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:142
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_acd4cf33:

    # "It's adorable."
    "なんて可愛いんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:147
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_6ab9a403:

    # emi "Not bad, Hisao. Come on, we'd better start running."
    emi "悪くないよ、久夫くん。行こ、そろそろランニング始めないと"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:152
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_9242d86a:

    # emi "We'll start off with just a mile, okay?"
    emi "じゃあ軽く１６００からいくよ。いい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:157
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7d892481:

    # emi "That's four laps around the track, got it?"
    emi "トラックを４周だよ、わかった？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:159
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_c49d4f68:

    # hi "That sounds fine to me."
    hi "それでいいぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:166
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a3c2cba2:

    # "This shouldn't be too hard, right?"
    "そんなにきついってことはない、よな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:171
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_241fb54b:

    # "A hazy memory of running a mile for gym class surfaces in my mind."
    "体育の授業で４周走ったときの、ぼんやりとした記憶が頭に浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:173
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_06beb2d9:

    # "Yeah, it wasn't that bad."
    "そうだよな、そんなに酷いもんじゃなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:184
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_5e41fe27:

    # "Emi sets a pretty good pace, and I fall in behind her."
    "笑美はかなり速いペースを保って走り、俺はその後ろを付いていく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:194
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_aa29d2ce:

    # emi "Try to keep up, okay Hisao?"
    emi "がんばってついてきてね。いい？　久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:196
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_475aca2e:

    # hi "Roger."
    hi "了解"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:205
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_f6b3ec53:

    # "We round the first curve without incident, though I can already feel my heart rate increasing slightly."
    "俺たちは無事に最初のコーナーを回るけど、早くも自分の心拍数が少しずつ上がってきているのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:207
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_3b992da6:

    # "By the second curve, I've started to breathe through my mouth."
    "２つ目のコーナーにさしかかった時には、もう口で息をし始めていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:209
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_74a67ca5:

    # "Emi doesn't even seem to be breaking a sweat."
    "笑美は汗の一滴すらかいてるようには見えない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:211
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_b2c0364a:

    # "As if to punctuate her superiority, she turns around and starts running backwards."
    "自分の優位を見せびらかすように、笑美は振り返って後ろ向きに走り始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:218
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_ee563799:

    # emi "Are you doing okay, Hisao?"
    emi "今のところは順調？　久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:220
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_8a78c4e7:

    # hi "Never… better."
    hi "ぜっこー……ちょー……だ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:225
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_40dc2964:

    # emi "Oh really? Maybe I should speed up then, hmm?"
    emi "本当？　じゃあもっとスピードあげちゃおうかな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:227
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_23b17eca:

    # hi "Oh… no, …wouldn't want you…"
    hi "ああ……いや……おまえに……むちゃを……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:229
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d1f5d9c4:

    # hi "…to… overex…ert yourself."
    hi "……してほしく……ないから……やめて……おこう……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:231
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_ba143103:

    # "My heavy panting and wheezing makes the statement less convincing than I had hoped. Emi simply smiles and turns around again."
    "ぜえはあと荒い息のせいで、言葉に込めたかった説得力も薄れる。笑美はただにこっと笑って、また正面を向く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:236
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_731ab6b5:

    # emi "You're the boss, Hisao. We'll stay at this pace."
    emi "じゃあ久夫くんの言うとおりにしようかな。このペースを続けるね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:245
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_b1675a0a:

    # "I get the feeling that I'm being mocked."
    "なんとなく馬鹿にされているような気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:247
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_49ed3f0d:

    # "If I weren't in such terrible shape, I'd probably feel offended."
    "もしこんな体たらくじゃなければ、たぶん腹を立てていただろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:249
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_fdb200c3:

    # "By the third lap, my breath is coming in ragged gasps."
    "３周目には、もう息も絶え絶えになっていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:251
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_9c0e15d5:

    # "I'm also awash in my own sweat. Gross."
    "体も汗でびっしょりだ。気持ち悪い。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:253
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_f25d15c3:

    # "We round the curve to start our fourth lap, and Emi looks back at me with a grin."
    "俺たちがコーナーを回り４周目に突入すると、笑美は振り返ってにやりと笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:263
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_4269ca92:

    # emi "Here we go!"
    emi "行くよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:274
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_f7e7b32a:

    # "She takes off at blinding speed while I stubbornly stick to my slower pace."
    "俺が頑なに遅いペースで留まる間に、笑美は目もくらむような速さで走り去っていく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:276
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7c1ae27f:

    # "By the time I get to the first turn, she's already rounding the second."
    "俺が最初のコーナーを回り始めるころには、笑美はもう２つ目に入っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:278
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_ed0cee80:

    # "As I struggle across the back stretch, Emi continues running and catches up to me."
    "俺がバックストレッチを抜けるのに苦労していると、ペースそのままの笑美が追いつく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:290
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_e1bc1806:

    # emi "Come on, Hisao! You can do it!"
    emi "久夫くん、しっかり！　久夫くんならできるよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:299
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_0c9f33ca:

    # "I'd answer her, but I'm too focused on getting air into my lungs and ignoring the burning in my leg muscles."
    "返事をしようにも、息を吸うのと足の筋肉が燃えそうなのを無視するのとでそれどころじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:301
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_f064afaf:

    # "Part of me wants to say something like 'Maybe {b}you{/b} can, but I'm about to die here.'"
    "『{b}お前{/b}はできるかもしれないけど、こっちは今にも死にそうなんだよ』みたいなことを、心の一部が言いたがっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:303
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a7a08043:

    # "But again, I doubt I can actually form words right now."
    "といっても、今の俺が実際にそれを言葉として発声できるかどうか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:305
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_dda8a66c:

    # "Emi keeps pace with me as I round the second turn and cross the finish line."
    "笑美は第２コーナーを回ってゴールラインを踏むまで、俺とペースを合わせてくれる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:317
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_2a941404:

    # "Her sprint seems to have gotten her sweating."
    "笑美は全力疾走で汗ばんだみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:319
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_e9e42e5c:

    # "It's actually caused her shirt to turn slightly translucent. It seems she wears a black sports bra."
    "実際そのおかげで笑美のシャツが少し透けている。黒いスポーツブラを着けているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:321
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_0ad1f566:

    # "I feel a vague stab of guilt for being the sort of guy who stares at a girl's chest, but my legs and chest are burning so badly I can't bring myself to care that much."
    "自分が女の子の胸を見つめるような奴だったことに漠然と罪悪感を覚えるけど、俺の足と胸はそれを気にしていられないほどひどく熱くなっていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:326
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_e4230a0e:

    # emi "Not bad for a first effort, Hisao."
    emi "初めてにしては悪くなかったよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:330
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_2602d027:

    # hi "Ki— …kind of you… to say… so."
    hi "そりゃ……どうも……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:332
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_2bf2734c:

    # "Emi seems to be, if not out of breath, at least breathing a little more heavily than she was before we started running."
    "笑美は、息を切らせてとは言わないまでも、少なくとも俺たちが走り始める前よりはちょっと息が荒いみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:334
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7d0abb7f:

    # "It must have been the sprint that did it."
    "間違いなくあの全力疾走のせいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:339
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_93ff6411:

    # emi "Hey, I've got to get a few sprints in. You should walk around the track to cool down."
    emi "ねえ、あたしもう少し全力で走んなきゃいけないんだ。トラックの周りを歩いてクールダウンした方がいいよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:341
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_f7f5c16c:

    # emi "Then we can stretch out, and we'll be all done, okay?"
    emi "その後ストレッチして、今日はおしまい。いい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:343
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_2fba0c0a:

    # hi "Sounds great."
    hi "そうだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:345
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_1e8987af:

    # "My legs are on fire, and my breathing is still heavy, but surprisingly my heart seems to be taking the strain well."
    "足は火が付いたようだし、まだ息も上がったままだけど、驚いたことに心臓の方はこれまでの負担にも持ちこたえているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:347
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7c5b4b2c:

    # "Another triumph of medical science, I suppose."
    "ここでも医学の勝利、かな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:352
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_c4d7abb1:

    # emi "You should put your hands behind your head. It makes it easier to catch your breath."
    emi "頭の後ろに手を置いて。そしたらもっと呼吸がしやすくなるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:363
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_2b48142f:

    # "Surprisingly, she's right. I begin to stroll around the track, happy to feel my breath coming back to me."
    "驚いたことに、笑美の言うとおりだ。呼吸がまた落ち着いてくるのはうれしく、俺はゆっくり歩いてトラックを回り始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:377
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_99c9b315:

    # "There's a blur as Emi sprints by me."
    "目にも止まらない速さで、笑美が俺の横を走り抜ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:379
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7ab57c57:

    # "Watching her run is absolutely fascinating."
    "笑美の走りにはまったく惚れぼれする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:381
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_1ec3e2d4:

    # "It's not just because she's on prosthetics, though that is interesting."
    "義足をつけているのも興味深いけど、それだけじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:388
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_5cc3f529:

    # "The really interesting thing is the way her face changes."
    "本当に興味深いのは、その表情の変わりっぷりだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:390
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_018b49e7:

    # "I can only catch glimpses of it as she runs by, but her eyes seem to come alive with a sort of fierce joy."
    "俺の横を走り抜ける一瞬の間しか見ることはできないけど、笑美の目はなんだか荒々しいまでの喜びで生き生きとして見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:392
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_29c26b7d:

    # "It's as if there's nothing else in the world but her and the track."
    "まるで、この世界に笑美とトラックしか存在しないかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:401
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7469cb79:

    # "By the time I've gotten to the final stretch, Emi seems to have finished her sprinting."
    "俺が最後の直線コースにさしかかったころには、笑美は全力疾走を終えていたようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:403
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_f3fa0552:

    # "She's breathing heavily now, but she's wearing a satisfied grin on her face. She waves to me cheerily as I near her."
    "今は笑美も激しく息をしているけど、満足げな笑顔を浮かべている。俺が近づくと、笑美は嬉しそうに手を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:408
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7728289a:

    # emi "Feeling better, right?"
    emi "気分、よくなったでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:410
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_3f3c5d2a:

    # hi "Actually, yeah."
    hi "ああ、ましになったよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:415
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_68cd6140:

    # emi "D'you want to take another lap around with me? I've got to cool down too, you know."
    emi "あたしともう一周歩かない？　あたしもクールダウンしなくちゃなんないしさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:417
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d04a9ce4:

    # "Part of me would rather sit down, and not move, but something tells me that would be a bad idea."
    "むしろ座り込んでじっとしていたいと思う部分はあるけど、多分そうしないほうがいいんだろうと感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:419
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_1159e43e:

    # "Besides, if I sit down, there may be no getting back up again."
    "それに、もし座ってしまったら、もう二度と立ち上がれないかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:421
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_8bce8989:

    # hi "Sure, why not?"
    hi "わかった、そうしようか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:423
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_b6fb0dea:

    # "Emi's got her hands behind her head now as well, which makes her seem very relaxed."
    "笑美は俺と同じように手を頭の後ろに回し、とてもリラックスしているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:425
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_2f23bafe:

    # "The positioning of her arms also pulls her shirt upwards ever-so-slightly so that I can see a small strip of her belly."
    "腕を上げているせいでシャツも上にほんの少しだけ引っぱられて、笑美のお腹の肌がちらっと見えてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:427
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_0c84fbdb:

    # "I do my best to act the gentleman and not look, but the contrast of her skin against her red running shorts is rather arresting."
    "俺は全力で紳士的になってそれを見ないようにするけど、笑美の素肌と赤いブルマのコントラストはむしろとても印象的だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:432
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_14ee9e36:

    # emi "So how do you feel, Hisao?"
    emi "で、調子はどう？　久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:434
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_88e0c47e:

    # hi "Surprisingly good, actually. I'm sore and tired, but… surprisingly good."
    hi "すごくいい、ほんとに。体は痛いし疲れたけど……でもすごくいい"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:436
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7f0eb8a3:

    # "As soon as I say it, I realize that it's true."
    "俺はそう言うとすぐに、それが本当であることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:438
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_62f7c95d:

    # "Sure, part of me wants to lay down and die, but I feel like I've accomplished something."
    "もちろん俺の心の中にはすぐにでも寝転がって動きたくないという部分もあるけど、何かを達成したという満足感もある。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:440
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_4c7bc358:

    # "It's almost like a glow throughout my body that persists despite the soreness."
    "体の痛みにもかかわらず、満悦感に似た感覚が体中を駆け巡り続けているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:445
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a9ffb58f:

    # emi "Yeah, that's the runner's high."
    emi "そう、ランナーズ・ハイってやつね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:447
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_90c06fef:

    # hi "Runner's high?"
    hi "ランナーズ・ハイ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:452
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_04c79d5b:

    # emi "Yeah, it has something to do with… adrenaline?"
    emi "うん、確か……アドレナリンが関係してるんだっけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:454
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a062f3d0:

    # "Emi thinks for a moment as we walk, trying to remember."
    "一緒に歩きながら、笑美は思い出そうとしてちょっと考え込む。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:459
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_df0aad5a:

    # "Then she shrugs and grins at me."
    "それから笑美は肩をすくめて、俺に微笑む。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:464
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_3e5f464d:

    # emi "I don't actually remember. It's a good feeling though, isn't it?"
    emi "あは、思い出せないや。でも、それ気持ちいい感じだよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:472
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_12c594b2:

    # emi "Better than sex, right?"
    emi "エッチより気持ちいい、でしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:474
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_c449a224:

    # "I open my mouth to respond shortly before processing what she's just said."
    "俺は彼女が何を言ったのか理解する前に、返事をしようと口をあける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:476
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_35c4f685:

    # hi "…"
    hi "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:478
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a11d8922:

    # "Emi watches my face for a few moments before bursting into laughter."
    "笑美は少しの間俺の顔を見つめ、突然笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:485
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_771ee69f:

    # emi "Sorry, sorry! I couldn't resist! You're just too easy!"
    emi "ごめん、ごめんね！　あたし我慢できなかったの！　久夫くんが単純すぎて！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:487
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_70c6bd92:

    # hi "Why did I agree to run with you again?"
    hi "お前とまた走るなんて約束しなければよかったよ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:489
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d0a47d93:

    # "Emi just laughs harder. She takes a hold of my forearm and tilts it, allowing her to get a better view of my watch. Her face changes the moment she sees the time."
    "笑美はますます大きく笑う。俺の腕をつかんで傾け、腕時計がよく見えるようにする。そして時間を確認するなり笑美の顔色が変わる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:494
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_367b08ea:

    # emi "Oh no! We'd better get a move on, Hisao!"
    emi "あーっ！　もう行かなくちゃ、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:499
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_e3e60f60:

    # emi "Class is in an hour, and I need to shower!"
    emi "あと一時間で授業が始まっちゃう、シャワーも浴びなきゃ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:501
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_0fbc5506:

    # hi "I should probably do that as well…"
    hi "俺もそうしなきゃいけないんだけどな……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:506
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_95b3e36d:

    # emi "I need to see the nurse, too… maybe he'll write me a note for being late!"
    emi "ナースくんのところにも行かなきゃいけないし……もしかしたら、遅刻証明を書いてくれるかも！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:508
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_a7df11f7:

    # hi "Why do you need to see the nurse?"
    hi "なんでナースに会わなきゃなんないんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:513
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_9fdfbb49:

    # "Emi points to her prosthetics, as if that would explain everything."
    "笑美は、それで全て説明がつく、とでも言いたげに自分の義足を指さす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:518
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_3a925596:

    # emi "It's important to check for irritation."
    emi "炎症を起こしてないかチェックするのって大切なんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:520
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_fca6cde7:

    # emi "You know, from sweat or friction, or anything."
    emi "ほら、汗とか摩擦とかそんなので起こったりするからさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:525
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_dcb958de:

    # emi "Normally I only go after practice, but if we're going to be doing these morning runs then I guess I'll see him twice a day."
    emi "いつもは練習の後だけ行けばいいんだけど、もしあたしたちが朝練続けるんなら、一日に二回行くことになるかなあ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:527
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_5d4c2b10:

    # "Wait, so Emi has only started doing these runs since I showed up?"
    "待てよ、ってことは笑美は俺が来るようになってからこの朝練を始めたのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:529
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_324304bb:

    # hi "If it's more convenient for you to run with me at a later time…"
    hi "もし午後の練習で一緒に走る方が笑美にとって楽なら……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:534
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_34400a3d:

    # emi "Don't be silly! I've been meaning to start running in the morning for a while now."
    emi "バカなこと言わないでよ！　あたし、しばらく前から朝に走ろうと思ってたの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:536
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_9df154a5:

    # emi "But if I didn't have a partner to run with, I'd be less likely to keep up a routine."
    emi "でもあたし一緒に走る相手がいないと、そういうの続きそうにないしさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:541
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_b46ce083:

    # emi "It's always harder to blow off a commitment if you're going to let someone else down, you know?"
    emi "誰かをがっかりさせちゃうって思うと約束を破る気にはなりにくいものでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:546
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_3569a63b:

    # emi "So you'll be my running partner for the mornings!"
    emi "だから久夫くんは、あたしの朝のランニングパートナーになるんだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:551
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_1938da8f:

    # emi "We both need the exercise, so it all works out, don't you think?"
    emi "二人とも運動が必要なんだし、それなら一挙両得、って思わない？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:553
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_67928a08:

    # hi "Yeah, perfect."
    hi "ああ、完璧だな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:555
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_aa2f1fb3:

    # "Did it have to be me, though?"
    "でも、それって俺じゃなきゃいけなかったのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:557
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_dd3bcfa0:

    # "Well, I guess I can't complain too much. Emi's pretty fun to hang out with."
    "まあ、それほど文句は言えないな。笑美と一緒にいるとすごく楽しいし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:559
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_03d5148a:

    # "And she's right. I do need the exercise. Doctor's orders, even."
    "それに笑美は正しい。俺は運動しなきゃいけない。医者からも指示されてるしな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:564
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_4447b2a0:

    # "Emi waves a quick goodbye to me."
    "笑美は俺にさっと手を振って別れを告げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:566
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_abf27027:

    # emi "Right, I'm off! Come have lunch with us, okay?"
    emi "うん、じゃ行くね！　お昼一緒に食べよう、いい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:568
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "なんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:573
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_e8a4d80f:

    # emi "Lunch! You know, the meal? In the middle of the day? Come have it with us!"
    emi "ごはん！　ほら、食事だよ？　お昼の？　一緒に食べようよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:575
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_804bb8e8:

    # hi "Where?"
    hi "どこで？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:580
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_d58d26b2:

    # emi "The rooftop. Rin likes it up there."
    emi "屋上。琳がそこ好きなの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:582
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_af4d2208:

    # hi "When?"
    hi "いつ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:587
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_086b7aa2:

    # emi "Lunchtime, when else? That was a silly question."
    emi "お昼休み以外にいつ食べるっていうの？　変なこと聞くね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:589
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_c10acad7:

    # hi "Yeah, but I sort of felt the need to ask all three for completeness' sake."
    hi "ああ、でも完璧を期するには３つ全部聞いといたほうがいいと思って"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:594
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_93c4979f:

    # "Emi laughs and grins. I don't think I've ever seen a girl smile so much before."
    "笑美は声を上げて笑い、にっこりする。こんなにいっぱい笑う女の子は見たことがない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:599
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_9051983b:

    # emi "Not bad, Hisao. See ya!"
    emi "悪くないよ、久夫くん、またね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:611
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_308be61b:

    # "With that, she takes off like a shot for the school building."
    "そう言いながら、笑美は校舎の方に弾丸のようにすっ飛んでいく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:613
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_7a74aa51:

    # "I guess she's going to see the nurse first."
    "まずナースに会いに行くんだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:618
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_2bed7b1d:

    # "I hurry back to my room and hop in the shower, only to find that the water takes a while to heat up."
    "俺は急いで部屋に戻ってシャワーに飛びつくけど、水が温まるのには時間がかかることがわかるだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:623
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_342c12bc:

    # "The shock of the cold water nearly kills me."
    "冷水のショックで俺は死にそうになる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:628
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_34a08a21:

    # "I manage to warm the water a bit and spend some quality time feeling my muscles loosen."
    "なんとか水が温まるのを待ち、筋肉がほぐれるのを感じながら至福の時を過ごす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:630
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_9c771fb5:

    # "My heart, surprisingly, feels the least bothered by the run."
    "俺の心臓はあのランニングの後でもほとんど問題ない感じだ。驚いた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:632
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_bc17ae0c:

    # "I suppose that's a good thing, even if it does make me feel like a bit of a wuss."
    "たぶん、それはいいことなんだろう。自分がちょっと弱虫みたいな気分になるにしても。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:634
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_c2ae5904:

    # "I mean at least I'd have an excuse beyond 'I am out of shape' if my heart were bothering me."
    "心臓がおかしければ、少なくとも単に『体がなまってる』よりは立派な言い訳ができるんだし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:636
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_946cdfd3:

    # "Guess I'll have to keep this running thing up, otherwise I'm sure Emi won't let me hear the end of it."
    "この朝練は続けなくちゃならないんだろうな、でなきゃ笑美にいつまでも文句を言われる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:638
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_68fadd13:

    # "It's only after I get out and dry myself off that I realize that I've only ten minutes left to put my clothes on and get to class."
    "服を着て授業に行くまでにあと１０分しか残っていないと気づいたのは、シャワーから出て体をふいた後だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:640
translate jp a2_emi_morning_run_61fae46f:

    # "Crap."
    "くそ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:656
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5c4883df:

    # "The hands on the clock finally set me free from the tedium of yet another fun-filled class."
    "時計の針はようやく、楽しいたのしい授業の退屈さから今回も俺を自由にしてくれる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:658
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_08a359a8:

    # "Getting up from my seat proves to be more of a problem than I anticipated."
    "自分の席から立ち上がるだけのことが、思ったより大問題だとわかる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:660
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_396a8c92:

    # "My legs are killing me from the morning's run."
    "朝練から足が痛くてしょうがない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:662
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a7d006f9:

    # "Maybe doing these with Emi isn't such a hot idea after all."
    "結局、笑美との朝練はあまりいいアイディアではなかったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:664
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4bcb1d82:

    # "Still, the run's given me a hell of an appetite."
    "それでも、朝練のせいで腹だけはやたらと減っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:672
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_75e4d9e1:

    # "I'm halfway down the hallway to the cafeteria when I remember that I've got my lunch with me."
    "食堂への廊下の途中で、俺は弁当を持ってきていたことを思い出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:674
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c03d6341:

    # "My parents saw fit to provide me with some prepackaged stuff when I moved in, and a good thing too."
    "こっちに越してくる時に、うちの親がいくつか出来合いの食品を持たせてくれていた。ありがたいことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:676
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_21262c67:

    # "The hallway is packed with students headed for the cafeteria."
    "廊下は、食堂に向かう学生でごった返している。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:678
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_dcaec1c2:

    # "Going back is like swimming upstream - but I've got an appointment to keep on the rooftop."
    "ここを引き返すのは流れに逆らって泳ぐようなものだ――けど、俺には屋上に行く約束がある。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:685
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_892e4ffc:

    # "It takes me a moment to find the staircase leading up to the rooftop, but I'm willing to bet that Emi and Rin aren't up there by now anyway."
    "屋上への階段を探すのに時間がかかるけど、どうせまだ笑美と琳は屋上に行ってないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:687
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ad164af0:

    # "In fact, I think I saw Emi among the bodies in the hallway headed for the cafeteria."
    "事実、廊下の人ごみの中で笑美が食堂に向かってたのを見たと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:696
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0e22f9a4:

    # "I step out of the door to the roof and take a deep breath."
    "俺はドアから屋上に出て深呼吸する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:698
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d6366ef2:

    # "The fresh air blowing against my face and body almost makes my legs hurt less."
    "新鮮な風が顔や体に吹いてきて、足の痛みも和らぐようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:703
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_f35d1b51:

    # rin "Maybe if I'm upside down…"
    rin "さかさまになれば……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:708
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c6c0a8ae:

    # "Part of me wants to be surprised that Rin's already up here."
    "琳がもう上がってきていたことに、心のどこかで驚いている自分がいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:710
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c7ccc17e:

    # hi "What's that going to accomplish?"
    hi "さかさまだったら何ができるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:715
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c67019a2:

    # rin "Things in the clouds."
    rin "夢みたいないろんなこと"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:717
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_85907979:

    # hi "Couldn't you just… look at them right-side up?"
    hi "それって……普通に上向きじゃだめなのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:722
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5a5fda0c:

    # "Rin rolls her eyes in something approaching exasperation."
    "琳は激怒に近い雰囲気であきれ顔をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:724
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_95139877:

    # rin "Then I wouldn't get a new perspective."
    rin "それじゃ、あたらしい物の見方を得られないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:726
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a776cc82:

    # hi "Is upside down really a new perspective?"
    hi "さかさまってほんとにあたらしい物の見方なのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:731
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_53969c63:

    # "Ah ha! That caught her off guard. Rin looks pensive."
    "おっ！　今の質問は琳の不意を突いたみたいだ。琳は考えこんでいるように見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:733
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_08096063:

    # rin "You may have a point. Maybe sideways."
    rin "一理あるかもしれないね。横でもいいのかも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:738
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a869e95e:

    # "As Rin lays down on the bench to look at the sky, I give up."
    "琳が空を見ようとベンチの上に横たわったので、俺は諦める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:746
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_567b47cc:

    # "Fortunately Emi chooses that moment to burst through the door carrying two bags."
    "ちょうど運よく、笑美が袋を２つ抱えてドアから飛び出してくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:748
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3017a2b9:

    # "She nearly takes the door off the hinges."
    "もう少しでドアを外しそうな勢いだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:753
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a3ba992e:

    # emi "Sorry it took me so long! There were a ton of people in line."
    emi "ほんと遅くなってごめんね！　列にすごいたくさん人がいたの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:762
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3e4cb8f1:

    # "She drops the first bag in front of Rin and takes a seat on the bench next to her."
    "笑美は琳の前に袋をひとつ置いて、隣に腰掛ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:764
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_e551a58a:

    # hi "You buy Rin's lunch for her?"
    hi "いつも琳の昼飯を買いに行ってやるのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:769
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9d9f6eed:

    # emi "Sometimes, yeah. I'd have Rin buy my lunch for me in return, but I'm not sure how she'd carry it."
    emi "ときどき、ね。お返しに琳にも行ってもらってもいいんだけど、どうやって持ってくるのかわかんないし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:774
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_aea6058a:

    # rin "Plus I'd never buy her lunch."
    rin "それに、私は笑美の分は絶対買わないし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:776
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d1bbe7cf:

    # "If Rin's offended by Emi's comment, she doesn't show it. Emi sniffs."
    "琳は笑美の言葉に怒ってるのかもしれないけど、表情には出していない。笑美は鼻であしらって言う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:781
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_933f9843:

    # emi "How ungrateful of you."
    emi "ほんと恩知らずよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:783
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3b0be867:

    # "I'm not sure whether the two are joking with one another or if I'm witnessing the beginnings of a cat fight."
    "二人は冗談を言い合ってるのか、それとも俺はキャットファイトの始まりを目の当たりにしてるのか、俺にはよくわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:789
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_436e9532:

    # "The two girls stare at one another for a few tense moments before breaking into smiles."
    "二人が見つめ合って少しのあいだ緊張が走るけど、急に微笑みに変わる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:794
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_acf1c20e:

    # rin "Hey Emi, do you think being upside down is a new perspective on things?"
    rin "ねえ笑美、さかさまになるのはあたらしい物の見方だと思う？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:796
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_7260bda9:

    # "Didn't I already have this conversation?"
    "この話ってもうしなかったっけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:801
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d81c767d:

    # "Emi looks thoughtful, apparently giving the question some thought."
    "笑美は考え込んでるように見える。どうも答えを考えているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:803
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_dbb12f5c:

    # "After a deep and profound pause, she speaks."
    "深く重い沈黙の後、笑美は言う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:808
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d2e50e91:

    # emi "I have no idea."
    emi "わかんない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:810
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_28821c89:

    # "Well, at least she's as lost as I am."
    "やれやれ、笑美も俺と同じくらいには見当つかないか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:817
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_08aed08e:

    # emi "Hey Hisao, you're coming to the track meet, right?"
    emi "ねえ久夫くん、今度の陸上競技会に来てくれるよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:819
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cbd6abf5:

    # "The question comes out of the blue and catches me off guard."
    "いきなりの質問に不意を突かれる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:821
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_44d9c892:

    # hi "Um… I don't know yet?"
    hi "うーん……まだわかんないけど？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:827
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9e538550:

    # emi "Honestly, Hisao, after I went through all the trouble of letting you run with me in the morning, you won't even show up at my track meet?"
    emi "まったく、久夫くん、あたしは朝いっしょに走って久夫くんの面倒ぜーんぶ見てあげたのに、久夫くんはあたしの陸上競技会に来てもくれないんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:832
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_2fd656b3:

    # "Wasn't she the one that asked me to run with her?"
    "一緒に走ってって頼んできたのは笑美のほうじゃなかったっけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:834
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_07dc0a7b:

    # "Actually, she didn't even give me a choice in the matter."
    "実際、笑美は選択の余地なんてまったく与えてくれなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:836
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1a5371aa:

    # hi "Wait, no, I didn't say that…"
    hi "待った、違う、そんなことは言ってなくて……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:844
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9a9b2425:

    # "She beams at me as if I'd just agreed to give her a million dollars."
    "俺から１億円もらえることになったみたいに、ぱっと笑美の顔が晴れる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:849
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_154a1516:

    # emi "So you will come after all! That's great!"
    emi "じゃあやっぱ来るんだ！　やった！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:851
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_de4bd99c:

    # "I didn't say that either!"
    "そんなことも言ってない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:856
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0f3477f2:

    # rin "I'll be going too, so I'll make sure he comes, Emi."
    rin "笑美、私も行くから、久夫が必ず来るよう念押ししとく"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:862
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4379d478:

    # emi "Good idea, Rin! Maybe we can get some food or something after the meet's over?"
    emi "それいいね、琳！　終わったらご飯食べたりとかできるかも？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:864
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_e6a1235c:

    # "I feel like I've just been conned, but not by these two."
    "どうもハメられたような感じがする。でもこの二人にってわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:866
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_b6780cb5:

    # "More like by some outside force, pushing me irrevocably toward my destiny."
    "むしろ何か外部からの力が、後戻りのできない運命へと俺を押しやっているかのような。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:868
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4bc3ad5e:

    # "…Or maybe I shouldn't read books that feature conspiracy theories so heavily. Otherwise I might wind up sounding like Kenji."
    "……いや、陰謀論の特集本なんかを読みすぎるのはやめたほうがいいのかもな。でないと健二みたいなことを言い始めるはめになりそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:870
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_2c02e8c2:

    # "Still, I suppose that I've got to show up now."
    "それでも、競技会には行かなきゃいけないと思い始めている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:872
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0295fb78:

    # "I don't think that I could stand against both of them being disappointed."
    "笑美と琳の両方を失望させるなんて耐えられる気がしない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:874
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1057a31f:

    # "I'd never hear the end of it."
    "永遠に恨み節を聞かされ続けるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:876
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_427cd342:

    # hi "When is it again?"
    hi "競技会っていつだっけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:881
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_813457eb:

    # emi "Next week, silly! I just told you a few days ago."
    emi "もう、来週だよ！　あたし２、３日前に言ったはずだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:883
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c396cc9f:

    # hi "No you didn't."
    hi "言ってないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:888
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_95c917ad:

    # emi "I forgot? Well, you won't forget to come though, will you?"
    emi "あたし言い忘れた？　うーん、でも競技会には忘れずに来てくれるでしょ、ね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:890
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c70556d7:

    # hi "Of course I won't! I'll even make a note on a calendar or something!"
    hi "忘れないって！　カレンダーか何かにだって書いといてやるよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:895
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c6c911d1:

    # "Rin nods sagely."
    "琳はわけ知り顔でうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:900
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_f74c3152:

    # rin "That's probably a good idea, you know. Unless time changes its course."
    rin "それはたぶんいい考えだね。時間がその流れを変えない限りは"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:905
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_90bdb41a:

    # emi "It can do that?"
    emi "そんなことあるの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:910
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4cf85897:

    # "Rin gives a noncommittal shrug."
    "琳はあいまいに肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:915
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_af20b033:

    # rin "It hasn't yet, but you never know…"
    rin "まだ起きたことはないけど、実際はわからないよ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:920
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9a0aecd6:

    # "This time it's Emi who gives a shrug."
    "今度は肩をすくめたのは笑美のほうだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:925
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3670e31f:

    # emi "I suppose it can't be helped if it happens."
    emi "そんなことが起きたらどうしようもないよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:930
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_9d32ed2e:

    # rin "Not unless you're a time traveler or something."
    rin "タイムトラベラーかなにかでもなければね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:932
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4bb553f9:

    # hi "You don't actually think that could happen, do you?"
    hi "本気でそんなことがありうるなんて思ってないよな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:937
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_2d6cbe34:

    # emi "I don't think we do… do we?"
    emi "思ってない……よねえ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:942
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5a0cd67e:

    # "Rin shrugs again. That seems to be her default response to everything."
    "琳はまた肩をすくめる。こいつは何に対してもこういう反応をするみたいだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:947
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_5688ceba:

    # rin "I suppose not. But I reserve the right to change my opinion at a moment's notice."
    rin "思ってないよ。でも意見を一瞬で変える権利は留保してるからね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:949
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_35512302:

    # "For Rin, this statement makes a disturbing amount of sense."
    "琳にしては、不気味なくらい筋が通ったことを言う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:951
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a6da687c:

    # "The fact that I realize this now frightens me a bit."
    "それに気づいたことが少し恐い。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:953
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_3565aea4:

    # "I wonder if Emi gets this feeling all the time."
    "笑美はいつもこんな気分を味わってるのかな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:958
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cc5152be:

    # "If she does she's not showing it, though. Emi merely nods."
    "だとしても、笑美はそれを表に出してはいない。単にうなずくだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:963
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_dba1b764:

    # emi "As expected."
    emi "やっぱりね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:968
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_30b4b4ee:

    # rin "What's that supposed to mean?"
    rin "どういうこと？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:973
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8b2cd247:

    # "This time, it's Emi who shrugs."
    "今度は、肩をすくめたのは笑美だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:975
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1eea7705:

    # "It's like she's using Rin's own weapons against her."
    "まるで琳の武器を当の琳自身に対して使ってるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:980
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c2776c46:

    # emi "Your response is the sort of thing I'd expect from you, that's all."
    emi "琳の返事が思ったとおりだったってだけだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:985
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_15e372ef:

    # rin "Am I really that predictable?"
    rin "私、ほんとにそんなに予想できる感じかな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:990
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8272b43d:

    # "Emi's smile seems to border on gloating."
    "笑美は、ほくそ笑みに近い笑顔を浮かべているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:992
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_44c5b1ac:

    # emi "Nah, it's just that your unpredictability is pretty predictable."
    emi "ううん、予想できないとこが、予想できる、ってだけ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:997
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_558df1bc:

    # rin "Well that's all right then."
    rin "ならいいや"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1001
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_e050635d:

    # "I don't get the chance to see whether Rin's being serious or not, as the bell rings."
    "予鈴が鳴って、俺は琳が本気かどうか確かめる機会がなくなる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1003
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_39f8f28a:

    # "I didn't notice the lunch period slipping by at all."
    "昼休みが終わりそうなことに全く気づかなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1005
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_429a4ecf:

    # "Hanging out with these two was far too interesting."
    "二人と一緒に過ごすのが面白すぎたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1010
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cecf6725:

    # "Emi jumps up, a look of panic on her face."
    "笑美は飛び上がり、驚いた表情になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1012
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_82f72475:

    # emi "Oh no! I needed to stop by my room to pick up my notebook for the next class!"
    emi "いっけない！　あたし、次の授業で使うノートを部屋に置いてきたから行かなくちゃ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1017
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_b37e585e:

    # rin "Don't you wish you had a time machine now?"
    rin "今ならタイムマシンがあったらいいのにって思うでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1019
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_0c166bd8:

    # "Rin seems rather smug as she delivers this line; like she'd just won an argument."
    "琳はずいぶん得意そうな顔で言う。ちょうど今議論に勝ったみたいに。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1021
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_88db5625:

    # "Emi ignores Rin's comment."
    "笑美はそれを無視する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1026
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_bc4a86e9:

    # emi "Sorry Hisao, but could you make sure our garbage gets thrown away?"
    emi "ごめんね久夫くん、あたしたちのゴミ捨てといてくれる？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1031
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ace6a627:

    # emi "I usually clean up myself, but I've got to run!"
    emi "いつもは自分で片づけるんだけど、急がなきゃなんないの！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1033
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_40be391a:

    # hi "Sure, no problem."
    hi "もちろん、かまわないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1040
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_7a5c3d6a:

    # "Emi darts away with an urgency I'm starting to expect from her."
    "笑美があわただしく走り去るのもお約束に思えてきたな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1045
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d25319b3:

    # "I don't bother asking Rin why she couldn't help. She already seems to be preoccupied with something else entirely as she wanders off."
    "琳になぜ手伝わないのかと聞いたりはしない。もう琳は何か他のものに夢中みたいで、どこかへ行ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1047
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_4066e38f:

    # "She's probably used to Emi taking care of cleanup, and for some reason I doubt Emi's ever raised the issue with her."
    "たぶん、笑美に片づけてもらうことに慣れているんだろう。それになぜか、笑美もそこに異議を唱えたことがあるとは思えない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1049
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cf3cd5c2:

    # "Cleaning up from lunch doesn't take long, so I have plenty of time to toss our garbage and get to class."
    "後片づけにはそんなに時間はかからず、ゴミを捨てて授業へ向かうのに十分な時間があった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1056
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8d91fc52:

    # "Misha greets me with a wave and a devious grin as I walk through the door."
    "俺がドアを通ると、ミーシャが手を振りながらよこしまな笑顔で出迎える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1061
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_d436935d:

    # mi "Didn't see you in the cafeteria, Hicchan."
    mi "食堂では見なかったね、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1063
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_a64709d8:

    # hi "Yeah, I decided it was too crowded there."
    hi "ああ、あそこは混むからやめた"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1068
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_bf6f48a6:

    # "Misha's grin gets even wider."
    "ミーシャのにやにやが広がる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1070
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_876c078a:

    # mi "Oh really? Are you sure you weren't participating in an illicit ren—dez—vous?"
    mi "ホントにぃ～？　何かふ・じゅ・んな異性交遊とかしてなかったって断言できる～？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1072
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_c9e83981:

    # hi "W… what? What are you talking about?"
    hi "な……何だよ？　何言ってんだよお前？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1077
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_b0b0640d:

    # mi "You were on the roof, right? With both Rin and Emi, no less! You Casanova, you!"
    mi "屋上にいたよね？　琳と笑美といっしょだったよ絶対！　もう、この女ったらしってば～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1079
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_878f8a48:

    # hi "We… we just had lunch, that's all!"
    hi "お……俺たちは昼飯食ってたんだ、それだけだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1084
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_37f0ddb1:

    # "Misha bursts into laughter, drawing the attention of several of my classmates."
    "ミーシャが急に笑い出すと、何人かのクラスメートの注目の的になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1086
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_29373ff7:

    # mi "Wahahaha! You're so adorable when you blush like that, Hicchan!"
    mi "わははは～！　そうやって赤くなるのすっごいかわいいね、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1091
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_8be903a5:

    # "She gives me a conspiratorial wink."
    "ミーシャは俺に陰謀めいたウインクをする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1096
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ae22f87e:

    # mi "Don't worry, your secret's safe with me."
    mi "心配しなくていーよ、ひっちゃんの隠しごとはあたしの心にしまっておくから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1098
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_7b78579c:

    # hi "There's no secret!"
    hi "隠しごとなんかねーよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1103
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_cf3afc71:

    # mi "Oh?"
    mi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1105
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_be5b03a9:

    # "Misha seems disappointed and then brightens up again."
    "ミーシャはがっかりしたみたいだけど、すぐまた晴ればれとした顔になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1110
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_1ece101a:

    # mi "Time will tell~!"
    mi "そのうちわかるよね～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1112
translate jp a2_emi_clouds_time_travel_and_thou_ff9876aa:

    # "I don't know what the hell she's talking about, but blessedly our teacher comes in, and the class starts."
    "お前は何を言っているんだ。けど幸い、先生が教室に入ってきて授業が始まる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1125
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1cff6406:

    # "Another day of class has finally dragged itself to a close."
    "ある日の授業もようやくながら終わった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1127
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_05ca0e89:

    # "Unexpectedly, I managed to stay awake for the whole day."
    "期待はしてなかったけど、丸一日起きていることができた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1129
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1d6fd8f8:

    # "I'm pretty sure that counts as a miracle."
    "これはちょっとした奇跡と言っていいな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1131
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_416871ed:

    # "My legs seem unwilling to stand up for a moment."
    "俺の足はしばらく立ち上がる気がないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1133
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_5e66b684:

    # "I guess the run took a lot out of me."
    "たぶん、朝練でやられたんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1138
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_74c28be9:

    # "I head down the hallway and make my way to my room."
    "俺は廊下へ出て自室へと向かう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1143
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_bf52f83b:

    # "I sit down and half-heartedly chip away at my homework for a while, feeling like a vulture picking at a particularly unsavory carcass."
    "机に向かって、気乗りしないまま宿題をしばらくちまちまと進める。まるでハゲタカがクソまずい死体をつつくように。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1145
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4a4598f8:

    # "It knows this is what it eats, but it's not sure that it shouldn't be ordering takeout instead."
    "ハゲタカだって、食えると知ったところでこれをお持ち帰りにはしてもらわないよな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1147
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_232ef107:

    # "I don't think I can take this, but it's important to get my work done."
    "これ以上耐えられるとは思えないけど、課題を済ませるのは重要なことなんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1149
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0e0c5d25:

    # hi "Now let's see… what was I supposed to be looking over again?"
    hi "さて……何を調べるんだったっけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1151
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_64a68944:

    # "I know it's a losing battle, but I fight it anyway."
    "負けるとわかっていても戦わなければならない時がある。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1153
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_27ee5ad2:

    # "Halfway through my math homework, I put my pencil down."
    "数学の宿題の途中で俺は鉛筆を置いた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1155
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b70242d0:

    # "This isn't working. I need a distraction."
    "だめだ。気晴らしが必要だな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1157
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_eb28cb4b:

    # "Unfortunately, my options for distractions are rather slim."
    "あいにく、気晴らしになるような選択肢はほんのわずかしかない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1159
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6f956c74:

    # "I'm not in the mood to read, right now."
    "今は本を読む気分じゃない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1161
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4fb48ec5:

    # "Kenji is, unusually, out of his room at the moment."
    "健二は今、珍しく外出している。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1163
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_64fc6c34:

    # "If I go to the student council room, I'll just end up doing work for those two."
    "生徒会室に行ったら、結局は静音とミーシャの仕事を手伝うはめになるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1165
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_06cf80d7:

    # "And heaven only knows where everyone else is, except for…"
    "そして他の奴らがどこにいるかは神のみぞ知るってとこだな、あいつ以外は……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1167
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_00802bee:

    # "Well, I suppose that's an option."
    "そうだな、それもひとつの選択肢かもな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1169
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_dbb48dbc:

    # "I grab my shoes and head for the track. Emi's probably down there."
    "俺は運動靴をひっつかんで競技場へ向かう。笑美がそこにいるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1176
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_653e55ed:

    # "Track practice is just ending as I arrive at the track."
    "競技場に着いたら、陸上部の練習が終わるところだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1178
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1a4cde7b:

    # "The sun's beginning to dip low in the sky."
    "太陽が空の向こうに沈み始めている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1180
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_14cc8889:

    # "Has it really gotten that late already?"
    "もうそんなに時間が経っていたのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1185
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_42cbb343:

    # emi "What are you doing down here, Hisao?"
    emi "こんなとこで何してるの？　久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1190
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9e7cb374:

    # emi "Come to spy on me, have you?"
    emi "スパイしに来たんでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1192
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e69340a9:

    # "I give a shrug. To be honest, I'm not sure why I'm down here."
    "俺は肩をすくめる。正直、なぜここに来たのかわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1194
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c2e01bca:

    # hi "I didn't have anything better to do."
    hi "他にすることもないし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1196
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9574388a:

    # "I figure that's about right."
    "だいたい合ってるよな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1198
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e4a1f2c6:

    # "At the moment, Emi's the only person I can think of who I could visit."
    "いま、会えると思えたのは笑美だけだし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1203
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_abfddf6c:

    # emi "So I'm your last resort, am I?"
    emi "それで、あたしが最後の頼みの綱だってわけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1208
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_91b84e7f:

    # emi "Nobody cool around, so I'll just go see Emi, is that what you thought?"
    emi "他の人たちは微妙だし、じゃあ笑美にでも会いに行こう、なんて思ったの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1210
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e1766134:

    # "She actually looks angry."
    "ほんとに怒ってるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1212
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7b8e920a:

    # "A chance for some teasing of my own presents itself."
    "からかってやるチャンスの発生だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1214
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0839c18f:

    # hi "Actually, yeah, I guess you are."
    hi "実際そんなとこだろうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1219
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c76cf9de:

    # "Emi pouts, widening her eyes to give the maximum amount of puppy-dog resemblance."
    "笑美は口をとがらせ、子犬そっくりに目を見開く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1221
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_40493883:

    # hi "Kidding! I was kidding!"
    hi "冗談！　冗談だよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1226
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e991eace:

    # emi "So you are down here to stalk me!"
    emi "じゃああたしにつきまといに来たんだ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1228
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7afba655:

    # "Wait, what?"
    "待てよ、何だって？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1230
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b5cd958b:

    # hi "That's not what I meant!"
    hi "そんなつもりで言ったんじゃない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1232
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b81a7ea2:

    # hi "Why would I stalk you anyway? It's not like you require stalking."
    hi "なんで俺が笑美につきまとわなきゃなんないんだよ？　つきまとってほしいわけじゃないんだろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1234
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0faf65ab:

    # hi "If you're not asleep or in class, you're down here, right?"
    hi "お前は寝ているか授業中とかじゃなければここに来るんだろ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1236
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4c18e95f:

    # "Emi laughs at this comment."
    "笑美はそれを聞いて笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1241
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_64763d96:

    # emi "Well, you're not all wrong, I suppose - but you forgot about eating. I do that too, you know."
    emi "まあ、間違ってもいないと思うけど――でも久夫くん、食事のこと忘れてるよ。あたしだってそれくらいするし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1243
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_d3e576aa:

    # "I nod, conceding the point."
    "俺はうなずく。そこはしょうがない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1248
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_043c01a7:

    # emi "Plus I hang out with Rin sometimes too… so really I might take some effort to stalk."
    emi "それにあたし、ときどき琳とも遊ぶし……だからつきまとうのはちょっと大変かもしれないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1250
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9b365151:

    # hi "What do you two do together anyway? You don't seem to have a lot in common."
    hi "いっしょに何するんだよ？　共通点があるようには見えないけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1255
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_a7b66bae:

    # "She puts her hands on her hips and assumes a superior air."
    "笑美は自分の手をお尻に当てて偉そうな態度をとる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1260
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_52d85d1d:

    # emi "That's what you think. I've got all sorts of hidden hobbies, you know."
    emi "へえ、そう思うんだ。隠れた趣味ならあたしいろいろあるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1262
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_210f3a28:

    # hi "Oh really? Like what?"
    hi "ほんとに？　例えば？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1267
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6acf9d07:

    # "Emi puts her head to one side, as if she's trying to remember what it is she does in her free time."
    "笑美は、自分の自由時間にすることを思い出すように、頭を傾ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1272
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_18627e06:

    # emi "Well, Rin and I go out shopping sometimes."
    emi "そうね、琳とあたしでときどき外に買い物に行くよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1274
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_99eb9e20:

    # "I guess that makes sense. Emi's a girl, after all. But Rin?"
    "筋は通ってるな。なんだかんだ言っても笑美は女の子だし。でも琳は？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1276
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_514d8e11:

    # hi "Rin comes with you?"
    hi "琳も一緒なのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1281
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_a9081798:

    # emi "We usually swing by the art supply store."
    emi "あたしたち、いつも画材屋さんに寄り道するの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1283
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_67451027:

    # emi "Plus she likes this music store that sells all kinds of weird sounding stuff."
    emi "それと、琳はなんか変な楽器とか音楽とかいっぱい売ってる楽器屋も好きなの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1288
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8e065dad:

    # emi "She says it helps focus her."
    emi "そういうのがあると集中できるんだって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1290
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0672fa07:

    # "That makes a little more sense."
    "それならまあわかる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1292
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_e9e15980:

    # hi "I see. Any other hidden hobbies?"
    hi "ふーん。で他に隠れた趣味は？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1297
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_2a93f3e4:

    # "Emi wags a finger at me."
    "笑美は指を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1299
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_965d1fa2:

    # emi "Now now, why would I go and reveal all my dark secrets to you? We hardly know one another!"
    emi "待ってよ、なんで全部ばらさなきゃなんないの？　あたしたちまだそんな知り合いじゃないじゃん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1301
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ad6eb239:

    # "Somehow I think that's all that Emi has in the way of hobbies."
    "なぜか、笑美は琳といることが趣味の全てなんじゃないかと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1303
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_aadae404:

    # "Still, I don't think my question's been answered."
    "でも、自分の疑問が解けたとは思わない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1305
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6138c56d:

    # hi "Even if you do have a few hobbies, I still don't see why you hang out with Rin so much."
    hi "趣味の２つや３つはあってもさ、なんでそんなに琳とぶらぶらするのか、俺にはわかんないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1307
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0a4a72ff:

    # hi "I mean, she's kind of weird, isn't she?"
    hi "思うんだけど、琳って、どっちかって言うと変わってるよな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1309
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ad0bbf54:

    # "This comment causes Emi to laugh loudly."
    "その一言で笑美は大笑いする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1314
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ef8f38c6:

    # emi "Ha! That's the understatement of the year!"
    emi "あはは！　最高に控えめな言い方ね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1316
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4a7bd582:

    # hi "So why? I mean, you're a lot better at conversation and stuff, so I figure you'd hang out with a lot of people, but I think I've only ever seen you with Rin."
    hi "だからなんで琳？　っていうのは、笑美は人と話したりするの得意だから、いろんな人と仲いいんだろうなあって思ったら、琳といるとこしか見たことないしさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1321
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0d8635e5:

    # "Emi seems unusually defensive."
    "笑美は珍しく受身の様子だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1323
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4d3031d2:

    # emi "Hey, I hang out with plenty of people that aren't Rin! You just don't see me doing it because I'm not in your classes."
    emi "ちょっと、あたし琳じゃなくて他のみんなとも仲いいから！　久夫くんとはクラスが違うから、見たことないだけだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1325
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_29e25a96:

    # hi "Okay, but that still doesn't explain why you hang out with Rin."
    hi "そうだな、でもそれじゃまだ琳と一緒にいることの説明になってないぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1327
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3856b20c:

    # "I'm not even sure why I want to know this."
    "自分でもなんでこんなことを知りたいのかわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1329
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_07a60293:

    # "I guess it is because lunch was so strange."
    "今日のランチがあまりにも変だったからだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1334
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_bea7a016:

    # "Emi shrugs, looking for a moment very Rin-ish."
    "笑美が肩をすくめて、一瞬、すごく琳っぽく見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1338
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4554cb2e:

    # emi "It's because we have similar outlooks."
    emi "あたしたちが似たような生き方をしてるからだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1340
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_84486b97:

    # "If you were to ask me the least likely answer to my question, that would be it."
    "こんなに予想を裏切る答えもないと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1342
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c1dd2181:

    # hi "What do you mean?"
    hi "どういう意味ですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1344
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_00856469:

    # emi "It's like…"
    emi "例えば……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1351
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7d266f8f:

    # emi "Okay, Rin paints and stuff, right?"
    emi "そうね、琳は絵を描いたりしてるよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1353
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8a2b55c1:

    # hi "Yes…"
    hi "そうだな……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1355
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_fc449a6f:

    # "I'm not sure where this is going."
    "この話はどこに行くんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1360
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_7f1649c5:

    # emi "Well, I run."
    emi "で、あたしは走る"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1362
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_d920e11b:

    # hi "And?"
    hi "で？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1367
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_69c7a11f:

    # emi "And… that's why we're similar."
    emi "で……それがあたしたちが似てる理由"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1369
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_35c4f685:

    # hi "…"
    hi "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1371
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_57c81971:

    # hi "You lost me."
    hi "わけわかんねーよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1376
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_49ec4251:

    # "Emi frowns, as if trying to figure out her answer."
    "笑美はうまい答えを見つけようと顔をしかめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1378
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_fbb8954d:

    # emi "Well, maybe it's that we do things for the same reasons."
    emi "そうね、行動原理が同じなのかも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1380
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1385
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_263acb14:

    # emi "You know, we follow our passions."
    emi "んーとね、あたしたちは自分の情熱に従ってるの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1387
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_467afdba:

    # hi "So you're passionate about running and Rin's passionate about art, is that it?"
    hi "それって笑美が走るのに熱心で、琳は芸術に熱心だってことか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1389
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_909055c5:

    # emi "Well, sort of. Let me think…"
    emi "まあそんな感じ。えーっとね……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1394
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_39c6c229:

    # emi "Well, Rin explained it to me once, but I don't know how much of it I followed."
    emi "そうそう、琳は前にあたしに話してくれたけど、自分でもどれだけ理解できたかわかんないの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1396
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_1843aff7:

    # "Not surprising. I think any explanation from Rin would probably confuse anyone."
    "べつに驚くことでもない。琳からなら、なにを説明されても誰だって混乱するだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1401
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_f2ad4e5f:

    # emi "She says we both chase after an extreme."
    emi "琳は、あたしたちは二人とも極端なものを追いかけてるって言うんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1403
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3f3aa752:

    # emi "Like, she's always trying to find a new way to show a particular feeling or something."
    emi "例えば、琳は特別な感覚かなにかを表現する新しい方法を探そうとしてるの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1408
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b1c98b50:

    # emi "And I run because of the feeling I get from it."
    emi "で、あたしは走ることで得られる特別な感覚のために走るの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1410
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_04cdf809:

    # emi "And since we don't allow ourselves to be slowed down by anything, we make a connection based on that."
    emi "それに、ぐずぐずさせられるのは二人とも嫌なの。あたしたちはそれでつながってるんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1412
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_881fdebd:

    # hi "What do you mean 'slowed down by anything?'"
    hi "『ぐずぐずさせられる』って？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1417
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_df5bea04:

    # "Emi looks surprised and points to her legs."
    "笑美は驚いたようで、自分の足を指さす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1419
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3e12ee5a:

    # emi "You know, because I'm a runner. And Rin's a painter even without arms."
    emi "だって、あたしはランナーだから。それに琳は腕がなくたって絵を描いてる"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1421
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6327fc07:

    # emi "So we respect each other's determination."
    emi "だからお互いにその決心を尊重してるの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1426
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_bcd5c013:

    # emi "And that's why we hang out."
    emi "だからいっしょにいる"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1431
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c2f1fc54:

    # emi "I think."
    emi "たぶん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1433
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_3a4ba809:

    # "Well, I'm not sure that made any sense to me… but from Emi's sheepish expression, she's not sure about it either."
    "まあ、俺にその意味がわかったかどうか……でも、自信なさげな顔つきからすると、笑美もわからないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1435
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_cf4f24fd:

    # emi "Honestly, it's not something I think about much."
    emi "正直、そんなことあんまり考えないけどね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1437
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_03603dcc:

    # emi "We just get along - I think that's really all that matters."
    emi "あたしたちはうまくいってる――それがすべてじゃないかなって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1439
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_9a0bd601:

    # "I suppose she's got a point there."
    "笑美は核心を突いたなと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1441
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8da12570:

    # "Another question strikes me, and since I've got nothing better to do, I ask it."
    "別の質問が浮かび上がってきて、他にすることもなかったから、尋ねてみる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1443
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_42844917:

    # hi "So what got you so into running, anyway?"
    hi "ところでさ、何がきっかけでそんなに笑美は走るようになったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1448
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_91f35772:

    # emi "Oh, I've been running since I was really little!"
    emi "あー、ほんとにちっちゃいころから走ってるよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1453
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_594da9b4:

    # emi "My dad was a runner, and so as soon as I could walk, he started teaching me how to run."
    emi "パパが陸上選手で、あたしが歩けるようになるとすぐに走り方を教え始めたの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1458
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_6891bf5a:

    # emi "It was our father/daughter thing, you know?"
    emi "それがあたしにとって、父親と娘の絆だったんだよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1465
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0433ebbc:

    # emi "Our own mutual hobby."
    emi "ふたりの共通の趣味"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1467
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0255297d:

    # "A shadow crosses her face, and I'm shocked to see her looking… sad."
    "笑美の顔に影が差して、哀しそうに見えて……ショックだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1469
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_4845b643:

    # "Did something happen between them?"
    "笑美とお父さんの間に何かあったんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1474
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_da6aaba4:

    # emi "Man, I don't have a lot of time left."
    emi "ああもう、あんまり時間ないや"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1479
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_8460b1f8:

    # emi "Sorry, but I've got to get a few more laps in before I go see the nurse!"
    emi "ごめんね、ナースくんのところに行く前にもう少し走るから！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1490
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ce07fc80:

    # "She races off around the track, hair streaming in the wind."
    "笑美は髪を風になびかせてトラックをひた走る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1492
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_0fbb07b0:

    # "It seems to me she's going a lot faster than she was this morning."
    "今朝よりもかなり速く走っているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1494
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_b37e621c:

    # "As she rounds the track, I catch a glimpse of her face."
    "トラックを回っている笑美の顔を、俺はちらりと見る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1501
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_90636662:

    # "It's much the same as it was this morning, but her eyes seem to have taken on a harder edge."
    "今朝とほとんど同じだけど、その目つきは険しくなっているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1503
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_04f5d596:

    # "I guess she's right."
    "笑美の言うとおりかもな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1505
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_65203351:

    # "I don't really know much about her."
    "俺はほんとうに、笑美のことをよく知らない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1510
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_32d87805:

    # "I watch her run for a little while and then stand up to head back to my room."
    "少し笑美の走りを見てから、部屋に戻るために立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1512
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_5c001712:

    # emi "Hey!"
    emi "ねえ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1514
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c46bb449:

    # "She spots me leaving and waves to catch my attention."
    "笑美が帰る俺を見つけて、注意をひくように手を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1516
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_ffcd2dd0:

    # emi "Don't forget! Same time tomorrow morning, got it?"
    emi "忘れないで！　また明日の朝の同じ時間にね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1518
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_641f55dc:

    # hi "Got it."
    hi "わかりました"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1522
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_c706730e:

    # "I head back to my room."
    "俺は部屋へと戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1524
translate jp a2_emi_questions_that_need_answering_a60ae1c4:

    # "Homework beckons."
    "宿題が俺を呼んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1537
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_76143a19:

    # "I can't sleep."
    "眠れない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1539
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b69598ce:

    # "My body's tired, but my mind is kept awake, staring at the ceiling in the hollow darkness of my room."
    "体は疲れていても頭は起きていて、俺は部屋のうつろな闇に浮かぶ天井を見つめている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1541
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2e0c1f1f:

    # "I grasp desperately for a thread of thought, hoping that I can run my brain into the ground."
    "頭もくたくたになればいいのにと思って、必死で思考の脈絡をつけようとする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1543
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9a376b66:

    # "All I can think of is how I can't think of anything."
    "俺が考えられるのは、何も考えられないということだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1545
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3631b696:

    # "This is not productive at all."
    "まったく生産的じゃない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1547
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c451782f:

    # "I wonder if this is a side effect of my medication, though it seems odd for it to take so long to show up."
    "薬の副作用だろうか。でもそうだとしたら、出始めるのが妙に遅すぎる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1549
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_08f3e616:

    # "Then again, maybe I'm just not as used to my new surroundings as I'd like to think."
    "やっぱり、思うほど新しい環境に慣れていないだけかも。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1551
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c46c4013:

    # "I don't know, but for whatever reason, I'm awake and I shouldn't be."
    "わからないけど、でも理由はともかく、俺は、起きてちゃいけないのに起きている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1553
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7eccd23e:

    # "This is ridiculous."
    "ばかばかしいな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1560
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_641389ea:

    # "Ignoring my body's stiffness, I get out of bed and look at my clock."
    "体の凝りは無視して、ベッドから出て時計を見る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1562
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_828d67f9:

    # "Four in the morning. Last time I checked it was only one, so maybe I slept a little."
    "朝４時。最後に時計を確認したときはまだ１時だったから、少し寝たのかも。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1564
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2293b91e:

    # "I don't know."
    "わからないけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1566
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3e2bf3da:

    # "I throw on some clothes and head out of my room."
    "俺は服を引っかけて部屋を出る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1568
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_76e023e5:

    # "A walk might do me some good."
    "歩けば少しはましになるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1573
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c74c10cd:

    # "I'm surprised at how chill the air is compared to the relative warmth of the day."
    "日中の暖かさに比べて、外の空気がずいぶん寒いのに驚く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1575
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5b047865:

    # "I can almost see my breath as I wander the campus, waiting for the sun to come up or for me to fall asleep."
    "構内を歩き回っていると自分の吐く息が見える。日が昇るのが先か俺が眠くなるのが先か。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1577
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_eff6a17b:

    # "At this point, either option works for me."
    "現在のところ、どっちもありだけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1582
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8051d71b:

    # "I find myself at the track - where for the first time, Emi's not out running."
    "気がついたら競技場にいた――笑美が走っていない競技場を見るのは、初めてだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1584
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6535d7c5:

    # "I suppose that makes sense; it's too early, even for her."
    "そりゃそうだろう。さすがに笑美でもこの時間じゃ早いよな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1586
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b190f5db:

    # "The bleacher seats are cold, but at this point I welcome the sensation."
    "屋外の観客席は冷たいけど、今の俺にはこの感覚がありがたい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1593
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_50ee524f:

    # "The sun is starting to show its face over the horizon, and I know with an awful certainty that I'll get no more sleep tonight."
    "太陽が地平線に顔をのぞかせ始めて、今からまた寝るのはもう無理だなと確信する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1595
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5e32942f:

    # "The sun's steadily strengthening rays start to warm me up, and I watch the dew on the ground begin to steam slightly."
    "徐々に強くなる陽の光が体を暖めるにつれ、地面の露もすこし湯気を立てはじめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1597
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_34ea4543:

    # "My mind calms down, a little."
    "心がほんの少し落ち着いてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1608
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6bd09bdf:

    # "Someone's shaking me."
    "誰かが俺を揺さぶっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1610
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_92a1230a:

    # emi "Hey, wake up!"
    emi "ちょっと、起きてよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1612
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b4a2b0ba:

    # hi "Huh? Where? Wha?"
    hi "あぁ？　どこだ？　ふぁ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1618
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b087745b:

    # "I guess I fell asleep after all."
    "結局寝ちゃったんだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1623
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_cd1bd74c:

    # emi "What are you doing out here? You're going to catch a cold or something!"
    emi "こんなとこで何してんの？　風邪とか引くよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1627
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_14984b38:

    # "I rub my eyes and am confronted by Emi, who bends over me with a worried expression."
    "俺は目をこすって、心配そうにのぞきこんでいる笑美と向かいあう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1629
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7cca9672:

    # "I'm still a little groggy, so my response comes out in a mumble."
    "俺はまだふらふらで、言葉もはっきりしない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1631
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_19e4566c:

    # hi "Couldn't sleep. Watched the sun come up."
    hi "寝られなくってさ。日の出を見てたんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1636
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c2261f8a:

    # emi "Sounds like something Rin would say."
    emi "琳みたいなこと言うね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1638
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_69c3aca8:

    # "I shrug, feeling the stiffness that comes with sleeping on a bench for a few hours."
    "俺は肩をすくめる。２、３時間ベンチで寝たので、体が凝っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1640
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_66f23c32:

    # hi "Is it? I wouldn't know."
    hi "そうか？　知らないけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1645
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_f52a136f:

    # "Emi grins a little at my (somewhat cranky) response."
    "笑美は、俺の（多少めんどくさい）反応にちょっと笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1650
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6366a9b3:

    # emi "So, couldn't sleep, eh? Obviously we need to run you harder today!"
    emi "とりあえず、眠れなかったんでしょ？　なら当然、今日はきっちり走らなきゃ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1652
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4e03a9ca:

    # "Even though I've only known her for about a week, this seems a very Emi-ish response to the problem."
    "笑美のことは１週間くらいしか知らないけど、これはまったく笑美っぽい反応に見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1654
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8b420f5c:

    # hi "Hey, my body was plenty exhausted after yesterday!"
    hi "おい、体は昨日のあれでほんとにボロボロなんだぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1656
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a610478b:

    # hi "My mind was just racing, that's all."
    hi "気分が落ち着かなくてさ、それだけだって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1661
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a5841402:

    # emi "I don't see the difference. If you run hard enough, your brain will get tired too."
    emi "変わんないじゃん、きっちり走れば心だって疲れるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1663
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3bf389f7:

    # "I'm seriously questioning the wisdom of doing this first thing in the morning."
    "朝一でこんなことをする笑美の良識を俺は真剣に疑っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1665
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_62949494:

    # "I don't know if my grades will be able to handle me tiring my brain out like that."
    "そうやって頭をへとへとに疲れさせたら、学業の方がどうなるか自信がない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1675
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7837591c:

    # "Emi pulls me up from the bleachers with surprising strength for someone her size."
    "笑美は、小さな体からは考えられないほどの力で、観客席の俺を引っぱる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1677
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_aae8988a:

    # emi "Now come on, Hisao! We've got work to do!"
    emi "ほら行くよ、久夫くん！　走らなきゃ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1679
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ee027b4b:

    # "I don't actually know if I'm up to this today, to be honest."
    "正直、今日は走るのに耐えられるかどうかわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1681
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_50134bea:

    # "I mean I obviously didn't get much sleep… and what sleep I got was on the bleachers!"
    "つまり明らかに睡眠不足だし……寝たのだって観客席だぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1683
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_88f944e3:

    # hi "I don't know… should I really be running?"
    hi "どうすっかな……ほんとに走んなきゃだめか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1688
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b307e1c2:

    # "Emi glares at me."
    "笑美がにらんでくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1690
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_acddd7a0:

    # "Good heavens."
    "ありゃりゃ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1695
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_adbd75e7:

    # emi "What are you talking about? Of course you should be running!"
    emi "なに言ってんの？　走んなきゃだめに決まってるでしょ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1697
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6a432737:

    # emi "How else do you expect to work out the kinks?"
    emi "他にどうやったらすっきりするのよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1702
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8d135e74:

    # emi "You've been sleeping on the bleachers, for heaven's sake!"
    emi "観客席で寝てたじゃない、まったく！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1704
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_03d74015:

    # emi "The best way to get that soreness out is to run around a little."
    emi "痛みを取るにはちょっと走るのが一番だよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1706
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0cc077f2:

    # emi "Now stop hiding in the bleachers and get down here!"
    emi "ほら観客席に隠れてないで出てきなさい！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1708
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4afc55ab:

    # "There's no arguing that. I'm pretty sure she'd kill me if I didn't do as she said."
    "議論の余地はない。言うとおりにしなかったら間違いなく殺されるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1710
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_dee3663f:

    # "I get to my feet and hop down to the track."
    "俺は立ち上がって、トラックに飛び降りる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1715
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2ce4f5f1:

    # "The sun is warming things up rather nicely, I think."
    "太陽がうまいこと辺りを暖めているな、と思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1717
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_cf00c7cc:

    # "Emi and I begin to stretch out, and I find myself once again hard pressed not to stare."
    "笑美と俺はストレッチを始めて、俺はまた、笑美をじっと見つめないでいるのが一苦労なことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1719
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6aa53dd8:

    # "If this is how I have to wake up every day, I might be able to get used to this."
    "これで毎日起きられるなら、朝練にも慣れることができるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1724
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_32b1ca54:

    # emi "You know Hisao, it's not polite to stare."
    emi "ねえ久夫くん、失礼だよ、じろじろ見ちゃって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1726
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_015f864f:

    # hi "I wasn't staring! I swear!"
    hi "見ちゃってない！　誓って！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1728
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_81e5d4be:

    # "Emi raises an eyebrow and considers me for a minute, as if evaluating my response."
    "俺の反応を査定でもするみたいに、笑美は眉をつり上げてしばらく考える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1730
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bef44fa8:

    # "There's a brief moment where I'm afraid for my life."
    "人生で一番恐ろしい間だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1735
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a646895d:

    # "But then she smiles and laughs, shaking her head slowly."
    "でも笑美はゆっくり首を振って微笑み、やがて笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1740
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7be98044:

    # emi "Honestly, you didn't have to deny it so strenuously."
    emi "そんなにむきになって否定しなくてもいいのに"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1744
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_73c382b1:

    # "In response, I clap my hands together and go for a change of subject."
    "返事のかわりに俺は手を叩いて、話題を変える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1746
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_71c4d746:

    # hi "So! That's enough stretching, right?"
    hi "さて！　ストレッチはもう十分だよな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1751
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_726e445d:

    # "Emi gives a casual shrug."
    "笑美は軽く肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1753
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_384d34e7:

    # emi "Do you feel stretched? That's really how you tell."
    emi "伸ばせた感じしてる？　ちゃんと自分で判断するんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1755
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d9d66371:

    # "Well, I do feel up to the run, if that's what she means."
    "もし走れるかどうかという意味だったら、大いに走れる気分だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1757
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d95b885d:

    # hi "Yeah, I feel ready to go."
    hi "そうだな、準備万端だ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1762
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a27e564e:

    # emi "Same as yesterday, okay?"
    emi "昨日と同じでいい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1764
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bc59a534:

    # emi "We'll just run for a mile at a steady pace."
    emi "ちょうどいいペースで１６００いくよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1769
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0af6fe3a:

    # emi "Don't worry about going really fast, just worry about keeping the pace, got it?"
    emi "速く走ることは考えなくていいから、ペースを保つことを考えて、いい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1771
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_990cb073:

    # hi "You're the boss."
    hi "そうするよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1787
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_12693853:

    # "Emi grins again, and we take off around the track."
    "笑美がまた笑って、俺たちはトラックを回り始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1792
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1794
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1796
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_f4d423f9:

    # "I think I'm going to die."
    "もう死にそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1798
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bb36f705:

    # "We're not even done with the first lap, and my legs are on fire."
    "まだ１周目も終わっていないのに、足が燃えるように熱い。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1800
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a74ff24d:

    # "My breath is coming in ragged gasps."
    "呼吸も息切れでボロボロになってきている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1802
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5af15a77:

    # "I can feel sweat pouring down my brow, and we've only just now rounded the second turn."
    "眉毛に汗が伝ってくるのを感じる。それでもやっとカーブを２つ回っただけだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1812
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a151a2af:

    # emi "Come on, Hisao! You've got three more laps to go!"
    emi "ほら久夫くん！　あと３周あるよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1821
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_33709709:

    # "I can't do this…"
    "無理だ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1823
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ec88d4cf:

    # "I can't do this."
    "無理。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1825
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6e7f40bd:

    # "I can't do this!"
    "むり！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1827
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9984c60f:

    # "I think I might hurl."
    "吐きそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1829
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7b4b9cb9:

    # "Somehow we're on the second lap. Emi's not even sweating."
    "なんとか２周目に入った。笑美は汗ひとつかいていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1831
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2aa10bb9:

    # "How can she do this so effortlessly?"
    "なんでそんなに楽そうなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1833
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_91c9d742:

    # "For some reason I'm still moving."
    "どういうわけか、俺はまだ走っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1835
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6cb1b25d:

    # "She's like a machine."
    "笑美はまるで機械だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1837
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_903c560a:

    # "Third lap. What happened to the second?"
    "３周目。２周目はどうなったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1847
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a750ddef:

    # emi "Almost there, Hisao!"
    emi "あともう一息だよ、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1856
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3b6a2f5b:

    # "Liar! We've got another two!"
    "嘘つけ！　まだ２周もあるだろ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1858
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_89842ec6:

    # "Nothing to be done."
    "お手上げだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1860
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b9c02df1:

    # hi "I… ca… can't… do… this."
    hi "こ……こんな……の……むり……だろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1870
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1c290a50:

    # "Emi whirls around and begins running backwards."
    "笑美はくるっと回って後ろ向きに走り始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1872
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_45c4167c:

    # "Her face is a mask of anger that surprises me."
    "怒りの表情に驚く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1877
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_295f73eb:

    # emi "Never say that!"
    emi "そんなこと言わないで！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1879
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6d0b8e21:

    # emi "If you say that, you'll have already lost."
    emi "それ言ったら負けだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1884
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7babca53:

    # emi "Keep moving! If you're alive, you can keep moving, dammit!"
    emi "走り続けて！　生きてるんなら、走れるのに！　バカ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1893
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b24eb03c:

    # "Whoa, language. We're on the fourth lap now."
    "うわっ、なんて言い方だよ。俺たちはようやく４周目に入る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1895
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9e454ac9:

    # "She really seems to want me to keep going."
    "笑美は本当に俺に走り続けてほしいみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1897
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0dcece9c:

    # "Legs move. Move. Move. They feel so sluggish."
    "足よ動け。動け。動け。なんて重いんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1899
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8e9c8fe0:

    # "I'm in mud, or molasses, or tar."
    "泥か糖蜜かタールの中にいるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1901
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b7c8c503:

    # "I can't go on."
    "足が続かない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1903
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_536b5584:

    # "I'll go on."
    "走り続ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1913
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_47d50daa:

    # emi "Final stretch, Hisao! Give it all you've got!"
    emi "久夫くんラストまっすぐ！　全力で！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1922
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3f50336e:

    # "I pump my legs as fast as they'll go."
    "俺は、できる限り速く足を動かす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1924
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1a568b36:

    # "They keep refusing to obey my commands."
    "両足は命令に従うのを拒否し続けている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1926
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_22609351:

    # "Somehow, I keep moving."
    "どうにか、俺は動き続ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1928
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ee25f0ca:

    # "Somehow, I finish."
    "なんとか、俺はゴールする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1937
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bc26d0ff:

    # emi "That's it, Hisao! I knew you had it in you!"
    emi "そうだよ、久夫くん！　やればできるじゃない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1939
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0f69a088:

    # "The anger Emi showed a lap ago is gone, replaced with pride."
    "１周前に見せた怒りは消え、誇らしげな顔になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1941
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_38e7914a:

    # "She's positively radiant, like she just won the gold medal or something."
    "自分が金メダルかなにかでも取ったみたいに晴れやかだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1947
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4f2e8e77:

    # "I stagger to a stop and fall to my hands and knees, gasping for air."
    "俺は止まろうとしてよろけて、手と膝からくずれ落ち、空気を求めてあえぐ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1949
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c833a6bb:

    # "My heart is pounding far harder than it has in a long time."
    "こんなに動悸が激しいことになるのは本当に久しぶりだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1960
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c4d58312:

    # "I don't think it's done this since…"
    "あれ以来こんなこと起きてなかったのに……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1969
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0b026d98:

    # "Oh God."
    "しまった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1981
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3ff0d109:

    # "Please slow down, heart."
    "落ち着いてくれ、心臓。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:1997
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9853f1cb:

    # "Just slow down. Stop racing."
    "ちょっと落ち着いてくれ。すこし止まってくれ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2013
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_30b4ea74:

    # "I cough, and for some reason, feel a grin crossing my face."
    "咳払いをすると、なぜか、軽く笑ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2029
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_bd088b54:

    # "So this is how I die, huh?"
    "で、俺はこうやって死ぬのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2045
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_08cbb382:

    # "Trying to stay healthy?"
    "健康でいようとして？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2061
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_982e4257:

    # "How ironic."
    "皮肉なもんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2084
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b29d99bc:

    # "I'm all ready to give up right there."
    "あきらめる準備ならもうできてるって。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2107
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_270581ee:

    # "But then, I feel my heart slow down."
    "それでも、心臓が落ち着いてくるのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2109
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_348769ca:

    # "Two hands grab under my arms and tug upwards."
    "二つの手が俺の腕の下をつかんで、引き上げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2115
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4a7fb1d0:

    # "I look up and see Emi standing over me, with a mixture of delight and worry."
    "見上げると、笑美が喜びと心配の入り交じった顔で覆いかぶさっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2117
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7f24370d:

    # emi "On your feet!"
    emi "立って！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2122
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5dc4725e:

    # emi "Come on, you'll never catch your breath that way."
    emi "さあ、そんなんじゃいつまでたっても息を整えられないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2124
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_dc37cc9d:

    # "Somehow, I manage to stand. I try to raise my arms above my head, but they feel like lead."
    "俺はなんとか立ち上がる。頭の上に腕を上げようとするけど、腕は鉛のようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2126
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a43200c1:

    # "I start to walk around the track while Emi keeps close to me, like she's afraid I'll fall over or something."
    "笑美がそばにつき、俺は歩いてトラックを回り始める。笑美は俺が倒れでもしないかと思ってるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2128
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_95a5ecb8:

    # "She may not be far off."
    "当たらずも遠からず、かもな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2130
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b909c41e:

    # "I feel terrible, and say so."
    "ものすごくつらくて、笑美にそう言った。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2135
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_597d2011:

    # "Emi laughs."
    "笑美は笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2140
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b894e5e5:

    # emi "But you finished, didn't you?"
    emi "でもやり遂げたじゃない？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2145
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_481a9581:

    # emi "You said you couldn't, but you did."
    emi "久夫くんはできないって言ったけど、やり遂げたよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2147
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d5aeb26b:

    # emi "Isn't that worth it?"
    emi "それってすごいことじゃない？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2149
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_06322bd1:

    # "I'm not sure, and I don't really have the breath to say so."
    "すごいかどうかはわからないし、それを言うための息も続かない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2151
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_465de0c3:

    # "But that small grin I felt on my face earlier hasn't left."
    "でも、さっき俺の顔に浮かんだ笑いは消えていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2153
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6ecd178b:

    # "So what if my heart's weak?"
    "心臓が弱いからなんだっていうんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2155
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d84532bf:

    # "I still survived this morning."
    "それでも今朝は生き延びたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2157
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c73e7102:

    # "Maybe I'll survive tomorrow, too."
    "明日も生き延びるかもな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2166
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_a3fe2825:

    # "As soon as it becomes apparent that I'm not going to suddenly keel over, Emi takes off on her sprints."
    "俺がいきなりひっくり返ったりしないことがわかると、笑美はすぐ走り始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2168
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_3a8265cf:

    # "I don't know how the hell she can manage to sprint after running a mile, but I guess she's in much better shape than me."
    "１キロ以上走った後でなんであんなにバカみたいに全力で走れるのか俺にはさっぱりわからない。でも笑美は俺よりずっと体調がいいんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2170
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7e4551e2:

    # "Once again, as I walk around the track, I can't help watching Emi sprint."
    "またトラックを歩いてクールダウンするけど、やっぱり俺は笑美の走りを見ずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2177
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_42c24929:

    # "It's weird, but she's like a different person when she's pushing herself."
    "不思議だけど、がんばっているときの笑美は別人のようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2179
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_74c6bc89:

    # "Last time I noticed her eyes, but this time it's her mouth that catches my attention."
    "前に気がついたのは笑美の目だけど、今回は口だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2181
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_babecc1d:

    # "She's not wearing her normal grin."
    "笑美は、いつもの笑顔をしていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2183
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_95ac2142:

    # "She's still smiling, but there's a tightness to it."
    "まだ微笑んではいるけど、緊張感がある。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2185
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_312941aa:

    # "It's almost grim, like she's fighting a losing battle but doesn't care."
    "まるで、勝ち目のない戦いをしているけど、そんなことを気にしていないような険しい表情だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2187
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_11fbdd18:

    # "She seems to be running harder, like she did yesterday."
    "昨日と同じように、笑美はもっときつい走り方をしているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2189
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_e16fc7e9:

    # "Sweat has started to pour down her face, but she keeps going."
    "顔から汗がしたたり始めても、笑美は走り続ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2191
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_410c1567:

    # "Her mouth finally opens as she can no longer get enough air through her nose."
    "息を鼻から十分吸えなくなると、ついに口が開く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2193
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1f30972a:

    # "As she passes me once more, legs pumping, arms swinging in time, and her lips slightly parted…"
    "笑美はもう一度俺を追い越す。激しく上下する足、合わせて振れる腕、わずかに離れた唇……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2195
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_30b4666f:

    # "She looks beautiful."
    "きれいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2205
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_18bd337c:

    # "After we've both taken some laps around the track to cool down, Emi changes back to her usual self."
    "クールダウンするために二人でトラックを何周かしたあと、笑美はいつもの姿に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2207
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_6da562e1:

    # "The transformation I saw in her is gone."
    "笑美の中に見た変化はもうない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2212
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_64e3563b:

    # emi "Not bad today, Hisao."
    emi "今日は悪くなかったよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2214
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_aa97eef5:

    # "There's almost admiration in her voice."
    "まるで褒めているみたいに聞こえる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2216
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_12f01a28:

    # hi "What do you mean? I would have stopped if you hadn't yelled at me."
    hi "どういうことだよ？　笑美が俺に怒鳴らなかったらやめてたぜ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2221
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_56cf55aa:

    # "Emi colors a little, seemingly embarrassed about her outburst."
    "笑美は少し赤くなる。さっきの爆発が気まずいみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2223
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ca35667b:

    # emi "Sorry about that, I just… can't stand to see people give up."
    emi "ごめんね、あたし……他の人があきらめるのを見るのは耐えられなくって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2225
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_de2b9073:

    # emi "Especially about something like this."
    emi "特に今みたいなことで"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2230
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_5d81784f:

    # emi "Saying 'I can't go on' is silly when you're obviously going on while you're saying it."
    emi "言ってる間もできてるのに『できない』って言ってるのはおかしいよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2232
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_b4ea039e:

    # emi "That's what this is all about."
    emi "そういうこと"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2234
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ba3b6426:

    # hi "What, saying silly things?"
    hi "おかしなことを言うことがか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2239
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_ec3f0841:

    # "Emi sticks her tongue out at me."
    "笑美は、俺に舌を出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2241
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_adbf82f2:

    # emi "Idiot. I mean showing that you're alive."
    emi "ばか。生きてるって証の話よ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2243
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_897e0a4c:

    # "Showing I'm alive, huh? I didn't know it had to be so painful."
    "俺が生きてる証だって？　それがこんなに苦しいとは知らなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2245
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_7c1c837b:

    # "But it does feel pretty good, despite that."
    "にもかかわらず、気分はかなりいい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2250
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_cc842913:

    # emi "Besides, this is one of the hardest days."
    emi "でもね、今日はいちばん厳しい日のひとつだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2252
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_c1dd2181:

    # hi "What do you mean?"
    hi "どういう意味ですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2257
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_154c3d7a:

    # emi "Whenever you start a workout, it's difficult the first day, really hard the second day, and then the third day is easier."
    emi "トレーニングを始めるときって、１日めはきついの。２日めはもっときつい。で、３日めはちょっと楽になるの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2259
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_53dfac3f:

    # emi "You'll still get days that are really hard, but they'll pop up less and less."
    emi "ほんとうに苦しい日はまだ続くけど、それがだんだん少なくなっていくの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2261
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_f0f93232:

    # hi "So this will eventually get really easy, huh?"
    hi "で、結局は余裕でできるようになる、って？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2266
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_eff07f8a:

    # emi "Yeah, of course."
    emi "そうね、もちろんよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2271
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_80d1ae86:

    # emi "But then you have to increase the difficulty, or you'll never get ahead."
    emi "でもハードルは上げていかなきゃね、そうしないと伸びないもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2273
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_fcf6bfc0:

    # emi "You'll just get complacent, and you'll lose the sense of accomplishment."
    emi "自己満足になっちゃうし、達成感もなくなるでしょ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2275
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_2451ae5c:

    # hi "So I'll have to run more than just four laps, huh?"
    hi "ってことは俺は４周以上走らなきゃいけないんだな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2280
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8651c3ce:

    # emi "Yep! But not for a while - you'll have to be careful, you know."
    emi "うん！　でも当分は――慎重に、ね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2282
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_0300e3b8:

    # "A thought strikes Emi, and her face lights up."
    "なにかひらめいたようで、笑美の顔が輝く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2287
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_89bfeb68:

    # emi "Got it!"
    emi "わかった！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2289
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_d0c47400:

    # hi "Got what?"
    hi "何が？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2294
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_4c017187:

    # emi "You can come with me to see the nurse! That way you won't fall over dead or anything!"
    emi "いっしょにナースくんのところに行こう！　それならもう倒れて死んだりしないよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2296
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_9c1ae632:

    # "How charming."
    "なんて可愛いんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2298
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8221b7d6:

    # hi "Um… when?"
    hi "んー……いつ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2303
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_8d01a221:

    # emi "Right now, of course! You'll need a shower and everything, right? We don't have much time, then!"
    emi "今すぐに決まってるじゃん！　シャワーとかもするんでしょ？　あんま時間ないよ、ほら！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2305
translate jp a2_emi_second_times_the_worst_1bc39596:

    # "Grabbing my hand, she's off, pulling me along with her."
    "笑美は俺の手をつかんで、引っぱっていく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2317
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_857bfb7e:

    # nk "My goodness, but you're in a hurry today, aren't you, Emi?"
    nk "おやおや今日はずいぶん急ぎだね、笑美ちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2321
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_5ae9c801:

    # "I have no idea how we got to the nurse's office so fast, but here we are."
    "どうやってこんなに速く着いたのか全くわからないけど、俺たちは医務室にいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2330
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d5754401:

    # "The nurse grins at Emi and seems to completely ignore me."
    "ナースは笑美にニッと笑う。俺のことは完全に無視してるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2335
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_98529ab6:

    # nk "You've got plenty of time to take a shower and get to class, you know."
    nk "シャワーして授業に出るまで、まだ時間はたっぷりあるんだけどね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2340
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b3ad1b79:

    # nk "There's no need to run through the hallways like that. I could hear you coming a mile away!"
    nk "そんなに廊下をばたばた走らなくてもいいだろう。遠くからでも丸聞こえだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2342
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0b539636:

    # "Somehow, it doesn't seem like he's actually scolding Emi at all."
    "どうも、ナースは笑美を叱ってるようにはまったく見えない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2344
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8625f4b9:

    # "It's like this is a sort of routine between the two of them."
    "まるで二人の日常のひとコマみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2346
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_74b85397:

    # "Emi does a passable imitation of remorse."
    "笑美はそこそこの演技で反省してみせる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2351
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_9ee81738:

    # emi "I'm sorry! I won't ever do it again!"
    emi "すみません！　もう二度としません！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2357
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_4e03ecd8:

    # "The nurse and Emi both laugh at some private joke."
    "なにかの内輪ネタみたいだけど、ナースと笑美は笑っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2363
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b5ad5e35:

    # "Suddenly, it seems that he notices me."
    "突然、ナースが俺に気づいたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2368
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d32718b2:

    # nk "Ah, hello Hisao."
    nk "ああ、おはよう久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2373
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_63d326fb:

    # nk "What brings you here?"
    nk "何かあったかい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2375
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0498a2b7:

    # hi "Well, I've been—{w=.3}{nw}"
    hi "そうですね、俺は――{w=.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2380
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_02b7f261:

    # emi "Hisao's officially joined me on my morning runs."
    emi "久夫くんが正式に朝練に参加したの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2382
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_7d47f3a6:

    # "I start to explain, but Emi cuts me off."
    "俺は説明しはじめるけど、笑美が割って入る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2387
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_e2cc116b:

    # emi "I thought he might need to visit you so that he doesn't die or anything."
    emi "だから死んだりしないようにここに来たほうがいいかなって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2392
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_bc997636:

    # "The nurse raises his eyebrows in mock horror."
    "ナースは、大げさに怖がって眉を吊り上げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2394
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_5e0c0172:

    # nk "Yes, that would certainly put me out of a job fast, wouldn't it?"
    nk "まったくだよ、そんなことがあったら僕はすぐにクビになっちゃうから。ねえ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2400
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_766efe82:

    # nk "Well then Hisao, let's have a look at you."
    nk "それじゃあ久夫くん、診てみようか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2402
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_45f886f3:

    # nk "Lift up your shirt, would you?"
    nk "シャツ上げてくれるかい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2404
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_042ba446:

    # "I'm suddenly very conscious of the fact that Emi's in the room with me and blush in spite of myself."
    "突然、笑美が同じ部屋にいることをすごく意識してしまって、俺は思わず赤くなる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2406
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_dc7d82f2:

    # "The nurse seems to sense my discomfort, but it only seems to amuse him."
    "ナースには俺の戸惑いがわかるみたいだけど、それはナースを面白がらせているだけのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2411
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_aa95d5d6:

    # nk "A bit shy, are we?"
    nk "ちょっと恥ずかしいよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2413
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d72d846c:

    # "He makes an apologetic bow to Emi."
    "ナースは笑美に申し訳なさそうなお辞儀をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2415
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2b288b76:

    # nk "Sorry Emi, I tried to get you a free show, but it doesn't seem to have worked."
    nk "すまないね笑美ちゃん、無料のショーをお見せできるかと思ったけど、だめだったみたいだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2420
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0c8e4123:

    # "Emi stiffens slightly and fires a look of annoyance at him."
    "笑美はちょっとこわばって、ナースにいら立った視線を浴びせる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2422
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_9ce055ab:

    # emi "You're an asshole."
    emi "うっさいバカ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2427
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_133c748b:

    # "Emi bows to me apologetically."
    "笑美は申し訳なさそうに俺にお辞儀をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2429
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_87645ab1:

    # emi "I'll wait outside, okay Hisao?"
    emi "外で待ってるね、いい、久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2438
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2e4ba855:

    # "I begin to stammer that it's not really a big deal, she doesn't have to leave, but she's already out the door, and the nurse is laughing as he watches her go."
    "いやこんなのほんとうに大したことじゃないし別に出ていかなくてもいいから、と俺はしどろもどろで言いはじめたけど、笑美はとっくにドアの外で、ナースはそれを見て笑っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2443
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_37329bf0:

    # nk "Still got it! Ha!"
    nk "まだいけるな！　ハハハ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2445
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ed15e901:

    # hi "I don't follow."
    hi "なんだそれ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2450
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c6339cd4:

    # "He laughs again, like he's in on some joke that's over my head."
    "ナースはまた笑う。俺にわからない冗談でウケているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2452
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cd7da390:

    # nk "I can still get her flustered. It's a competition of sorts we've had going on for a while now."
    nk "僕はまだ笑美ちゃんを振り回せるんだな。これは僕たちがしばらくやってる競争みたいなものだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2454
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8042e277:

    # "That sounds incredibly sinister to me, and it seems as if the nurse realizes that too."
    "それが俺にはすごく嫌な言い方に聞こえたことが、ナースにもわかったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2459
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_28bff485:

    # nk "Er. That sounded a lot worse than it actually is, come to think of it."
    nk "えーと。今の言い方は実際よりもかなりひどすぎるね、そういえば"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2461
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_91aabb5a:

    # hi "I wasn't going to say anything…"
    hi "俺なにも言ってませんけど……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2463
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_90bb458f:

    # nk "No no, you're right. I should fill you in so that you don't get the wrong idea."
    nk "いや、いや、君は正しいよ。誤解しないように説明しなきゃね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2468
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cca4ed39:

    # nk "I'm actually relatively new here, you see. I got hired on the same year Emi started going here."
    nk "僕は、実はここではどちらかと言えば新人の方なんだよ。雇われたのは笑美ちゃんがここに通い始めた年でね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2470
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_62428424:

    # nk "Before that, I worked with Emi during her initial rehab following her accident."
    nk "その前は、笑美ちゃんとは事故の後の初期のリハビリで一緒だったんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2472
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cb507ed4:

    # "Hold on, what?"
    "待った、何だって？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2477
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b855e41b:

    # nk "We had to amputate her legs after a really nasty car wreck. It nearly killed her, and succeeded—"
    nk "本当にひどい交通事故で、僕たちは彼女の足を切断しなきゃならなくなってね。危ない手術だったけど、うまくいった――"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2479
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_23802bdf:

    # "He shuts up abruptly. I blink at receiving this unexpected piece of news."
    "ナースは急に黙りこむ。俺は不意に知らされたこの事実に驚いている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2481
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_806e0e98:

    # nk "Well, that's not my place to say. Anyway, we've known each other for quite a while."
    nk "いや、僕から話せることじゃないな。とにかく、僕たちはけっこう前から知り合いなんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2483
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_0024805d:

    # nk "So we have a slightly more familiar relationship than is strictly professional."
    nk "だから患者と看護師っていうより、もうちょっと親しい仲なんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2485
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ca08d0b1:

    # "He seems embarrassed, like he's done something stupid."
    "きまり悪そうに見える。なにか悪いことでもしたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2487
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_678baecf:

    # "I guess he's really worried about that. I wave a hand to let him know it's not a big deal."
    "ナースはそのことを本当に気にしてたんだと思う。俺は手を振って、大したことじゃないと伝える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2489
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2f2d6064:

    # hi "Don't worry, sir. I promise I'm going to be discreet."
    hi "心配しないでください、先生。黙っておきますから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2491
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_4a7248eb:

    # "I had been wondering about what caused Emi to lose her legs, and that was one of the scenarios I thought of."
    "笑美が足を失った原因は気になっていた。今の話は俺も可能性のひとつとして考えていたものだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2493
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2469416a:

    # "There were only so many ways that could have happened, but actually hearing about the facts… it's still a little shocking."
    "起こりうるパターンなんてそう多くはないにしても、実際に起こったことを聞くのは……やっぱり少しショックだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2498
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b857b057:

    # nk "Well, thanks. You're a good kid, Hisao."
    nk "いや、ありがとう。君はいい子だね、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2500
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d3bc83c0:

    # nk "I can see why Emi became friends with you."
    nk "なんで笑美ちゃんが君と友達になったのかわかったよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2505
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_3869face:

    # nk "She's quite indomitable, you know."
    nk "わかるかもしれないけど、笑美ちゃんは本当に負けん気が強い"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2507
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c1dd2181:

    # hi "What do you mean?"
    hi "どういう意味ですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2509
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_cf62e096:

    # nk "You didn't see her learning to walk. She'd go for so much longer than the others in the hospital. She refused to quit."
    nk "あの子が歩く練習をするところは見てないよね。病院では他の誰よりもいっぱい練習してたんだ。頑としてやめなかった"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2511
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_59000fd5:

    # nk "Normally it takes years to get to a point where you can even think about running again. Emi did it all in about a year."
    nk "普通は、また走るなんて考えられるようになるまで何年もかかる。それを笑美ちゃんは一年ぐらいで全部やったんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2513
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_4ccea4d5:

    # "He almost seems proud of her, like a father who watches his daughter win a competition or something."
    "ほとんど自慢してるみたいだ。まるでコンテストかなにかで優勝する娘を見る父親のように。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2518
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d7c93411:

    # nk "Hell, she'd probably have done it faster if not for the fact that we wouldn't let her."
    nk "まったく、もし僕たちが止めさせなかったらもっと早くやりとげただろうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2520
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c2a0fa04:

    # hi "Wouldn't let her? Why not?"
    hi "止めさせなかったら？　なぜですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2527
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_fde6c471:

    # nk "Because she'd go for so long that her legs would start bleeding where they met her prosthetics."
    nk "長いあいだ頑張りすぎて、義肢が当たる部分から出血しはじめたんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2529
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_bd17e116:

    # nk "It's a real concern - it's why she comes by every day after she runs."
    nk "実際、厄介な問題でね――だから毎日、走ったあとはここに来るんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2531
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_548b4a4b:

    # nk "To say nothing of the risk of infection if her legs get cut up and her prosthetics are dirty."
    nk "仮に足が傷ついて義肢が汚れていれば、感染症のリスクについては言うまでもない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2536
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_a5e5ee1e:

    # nk "But enough about that."
    nk "でもこの話はもういいね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2543
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_1d14f7e2:

    # nk "If we don't get you on your way soon, Emi will think we're up to something."
    nk "もし君をこのまま引き止めてたら、笑美ちゃんは僕らが何かを企んでると思うだろうし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2545
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2c7b1e1d:

    # "As he says this, he gives a wink and begins checking my heartbeat."
    "ナースはそう言うと、ウインクをして俺の心臓の鼓動をチェックしはじめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2547
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_f0057a9c:

    # "The stethoscope is way too cold."
    "聴診器があまりに冷たすぎる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2549
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d860dd4a:

    # "He really should have heated it up or something before he used it."
    "使う前に暖めるかなにかしておけばいいのに。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2551
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_a16ae1a0:

    # "After a few moments he leans back, satisfied."
    "しばらくして、ナースは背を反らして、満足する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2556
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8eb547e6:

    # nk "Well, you sound pretty good to me, Hisao. You didn't have any chest pains while you were running, did you?"
    nk "うん、だいぶいい感じに聞こえるね、久夫くん。走っている間、胸の痛みはなかったかい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2558
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_a65a2fd0:

    # hi "No, not really. I had some trouble catching my breath, though - and my heart was racing by the end, too."
    hi "いいえ、あんまり。でも、呼吸がちょっと辛かったです――それと終わるころには動悸が速くなってました"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2563
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ba2b3d3b:

    # "The nurse frowns as I say this, but then shrugs."
    "俺がそう言うと、ナースは眉をひそめるけど、肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2568
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8b617ffc:

    # nk "It's probably just because you're out of shape… but if you don't improve, then you should let me know, okay?"
    nk "それは単に運動不足だからだろうね……けどもし良くならないなら、僕にちゃんと知らせなきゃだめだよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2570
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ee2a94dd:

    # nk "Don't push yourself too much - and of course if you have any chest pains, come to me immediately, right?"
    nk "あまり無理をしないように――それと当然だけど胸に痛みを感じたら、すぐに僕のところに来ること、いいね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2572
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_02e0e06d:

    # "I put my shirt back on, and the nurse leans out of the doorway to call in Emi."
    "俺はシャツを戻して、ナースは笑美を呼ぼうとドアから顔を出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2581
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_007cb285:

    # emi "What took you so long? Now I'm going to be late!"
    emi "なんでそんなに時間かかるの？　あたし遅れちゃうじゃない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2588
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_62817229:

    # "The nurse gives me a significant look."
    "ナースは俺に意味深な目線を送る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2593
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_d5a90131:

    # nk "I was just seducing Hisao, that's all."
    nk "久夫くんを誘惑してただけだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2600
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_1d85b742:

    # emi "What!? Come on, what have I told you about seducing my friends?"
    emi "なにそれ！？　ちょっと、あたしの友達に変なことしないでって言ったでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2602
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_bf536748:

    # "I'd expected Emi to be shocked by this, but instead she seems merely annoyed, scolding the nurse as if he were a child stealing cookies."
    "笑美はショックを受けるかと思ったけど、ただうんざりしただけみたいで、クッキーを盗んだ子供でも叱るようにナースを叱っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2604
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_8404c4ae:

    # "Meanwhile, I try hard not to blush at the nurse's innuendo."
    "こっちは、ナースが変なこと言うから顔を赤らめないように必死だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2609
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_179c726d:

    # nk "I'll try not to do it again, though I fear young Hisao may be lost to the female gender forever!"
    nk "もうしないようにするよ。でもあいにく、若い久夫くんは永遠に女の子に興味をなくしちゃってるかもね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2613
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_2410c10b:

    # hi "Not freaking likely."
    hi "そんなわけないだろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2623
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_6b91b539:

    # "I didn't mean to say that out loud, but both the nurse and Emi regard me for a moment before bursting into laughter again."
    "大声で言うつもりはなかったけど、ナースも笑美も俺をちょっと見つめると、また爆笑し始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2628
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_fec5d999:

    # emi "Told you he was funny, didn't I?"
    emi "ね、彼面白いって言ったでしょ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2630
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_43725057:

    # "Huh. I guess Emi does talk to the nurse about a lot of stuff."
    "へえ。笑美がナースにいろいろ話しているってのは本当なんだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2636
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_c3046345:

    # nk "Well Hisao, you should probably get moving. You still need a shower before class starts, don't you?"
    nk "ところで久夫くん、そろそろ行った方がいいんじゃないかな。授業に出る前にシャワー浴びなきゃならないだろう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2638
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b5173a80:

    # "Crap! He's got a point, and it looks like I've only got a half hour!"
    "くそ！　ナースの言う通り、あと３０分しかないじゃないか！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2640
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_b91a3027:

    # hi "Thanks for your time. I'll see you later, Emi!"
    hi "ありがとうございました。あとでな、笑美！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2647
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ef6e7075:

    # "I dash out of the room as the nurse begins to remove Emi's prosthetics."
    "ナースが笑美の義足を外し始めたところで俺は医務室から飛び出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2649
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_dade5872:

    # "As I head down the hallway, I can just barely hear his voice drifting after me."
    "玄関へ向かう時、後ろからナースの声がかろうじて聞こえる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2651
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_489805b2:

    # nk "Emi, you've got to be more careful…"
    nk "笑美ちゃん、もっと気をつけないと……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2656
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_9a858a05:

    # "I make it back to my room and shower in record time. It occurs to me that I've already been up for four hours, and class hasn't even started yet."
    "俺は、記録的な速さで部屋に戻ってシャワーを浴びる。ふと、もう４時間も起きているのに授業はまだ始まってもいないことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2658
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_f189038c:

    # "This is going to be a really, really long day."
    "今日は本当に、ほんとうに長い一日になるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2660
translate jp a2_emi_an_apple_a_day_ecd9e0b0:

    # "I hope I don't fall asleep in class."
    "授業中に居眠りしなければいいけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2678
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0ae872c0:

    # "The morning sunlight streaming through my window wakes me up instead of my alarm, and I realize that it must be Sunday."
    "目覚ましではなく、朝日の光が部屋の窓越しに俺を起こして、今日が日曜日だと気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2680
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8531645a:

    # "Emi has kindly deigned to give me weekends off from our morning runs."
    "週末の朝練は、親切にも笑美が休みにしてくれた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2682
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_17743adc:

    # "I don't actually know if I woke up at all yesterday, or if I just slept through the entire day."
    "自分が昨日一度でも起きたのか、それともまる一日眠りっぱなしだったのか、よくわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2684
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b3acc230:

    # "My legs groan in protest as I lever myself out of bed."
    "ベッドからやっと出ると、抗議するかのように脚がきしむ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2686
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0b87aba1:

    # "All this running has really taken it out of me."
    "この朝練はほんとうに疲れる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2688
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0f6899b8:

    # "Still, I can't deny that Emi wasn't lying to me."
    "けど、笑美の言っていることは嘘じゃなかった。それは否定できない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2690
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_fef2121e:

    # "It has gotten a little easier."
    "すこし楽になってきている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2692
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c47a7bdb:

    # "I'd been worried that the runs would start to wear on my nerves, but thus far I haven't minded them that much."
    "毎朝これではイライラしてくるんじゃないかと心配していたけど、でも今のところはそれほど気になっていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2694
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3da050e9:

    # "Well, it's only been a week."
    "まあ、まだほんの一週間だけだしな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2696
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_be08b7e2:

    # "I suppose there's plenty of time for me to start dreading the sound of my alarm in the morning."
    "うっとうしい朝の目覚まし時計の音が鳴り出すまで、まだたっぷり時間があるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2698
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_20bea67e:

    # "Not that I could ever skip out now."
    "もっとも、今さらやめられるはずもないけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2700
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4b3b6031:

    # "As Emi said, it's harder to stop a routine when there's another person."
    "笑美が言ったように、他の人間がいるほうが、一度始めたことを続けやすい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2702
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ae26a29f:

    # "And frankly, I don't think I'm equipped to deal with a disappointed Emi."
    "それに、言ってしまえば、がっかりした笑美を相手にする覚悟はできていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2704
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d2cc60bd:

    # "She'd probably give me those puppy-dog eyes and I'd feel terrible about myself."
    "たぶん笑美はあの子犬みたいな目で俺を見つめてきて、俺はひどい自己嫌悪におそわれるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2706
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b240465b:

    # "Which reminds me… wasn't I supposed to be somewhere today?"
    "そういえば……俺は今日どこかに行くんじゃなかったっけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2715
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2ef6dfe6:

    # emi "Hey, you're coming to my track meet on Sunday, right?"
    emi "ねえ、日曜日の陸上競技会、来るんだよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2720
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_02dc098f:

    # emi "What am I talking about, of course you are."
    emi "何言ってるんだろあたし、来るに決まってるよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2725
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e3466ecf:

    # emi "Right?"
    emi "そうだよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2727
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_5dab419c:

    # "Those puppy-dog eyes again."
    "また子犬の目。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2729
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2d3068e7:

    # hi "Of course I'm going!"
    hi "もちろん行くって！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2731
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_93ddc742:

    # hi "I owe you, right?"
    hi "笑美にはずいぶん世話になってるし、だろ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2736
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_172c8033:

    # emi "Exactly! So don't forget, okay?"
    emi "そうよ！　だから忘れないで、いい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2743
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_042c0a68:

    # "Crap, Emi's track meet!"
    "くそ、笑美の大会だ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2745
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ea7ea6d1:

    # "I'd better get a move on if I don't want to miss her running, since she's the only reason I'm even considering going."
    "笑美が走るのを見逃したくないならさっさと行かないと。そもそも笑美がいなきゃ行く理由なんてないんだから。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2747
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_249ec248:

    # "Otherwise, it would defeat the whole purpose of going."
    "笑美がいないんじゃ、行く目的がなくなってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2755
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2ab2d277:

    # "And so, I soon find myself quite suddenly surrounded by a crowd of people, all turning out to see our track team compete with another school like this one."
    "かくしてその直後、俺はうちの陸上部と他校のチームとの試合を見に来ている大勢の人に囲まれている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2760
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2764
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0fd7c9e8:

    # n "{vspace=30}I'll admit it, it's almost comforting to know we're not the only school like this."
    n "白状すると、ここ以外にも同じような学校があるのを知って安心した。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2766
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6e6ad5e6:

    # n "After you see that there can be {b}two{/b} schools with a bunch of… defective kids, well."
    n "生徒……まあ、障害児だ、そういう生徒がたくさんいる学校が{b}２つ{/b}もあるなんて知ったら。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2768
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_71e784de:

    # n "…You stop feeling so defective."
    n "……自分が不良品だという気がしなくなる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2770
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a4613cce:

    # n "You also stop feeling unique, which in most cases would be a bad thing, but in this case it sure as hell isn't."
    n "それに、自分が特別だという感覚もなくなる。普通ならそれは良くないことだけど、今回みたいな場合はマジで最高だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2772
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6b20a779:

    # n "That's part of Yamaku's appeal, I guess."
    n "それが山久学園の売りの一つなんだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2774
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b5139394:

    # n "Learn that you're not unique - hell, learn there's a lot of others who would kill to be saddled with your problem instead of whatever they're dealing with."
    n "自分が特別ではないと知る――今自分が苦しんでいるものと取り替えられるなら、他人の障害を抱え込むこともいとわない、そんなやつが山ほどいることを思い知る、ってことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2776
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_766cf5bb:

    # n "Some of the kids here aren't here because they're missing a leg or they have a heart condition."
    n "足がないとか心臓が悪いとかの理由でここにいるわけではない生徒もいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2778
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_39f93d3b:

    # n "Some of them might be here because they're as good as dead in two, maybe three years if they're lucky."
    n "中には、あと２年、運がよくても３年で死んでしまうからここに来ている生徒だっているかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2780
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_93679835:

    # n "And that's only if they get the right sort of care."
    n "そしてそれも正しいケアを受けられればの話だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2782
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b3a290a2:

    # n "It's a bitter sort of comfort to be able to say 'Well, at least I've got a chance of being alive through college,' but there it is."
    n "『まあ、少なくとも俺は大学卒業までは生き延びられそうだ』と言えてしまうのもなんだか苦々しい慰めだけれど、そういうことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2787
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2793
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1815f73c:

    # "I'm brought out of my rather morbid musings by the appearance of Rin near the entrance to the bleachers."
    "観客席の入口近くに琳が現れて、俺は少々陰気な物思いから現実に引き戻された。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2798
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8e24cda9:

    # rin "You came."
    rin "来たんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2800
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_128022b9:

    # hi "Of course. I said I would, didn't I?"
    hi "当然。行くって言ったよな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2805
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_909aa193:

    # rin "That doesn't necessarily imply that you had to follow through."
    rin "だからって、必ずそうしなきゃいけないとは限らないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2810
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ad62fba4:

    # rin "Lots of people say things and don't mean them."
    rin "思ってもいないことを言う人、いっぱいいるから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2812
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_fb2dd3f8:

    # hi "Well, I don't."
    hi "いや、俺は言わないぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2819
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6507a2c2:

    # "Rin shrugs. Seemingly bored with our conversation, she turns on her heel and heads back toward the stands."
    "琳は肩をすくめる。話をするのに飽きたみたいで、きびすを返して観覧席のほうへ戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2821
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_faed3f0b:

    # rin "I owe Emi money now."
    rin "笑美に借りができちゃった"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2823
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e2ba6edd:

    # hi "Why's that?"
    hi "なんでだよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2828
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_196a8af9:

    # rin "I didn't think you'd show up."
    rin "来ると思わなかったから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2830
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_488e3bc3:

    # rin "Emi did."
    rin "笑美は思ってたけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2835
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_817f336c:

    # rin "So I owe her 500 yen."
    rin "で、笑美に５００円借りってわけ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2837
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_57ba34b5:

    # hi "You two bet an awful lot, don't you?"
    hi "お前ら、しょっちゅう賭けてないか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2839
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9629d0c2:

    # "Another shrug from my armless companion."
    "腕のない連れは、また肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2844
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9b000ac9:

    # rin "I don't think so."
    rin "そんなことないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2851
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6f256d6f:

    # "We enter the bleachers, and Rin nods upwards."
    "観覧席に入ると、琳はあごで上のほうを指す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2856
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7662434f:

    # rin "Up there."
    rin "あそこ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2861
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_40a2c283:

    # rin "I came out to see if you'd come."
    rin "私、君が来るかどうか確かめに来たんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2863
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_18cb290c:

    # "For the bet, I presume."
    "賭けのため、だろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2865
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3f0787e5:

    # "Rin leads the way, and soon we've settled down on an almost-empty bench."
    "琳に連れられて、俺たちはほとんど空っぽのベンチに腰を下ろす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2881
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7a6f9b84:

    # "There's an older woman sitting next to Rin - someone's mother, I assume."
    "年上の女の人が琳の隣に座っている――誰かのお母さん、だろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2883
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2e0de5c3:

    # "She's got rather long hair done up in a braid. On seeing Rin, she gives her an oddly familiar-seeming grin."
    "その人はいくぶん長い髪を三つ編みにまとめている。琳を見て、妙に見覚えのある感じで笑いかける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2888
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_283b7902:

    # emm_ "Well, this is surprising."
    emm_ "まあ、驚いた"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2893
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8c864ddc:

    # emm_ "I thought you went to get a snack, not a boy."
    emm_ "てっきりおやつでも探しに行ったのかと思ったら、男の子と帰ってくるなんて"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2895
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2900
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_907e156b:

    # rin "A snack?"
    rin "おやつ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2905
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7c36f392:

    # rin "I wondered why I was down there."
    rin "なんで下の方にいたのか不思議だったんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2911
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b914c422:

    # "The woman laughs, again in a way that seems familiar."
    "その人は笑う。またあの感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2913
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e46e7cb4:

    # "Where have I seen her before?"
    "この人にどっかで会ったことあったかなあ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2918
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_61b02c3e:

    # emm_ "Well, I suppose you've always been one to go out for one thing and bring back another."
    emm_ "そうねえ、あなたっていつもなにかを取ってくるって言って出かけて、別のものを持って帰ってくる子だから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2920
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ff7e3f96:

    # emm_ "But I'm being rude! I haven't introduced myself."
    emm_ "って、やだ！　私、自己紹介もしてないじゃない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2922
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_745695d4:

    # emm_ "I'm Meiko Ibarazaki, Emi's mother."
    emm_ "茨崎芽衣子です、笑美の母です"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2927
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d482a825:

    # emm "Pleased to meet you."
    emm "よろしくね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2929
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3806c202:

    # "Well, that explains it."
    "ああ、それでか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2931
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4ad57b2c:

    # "She's like a taller, older and better endowed Emi."
    "芽衣子さんは、背が高くて年上でよりスタイルがいい笑美みたいな感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2933
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1304efe8:

    # "Apart from her hair being a darker shade than Emi's, there's really no mistaking the resemblance."
    "笑美よりも濃い色合いの髪を別にすれば、本当によく似ている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2939
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_37f76da9:

    # hi "Sorry, I'm Hisao. Hisao Nakai."
    hi "すみません、久夫です。中井久夫です"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2941
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_430b70b4:

    # hi "And really, you don't have to apologize for not introducing yourself, Mrs. Ibarazaki."
    hi "それと、自己紹介しなかったのを謝ることないですよ、茨崎さん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2943
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1ae3d4e3:

    # hi "That's really Rin's job in this situation, isn't it?"
    hi "本当は琳が紹介するところ、ですよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2949
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_abe5fff5:

    # "Another laugh from Emi's mother."
    "笑美のお母さんが笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2951
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_77566830:

    # emm "I take it you've not known Rin for that long, then."
    emm "琳ちゃんと知り合ってそんなに経ってないみたいね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2956
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_bc4d77bd:

    # emm "It's best not to expect her to remember something like that."
    emm "琳ちゃんがそういうことを思い出すなんて期待しない方がいいわ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2961
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_59905f29:

    # emm "She's got other things to think about, I assume."
    emm "多分だけど、琳ちゃんはもっと他に考えることがあるのよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2966
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_42fb76ba:

    # "Rin nods, seeming pleased by this assessment."
    "琳はうなずく。この評価に喜んでいるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2971
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7b3561e6:

    # rin "She's right."
    rin "正解だね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2976
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_226e36e9:

    # rin "I was thinking about sunsets."
    rin "夕暮れについて考えてたんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2982
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_fb0bc169:

    # emm "You see? It's really up to us to make introductions and the like."
    emm "ね？　自己紹介みたいなことは私たちでやるべきなのよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2984
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_5f17d9f6:

    # "For lack of any better response, I nod."
    "他にいい反応もないので、とりあえずうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2986
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3579207f:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki leans back a little on her seat and raises an eyebrow."
    "笑美のお母さんは、席の上ですこし体を反らして、眉を吊り上げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2995
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3bf3d415:

    # emm "So, how long have you and Rin been dating?"
    emm "それで、いつから２人はお付き合いしてるのかしら？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:2997
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_873079cb:

    # "My response consists of silence as my brain suddenly lurches into gear. But just before I can begin to utter a hastily babbled explanation, Emi's mother bursts into laughter again."
    "いきなり調子を狂わされて何も言えなくなる。でも、俺があわててべらべらと説明し始める前に、芽衣子さんはまたドッと笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3005
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_35442e7c:

    # emm "Ha! You're a blusher, aren't you?"
    emm "あはは！　久夫くん、すぐ赤くなるほうなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3007
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_14a3feb0:

    # "I don't know if there's any way to keep my dignity in this situation, so I settle for a mumbled response."
    "この状況でどうやったら自分の尊厳を保てるのかわからなくて、とりあえずブツブツ言うことにする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3013
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_da9749d8:

    # hi "Maybe."
    hi "かもな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3018
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ca5b56c3:

    # emm "So this must be a new romance then, mustn't it?"
    emm "なら、新しいロマンスってことなのね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3023
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e70ce690:

    # hi "Wait, that's not the question that—"
    hi "待ってくださいよ、それは質問じゃなく――"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3029
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1ae37bd5:

    # "Another laugh."
    "また笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3034
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4565795e:

    # emm "I know, but it's funny to watch you squirm."
    emm "わかってるわ。でもあなたがもじもじしてるところを見るの、面白くて"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3039
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2fbc3b45:

    # emm "I'm sorry. Forgive an old woman her amusements."
    emm "ごめんなさいね。おばさんの楽しみなの、許してちょうだい"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3041
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d567d04b:

    # "Old woman?"
    "おばさん？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3043
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ef81889d:

    # "She sure doesn't look that old to me."
    "ぜんぜんそうは見えないけどなあ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3045
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_cd154af5:

    # "Clearly Emi gets her youthful features from her mother."
    "笑美の元気なところは明らかにお母さんゆずりだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3050
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_928dae43:

    # hi "I suppose I can let it go."
    hi "別に気にしてませんよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3056
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_f2fcf1c8:

    # emm "How kind of you."
    emm "ありがとう"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3063
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_34cc1882:

    # rin "It's starting."
    rin "始まるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3072
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_fdd4654b:

    # "I direct my attention to the track, where they're preparing for the first sprint."
    "トラックに目をやると、選手たちが最初の短距離走に備えている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3074
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_214fba4d:

    # "It looks like the 400 meter dash."
    "４００メートル走みたいだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3076
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ad8eb1ef:

    # "My eyes scan the runners, before finding Emi."
    "笑美を探す前に、ランナーたちを見渡す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3081
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_33e08575:

    # "She's smiling, with an almost cocky look on her face."
    "笑美はほとんど自信過剰なくらいの笑顔を浮かべている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3089
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_356375bd:

    # "The starter raises his pistol."
    "スターターがピストルをかかげる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3101
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_62075404:

    # "Emi explodes off the block, disappearing from the starting line in a blur."
    "笑美はスターティングブロックから飛び出すと、残像を残してスタートラインから消える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3103
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_94fa712c:

    # "It's amazing. Even as the other sprinters converge on the lanes closest to the inside line, Emi surges to the front of the pack."
    "すごい。他の選手がレーンの内側ぎりぎりを走っているときでも、笑美は先頭へと躍り出る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3105
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_5386ef75:

    # "By the time she rounds the final turn, some of the other runners have caught up with her."
    "最後のコーナーを曲がるころになって、何人かのランナーが笑美に追いつく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3107
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7327cf79:

    # "Their efforts come to naught though, since a final burst of speed from Emi leaves them at least a half second behind."
    "しかしその努力は無駄に終わる。笑美の爆発的なラストスパートで、他の選手は少なくとも０．５秒は離される。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3119
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9647ba32:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki whoops and shouts, applauding wildly, and generally looking like any other parent cheering on their child."
    "芽衣子さんはきゃあきゃあ叫んで拍手喝采する。子供を応援する他の普通の親みたいに。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3121
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_42d67943:

    # "Emi bounds off the track, looking pleased with herself."
    "笑美はトラックから跳び出る。自分に満足したみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3130
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_927c7898:

    # "I cheer right along with the rest of them."
    "俺もみんなといっしょに喝采を続ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3132
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_f5f2273f:

    # "The announcer (sounding suspiciously like Misha) gleefully gives the results."
    "アナウンサー（どうもミーシャのように聞こえる）が大喜びで結果を伝える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3138
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_49aa6f79:

    # emm "I think she's gotten faster since the last time."
    emm "この前より速くなったと思うわ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3143
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7a658918:

    # hi "That was incredible."
    hi "すごかったですね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3149
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6e0f28f0:

    # "Mrs. Ibarazaki grins proudly."
    "芽衣子さんは誇らしげに笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3151
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_24acd1f9:

    # emm "Emi's a heck of a runner."
    emm "笑美はすごいランナーなのよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3156
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b6ee50d3:

    # "We fall silent as the next event is being prepared."
    "次の種目の準備が進むあいだ、俺たちは黙り込む。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3158
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b628005f:

    # "I'm surprised to see Emi striding out onto the track again."
    "笑美がまたトラックに大股で入っていくのを見て驚く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3163
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a262c76c:

    # hi "Wait, didn't she just run?"
    hi "え、いま走ったばっかりですよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3165
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e8c4686e:

    # "Emi's mother nods."
    "芽衣子さんはうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3170
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c130b458:

    # emm "Yes, but she runs multiple events for the team. Especially the sprints."
    emm "ええ、でも笑美はほかの種目も走るの。特に短距離走ね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3175
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c19ab472:

    # emm "It's a lot of running, but Emi can handle it."
    emm "いっぱい走ることになるけど、でもあの子なら大丈夫よ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3177
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6fcd9d17:

    # "From the looks of things, she's right."
    "様子を見てると、どうもその通りみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3179
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c4a6384b:

    # "Emi doesn't appear to be tired, as if she hadn't run the previous event at all."
    "笑美に疲れの気配は見えない。まるで前の競技にそもそも出ていなかったかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3181
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_64ea2cbf:

    # "If not for the sweat visible on her shirt, you'd never know."
    "もしシャツが汗ばんでいるのが見えなければ、気づきようもないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3186
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1bee6ed0:

    # hi "Which event is this?"
    hi "今度の競技は？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3192
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7d1676cf:

    # emm "It's the 200 meter dash."
    emm "２００メートル走ね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3194
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a9c47c5a:

    # emm "She'll do this one, the 100-meter, and the relay."
    emm "あと１００メートル走とリレーもやることになってるの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3199
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3207
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0de8c5d6:

    # "Once again the pistol sounds, and once again Emi flies off the block."
    "ピストルがもう一度鳴り響くと、笑美ももう一度スターティングブロックから飛び出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3209
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2417e5b8:

    # "A thumping sound draws my attention away from the race."
    "ドシンという音が俺の意識をレースから引き離す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3211
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ebb65b2c:

    # "It's Rin's foot."
    "琳の足だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3213
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_801e329d:

    # "She seems completely absorbed in the race."
    "琳はすっかりレースに夢中みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3221
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_f49b9658:

    # "Emi's mother cheers again, and I assume that the race is over."
    "芽衣子さんがまた声を上げ始めて、レースが終わったんだなと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3223
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_941ecf11:

    # "Sprints don't seem to me like they'd take very long to complete."
    "短距離走はそんなに長いこと走らないだろうし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3225
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c382c6c8:

    # hi "Your foot."
    hi "お前の足"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3231
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e9686c2a:

    # rin "Hmm?"
    rin "んー？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3233
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2cb216d6:

    # hi "Your foot was bouncing on the bleachers."
    hi "お前の足、席の上で跳ねてたぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3238
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8cf3c02d:

    # rin "Oh."
    rin "ああ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3240
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8e421606:

    # hi "You seem pretty into this stuff. I'm surprised."
    hi "なんだかのめり込んでるみたいだな。驚いたよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3245
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d2491b20:

    # "Rin looks at me quizzically."
    "琳はいぶかしげに俺を見る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3247
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6190fe41:

    # rin "Why wouldn't I be?"
    rin "そんなに変？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3249
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_dae65d75:

    # hi "No reason, I just thought stuff like sports wouldn't interest you."
    hi "別に。お前はスポーツなんかには興味がないと思ってたからさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3254
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_de550c0c:

    # rin "Hmm, I suppose you're right."
    rin "うーん、君の言う通りだね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3256
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_056a211c:

    # rin "It's not that interesting."
    rin "そんなに面白くはないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3261
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_555d1430:

    # rin "But I'm watching Emi, not the sport."
    rin "でも私は笑美を見てるから、競技じゃなくて"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3263
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ed15e901:

    # hi "I don't follow."
    hi "なんだそれ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3268
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_fe9a74c4:

    # rin "Emi's the most Emi when she runs."
    rin "笑美は走ってるときがいちばん笑美なんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3270
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9fcc19fb:

    # rin "You don't get to see Emi at her Emiest very often."
    rin "笑美が最笑美状態なのを見られるチャンスはそうそうないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3275
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3ae9d7f7:

    # rin "But here, you can. See?"
    rin "でもここなら見えるよ。ほらね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3277
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3fc268c5:

    # "She directs my attention toward the track again, where the 100-meter dash is about to start."
    "琳が俺の注意をもう一度、１００メートル走が始まろうとしているトラックのほうに向ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3285
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4b886958:

    # "I watch Emi closely."
    "俺は笑美をしっかりと見る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3287
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_befbd79a:

    # "As she gets onto the starter blocks, her whole body seems to relax, but it's a false relaxation."
    "スターティングブロックに乗りかかると、体全体がリラックスしているように見えるけど、それは見せかけのリラックス状態だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3289
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_dedaa01b:

    # "I can see that she's actually like a coiled spring."
    "笑美の体が本当にバネのように見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3294
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2ed0b4eb:

    # "As the starter tells everyone to get set, her head snaps up, and her eyes narrow slightly."
    "スターターが位置につくよう声をかけると、頭がピシッと上がり、目はほんの少し細くなる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3296
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1ab7f00a:

    # "Her mouth curls upward in what could be a grin and could be a growl."
    "口が上向きに曲がり、笑いとも唸りともとれそうな形になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3306
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3dbe4dc8:

    # "When the pistol goes off, it's as if she's been unleashed from a cage, like she was always moving at this blinding speed, but we couldn't see it happening until the starter's pistol dispelled the illusion of motionlessness."
    "ピストルが鳴り響いたとき、笑美は檻から解き放たれたかのように、常にこんな目にも止まらぬ速さで動いていたかのように走り出す。 でも、すべてが静止していたかのような錯覚をスターターのピストルが吹き飛ばすまで、俺たちにはそれがわからなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3308
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d842224f:

    # "It's all over in a few seconds, but in those few seconds I feel like I just witnessed something very personal for Emi."
    "それは数秒で終わったけど、その数秒のあいだに、俺はすごく個人的ななにかを笑美に見た気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3313
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_684ddac6:

    # "As soon as she crossed the finish line, the fierce look was replaced by her normal grin."
    "笑美がゴールラインを横切るやいなや、いつもの笑顔が険しい表情にとって代わる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3315
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e0805e23:

    # "The conquering general returning to his farm."
    "一仕事終えて、普段の姿に戻ったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3317
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6ca17858:

    # hi "Amazing."
    hi "すごいです"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3319
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c7970656:

    # hi "She's really amazing. I've never seen anyone move that fast."
    hi "ほんとにすごい。あんなに速く走る人は見たことないですよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3326
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e245860a:

    # emm "Well, don't look at me, I'm far too relaxed to run that fast."
    emm "あら、私を見られてもなあ。私はあんなに速く走るにはのんびりしすぎてるから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3332
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_5a6f12a2:

    # emm "No, I think Emi's prowess all came from her father's side."
    emm "ううん、笑美の才能はみんな父親から受け継いだんだと思う"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3334
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3a556b49:

    # "At the mention of Emi's father, Mrs. Ibarazaki looks wistful, almost sad."
    "笑美の父親の話になると、芽衣子さんは寂しげな、悲しそうな顔をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3336
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3c9c175b:

    # emm "He got her into running, you know."
    emm "彼が笑美にランニングを教え込んだのよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3341
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6dc6f21e:

    # hi "Yeah, she told me."
    hi "ええ、笑美がそう言ってました"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3343
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d98d30de:

    # "I'm uncertain as to whether or not it would be rude of me to ask after Emi's father."
    "笑美の父親についてたずねるのが失礼にあたるかどうか、俺は判断しきれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3345
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8d484ca9:

    # "But after that look on her face a few days ago, I feel compelled to ask."
    "でも、数日前の笑美の顔を見たあとだと、聞かざるを得ない感じがする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3347
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_47fb97a9:

    # hi "Where is her father now, if I might ask?"
    hi "聞いてもよければですけど、お父さんはいまどちらに？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3349
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_85839e43:

    # "Emi's mother hesitates, clearly not willing to answer the question but at the same time not wishing to appear rude."
    "明らかに質問に答える気はないけど同時に失礼になるのも避けたいようで、芽衣子さんは口ごもる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3355
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1954442b:

    # emm "He… isn't around any more."
    emm "お父さんは……もういないの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3357
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d185323f:

    # hi "I'm sorry, I didn't mean to bring up bad memories."
    hi "すみません、嫌なことを思い出させるつもりはなかったんですけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3362
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ff763c3d:

    # hi "Emi just seemed a little sad when she mentioned him earlier."
    hi "前に笑美がお父さんのことを話してたとき、なんだか悲しそうにしてたから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3368
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_16e971c2:

    # emm "That's not surprising, considering."
    emm "そうね、そうでしょうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3370
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3372
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6e166686:

    # emm "They were very close."
    emm "とっても仲がよかったから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3377
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e1f8a5e6_1:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3381
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_cfc64809:

    # "A beeping noise suddenly emanates from Mrs. Ibarazaki's pocket. Reaching into it, she pulls out a cell phone and looks at it."
    "突然、芽衣子さんのポケットから電子音が鳴り出す。芽衣子さんはポケットに手を突っ込むと、携帯電話を取り出して一瞥する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3387
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_11150d81:

    # emm "…Honestly, text messages?"
    emm "……メールだなんて、何考えてるのよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3389
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9884910a:

    # emm "What is he, sixteen?"
    emm "高校生じゃあるまいし、もう"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3391
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_34d1d59d_1:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3396
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_bdc861ba:

    # emm "Oh, nothing."
    emm "ううん、なんでも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3401
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8a9af1ea:

    # emm "I've got to go meet up with a friend of mine."
    emm "友達と会わなきゃいけなくなっちゃったの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3406
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1f7c4f4c:

    # emm "Will you tell Emi I'm very proud of her and that I'll call her later tonight?"
    emm "笑美に、母さんがよくやったわって言ってたって、それと夜になったら電話するって、伝えてもらえるかしら？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3411
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2f6a93ba:

    # hi "Of course."
    hi "ええ、もちろん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3425
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_622d1442:

    # "I'll admit that I zone out for a while."
    "しばらくぼうっとしてたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3427
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_32fb0deb:

    # "I almost don't notice that the relay's about to begin. But when I look, I can't find Emi."
    "もうすぐリレーが始まるのを見逃すところだった。でも、トラックを見ても笑美の姿が見つからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3429
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_744d1d12:

    # hi "I thought that Emi would be running the relay."
    hi "笑美、リレーにも出るんだと思ってたけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3434
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ad0eb544:

    # rin "She runs anchor."
    rin "笑美はアンカーだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3439
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_df65623e:

    # rin "So she won't be running for a while yet."
    rin "だからまだしばらくは走らないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3441
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9a287fc4:

    # hi "Ah."
    hi "ああ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3446
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4f0bbe13:

    # rin "Did you see it?"
    rin "見た？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3448
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0f638bea_1:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3450
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_cd582b13:

    # rin "Emi at her Emiest."
    rin "最笑美な笑美"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3452
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_da9749d8_1:

    # hi "Maybe."
    hi "かもな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3457
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_720de3d4:

    # rin "Hmm. Maybe this time."
    rin "ふーん。次はきっと見られるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3461
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_f4815bcf:

    # "The race begins, and I cheer Emi's teammates along as they pass the baton."
    "レースが始まって、笑美のチームメイトがバトンを渡されるたびに俺は声を張り上げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3470
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b4db896e:

    # "Finally, I see Emi sprinting onto the track to take the final handoff."
    "いよいよ、最後のバトンを繋ぐ笑美がトラックを走るのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3472
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8a1384d5:

    # "Once again I'm taken aback by how graceful she looks when she runs."
    "またも、笑美が走るときの優雅な姿に心を奪われる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3474
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9dc6b057:

    # "It really is beautiful."
    "本当にきれいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3476
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c5959e99:

    # "The look of determination and fearlessness on her face only adds to the picture."
    "決意を固めた、なにものをも恐れないような表情が、ただただその美しさを高めていく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3478
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_eba05354:

    # "Emi at her Emiest, I suppose."
    "最笑美状態、なんだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3486
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9831e727:

    # "But then, as she crosses the finish line, I see her stumble slightly."
    "でもその時、笑美がゴールラインを横切る瞬間、少しよろめくのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3488
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_68a864f6:

    # "It's only barely, but it's a definite stumble."
    "ほんの少しだけど、でも確かによろめく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3496
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2c15b4e9:

    # "Rin inhales sharply, and actually looks concerned for a second."
    "琳は鋭く息を吸い込むと、一瞬、本当に心配したような様子を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3498
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e66078ab:

    # rin "Aw, Emi…"
    rin "あれ、笑美……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3500
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_38570eb3:

    # hi "Did she hurt herself, do you think?"
    hi "どこか痛めたんじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3505
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_bf088471:

    # rin "You noticed it too?"
    rin "君も気づいた？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3510
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_af7ffe6f:

    # rin "It must be bad."
    rin "あれはまずいよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3515
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3032e35c:

    # "She frowns, as if deciding on the next course of action."
    "次にどうするかを決めているかのように、琳は眉をひそめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3517
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a3651292:

    # "Eventually that proves to be too tiresome, and she shrugs again."
    "結局はそれにうんざりして、琳はまた肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3522
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0db301bd:

    # rin "Well, let's go down."
    rin "それじゃ、降りようか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3524
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_da48fab6:

    # rin "Gotta crown the victor."
    rin "勝者に冠を授与しないとね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3529
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8ece8966:

    # rin "See if you can find a laurel branch."
    rin "月桂樹の枝、探してきてよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3531
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_14d0d891:

    # hi "That's not going to be easy."
    hi "そりゃ簡単にはいかないぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3536
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4387f3ee:

    # "Rin shrugs."
    "琳は肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3541
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_75256cce:

    # rin "At least we tried."
    rin "少なくとも探そうとはしたよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3543
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ff58ccb4:

    # "Well, we didn't really try all that hard."
    "まあ、それほど真面目にはやらなかったけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3545
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_853d2b6d:

    # "Or at all. But hey, whatever."
    "というより全然。でも、どうでもいいか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3556
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a3fc7fb8:

    # "Emi is surrounded by her teammates, all of them congratulating her on the run."
    "笑美はチームメイトに囲まれている。みんな笑美の走りを祝っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3558
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b8995621:

    # "Rin seems to be waiting for Emi to notice that she's arrived."
    "琳は、自分が来ていることに笑美が気づくのを待っているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3560
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c5897460:

    # "Oh yeah, I guess she can't exactly wave Emi over."
    "ああそうか、琳は笑美に手を振ってやることができないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3562
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_de08b7fc:

    # "Then again, I'm not sure that Rin would do such a thing even if she had arms."
    "それに、もし腕があっても、そんなことをしたかどうか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3564
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1bea275d:

    # "It doesn't seem her style to draw attention to herself. Or to emote beyond shrugging."
    "誰かの注意を引く、というのは琳の流儀じゃないように思う。肩をすくめる以上の感情表現もそうだけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3566
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a51f2471:

    # "Either way, I'm not willing to wait, so I wave to Emi, who looks up and grins happily at me - er, us."
    "どっちにしろ待ってやるつもりはない。俺が手を振ると、笑美は顔を上げて俺に、いや、俺たちに微笑みかける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3578
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_69687d3f:

    # emi "Hey, you showed up!"
    emi "来てくれたんだ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3583
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a9e97cf6:

    # emi "Guess Rin owes me money, huh?"
    emi "これで琳には貸しができたよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3588
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_962c8615:

    # rin "We would have brought you a crown of laurels, but Hisao didn't find one."
    rin "月桂樹の冠をあげようと思ってたんだけど、久夫が探してくれなくってさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3593
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_57f0895e:

    # hi "Hey, neither did you."
    hi "おい、お前もだろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3598
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_68d3c7a6:

    # rin "It wasn't my job to look."
    rin "探すのは私の役目じゃないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3600
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_478e7a49:

    # hi "When did we assign jobs?"
    hi "いつそんなこと決めたんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3605
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_51225eda:

    # rin "When I said 'See if you can find a laurel branch.'"
    rin "『月桂樹の枝、探してきてよ』って言ったとき"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3610
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_f73cd465:

    # rin "Try to keep up."
    rin "ちゃんと聞いてなよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3612
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_86af4c08:

    # "I shrug. Guess Rin's rubbing off on me."
    "俺は肩をすくめる。琳のくせがうつったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3614
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_202ec59f:

    # hi "Seems it's my fault after all, Emi."
    hi "やっぱり俺のせいみたいだ、笑美"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3620
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4e83c593:

    # "Emi laughs at Rin and me."
    "笑美は俺と琳を笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3625
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_2beaa6fc:

    # emi "It's okay, I'm sure you'll make it up to me somehow."
    emi "大丈夫だよ、きっとほかのことで埋め合わせしてくれるよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3630
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_5a036de1:

    # hi "Uh, sure."
    hi "あー、もちろん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3636
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a579d2cf:

    # emi "Good! So, how'd I look?"
    emi "よし！　で、あたし、どうだった？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3641
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3ff78a0b:

    # "I stop myself from blurting out 'beautiful' or 'amazing' and settle for the substantially safer 'very impressive.'"
    "俺は『きれいだ』とか『すげえ』なんてことを口走らないようにして、もっと差し障りのない『すごく良かった』という表現に落ち着く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3646
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7699e576:

    # "Emi seems pleased with this assessment."
    "笑美はこの評価に喜んだみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3648
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9472d192:

    # "I don't mention how much more impressive her performance is given her lack of legs. I figure she knows that already."
    "脚がないおかげで、その走りがはるかにカッコよく見えたことには触れないでおく。笑美にはもうわかってるはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3650
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_edfe4477:

    # "Besides, it seems like it would take away from her efforts, somehow."
    "それに、どうもそれを言うのは笑美の努力をだいなしにしてしまうような気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3656
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6e7e5131:

    # emi "Great to hear! I was worried that I looked a little slow on the relay, but I guess I did fine, huh?"
    emi "よかった！　リレーで少し遅くなっちゃったかなって心配したけど、あたし頑張ったでしょ、ね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3661
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c997b75e:

    # hi "Actually, I noticed—{w=.4}{nw}"
    hi "あのさ、俺、気づいたんだけど――{w=.4}{nw}"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3668
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_fe1e4a5e:

    # "Rin kicks me and keeps me from finishing my sentence."
    "言い終わる前に、琳が俺を蹴飛ばして制止する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3673
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d5845e4d:

    # emi "What was that all about?"
    emi "なんのこと？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3678
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_27bbeb35:

    # rin "He noticed it. At the end."
    rin "気づいたんだって。終わりのとこ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3683
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0ed1fabc:

    # emi "Hmm, that's no good."
    emi "ああ、それは良くないなあ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3688
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c64d3b7a:

    # emi "Guess the nurse will look at it for me later."
    emi "あとでナースくんが診てくれるよ、きっと"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3696
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_321792a3:

    # "There's a carelessness in her voice, as if it isn't a big deal, but I suddenly notice a slight twitch on her face."
    "なんでもないような気の抜けた声色だけど、俺はすぐにわずかな顔のけいれんに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3698
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8eda6a0e:

    # "Like she's trying to hide the fact that she's in pain."
    "本当は痛いのを隠そうとしているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3700
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d231356b:

    # "It's then that I notice her breathing is a little shallow, too."
    "それに息づかいが浅いことにも気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3702
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_b16f343b:

    # "I guess she really is hurt."
    "本当に痛いんだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3704
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8fb5a030:

    # "She must notice my concern, because she skips up to me and gives me a friendly pat on the shoulder."
    "笑美はスキップしてこちらに近寄り、気さくな感じで肩を叩く。俺が心配しているのに気づいているんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3710
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c23c81e3:

    # emi "Hey, you look a little worried!"
    emi "ねえ、なんか心配そうだね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3715
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_21e25a75:

    # emi "I'm fine, really!"
    emi "平気だよ、ほんとに！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3717
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_1fe2c3ba:

    # emi "Just sore from all the running, is all."
    emi "走りっぱなしで疲れちゃって、それだけ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3722
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8aeee8eb:

    # emi "And come on, a little pain isn't going to stop me."
    emi "それにほら、ちょっと痛いぐらいじゃあたしは止まらないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3724
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_3012bc85:

    # hi "Oh no?"
    hi "本当かよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3729
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d2836be6:

    # "Emi grins, and for a moment she looks like she did during her sprint, fierce and unconquerable."
    "笑美はにこりと笑うと、一瞬、短距離走のときのように、荒々しく誰にも打ち負かされないような様子を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3731
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7a0ce800:

    # "Or to put it another way, really beautiful."
    "言いかたを変えれば、ほんとにきれいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3736
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_07790361:

    # emi "Hasn't yet."
    emi "まだまだだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3738
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ae771e14:

    # hi "Well then. I guess I shouldn't worry, huh?"
    hi "まあそれなら、心配ない、だな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3743
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_7abf794a:

    # emi "Damn right! I'm Emi Ibarazaki, fastest thing on no legs! I don't stop for anything!"
    emi "そういうこと！　あたしは茨崎笑美、地上最速の足なきもの！　どんな時でも止まらない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3745
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_05823cbc:

    # hi "Impressive."
    hi "すげえや"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3750
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a4decc24:

    # "Emi giggles, and then seems to remember something."
    "笑美はくすくすと笑うと、なにかを思い出したようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3755
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_eb68f3c3:

    # emi "Oh, before I forget…"
    emi "そうだ、忘れないうちに……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3757
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c8698477:

    # emi "Rin and I are going to do something next Sunday as a post-track meet celebration!"
    emi "次の日曜日に琳とあたしとで、競技会の後のお祝いに何かしようと思ってるんだ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3762
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6fe2177a:

    # emi "You should come along!"
    emi "久夫くんもおいでよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3767
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_97fc141d:

    # emi "Normally we do it the day after, but since the track meet was on a Sunday, I've got homework and class and all that stuff to take care of."
    emi "いつもなら次の日にやるんだけどね、でも今日は日曜日でしょ。宿題とか、授業とか、やることがたくさんなの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3772
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_17ce21d4:

    # emi "Plus our morning run, of course."
    emi "プラス、朝練もね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3774
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e6d98932:

    # hi "Right, of course."
    hi "そうだな、もちろん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3776
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ce333f72:

    # hi "Oh, right. Your mom wanted to say she's proud of you."
    hi "あ、そうだ。お前のお母さんがよくやったって伝えてくれってさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3778
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_586c46c7:

    # hi "She'll call you later tonight."
    hi "夜遅くに電話するって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3783
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6b87640b:

    # emi "I thought I saw her in the stands!"
    emi "たしか客席にいるの、見たよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3788
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_169ce240:

    # emi "I'm glad she made it!"
    emi "来てくれてよかった！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3793
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ae6b1c2b:

    # emi "Used to be my dad who showed up to my meets, but Mom's done a pretty good job of taking over."
    emi "競技会にはいつもパパが来てくれてたんだけど、ママがうまくバトンタッチしてくれたんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3799
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_752c6e25:

    # "She shivers slightly, and I realize that she's still all sweaty."
    "笑美が少し震えて、俺は笑美がまだ汗をかいているのに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3801
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8fc3cff3:

    # "A breeze has started to blow, too."
    "軽く風も吹きはじめている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3803
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_815488d2:

    # "I'm not cold at all, and I've got my jacket with me, so without a word I throw it around her shoulders."
    "俺はぜんぜん寒くないし、上着があるので、黙って笑美の肩に上着をかけてやる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3815
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4ef47458:

    # "Emi jumps slightly and then grins at me."
    "笑美は少し驚いて、そして俺に笑いかける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3820
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9ab1c330:

    # emi "Hey, thanks!"
    emi "ありがと！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3825
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_e688ef3d:

    # emi "It's getting a little cold, I guess."
    emi "ちょっと寒くなってきたかな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3827
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_38e88afc:

    # hi "Yeah, looked like it."
    hi "ああ、みたいだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3829
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_328b4b99:

    # "Just as I begin to wonder whether or not giving Emi my jacket could be taken the wrong way, a boy in a track uniform approaches."
    "笑美に上着を貸してやったのは間違いだったんじゃないかと思いはじめると同時に、陸上のユニフォームを着た男子が近づいてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3831
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_46dd8a0c:

    # "Teammate" "Hey, Emi! You're going to miss the medal ceremony!"
    "チームメイト" "ねえ、笑美！　表彰式遅れちゃうよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3836
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8388fbc4:

    # emi "Oh yeah, thanks!"
    emi "あ、そうだった！　ありがと！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3842
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_617381f4:

    # "She turns to Rin and myself."
    "笑美は琳と俺に向きなおる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3844
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ee4af1d4:

    # emi "You don't have to stick around for this part. It takes forever."
    emi "終わるまで待ってなくてもいいからね。すごく長くなるから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3849
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_a870e1be:

    # emi "Besides, you should get cracking on your homework now if you don't want to be up late, Hisao."
    emi "それに、夜更かししたくなかったら、宿題は今すぐやっつけないとだめだよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3854
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8c433706:

    # emi "Morning run tomorrow! Don't forget!"
    emi "明日は朝練！　忘れないでね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3859
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6e315c48:

    # hi "How could I?"
    hi "どうやって忘れるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3865
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_d979fc34:

    # emi "Good point. I mean, it's spending time with {b}me{/b}, after all."
    emi "それもそうか。というか、結局{b}あたしと{/b}一緒に時間を過ごすってわけだしね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3881
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_9ed08ccb:

    # "With this, she waves quickly and dashes off to receive her medals, or whatever they pass off as a medal these days."
    "笑美はそう言いながら素早く手を振って、メダルを、あるいはメダルとして扱われているものを受け取りに走っていった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3890
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_18d0c56c:

    # "Rin and I head away from the track, Rin remaining deep in whatever thoughts she has for most of the walk back to her dorm."
    "俺と琳はトラックを離れる。寮に戻ってくるまで、琳はほとんどずっとなにか深い考えごとをしている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3892
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_18abd5bd:

    # "As I see her off, she speaks up."
    "俺が見送ると、琳は口を開く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3897
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_4307978d:

    # rin "You're probably not getting that coat back, I think."
    rin "上着、返してもらってなかったと思うけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3899
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_eaa0c1dd:

    # hi "I'm sure I'll get it back eventually."
    hi "もちろん、そのうち返してもらうよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3904
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ef346eb2:

    # rin "Interesting. Take it as it comes, huh?"
    rin "いいね。出たとこ勝負ってわけだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3909
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_46b8ecfa:

    # rin "Very Emi-ish."
    rin "すごく笑美的だね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3914
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c4e39d47:

    # "With this odd statement, she turns and heads into the building."
    "この奇妙な言葉とともに、琳は振り向いて建物に向かう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3916
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_480b1e32:

    # "Honestly, was it that big a deal?"
    "正直、そんなに大したことか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3918
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_0a363d04:

    # "Emi was cold and, unless I'm mistaken, in pain."
    "笑美は寒がっていたし、俺が間違ってなければ、痛みもあったはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3920
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_83ed3073:

    # "Giving her a solution to at least one of those problems seems like an obvious reaction."
    "そのうちの一つぐらいを解決してやるのは当然の反応だろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3922
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_31bcb3e8:

    # "Though I guess there is a chance I could lose my jacket if Emi never remembers to return it."
    "もっとも、笑美が返すのを忘れてれば、上着を失くす可能性はあるけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3924
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_6f55c046:

    # "I guess Rin has a point."
    "琳はいいところをついてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3926
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_25f6be0c:

    # "Still, I can't bring myself to muster much worry over the whole thing."
    "それでも、なにからなにまで心配するわけにもいかない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3928
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_8ef060f3:

    # "After all, it's been getting warmer lately."
    "だって、最近は暖かくなってきてるし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3930
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_c5518592:

    # "I don't need a jacket."
    "上着はなくてもいい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3932
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_bd9ef064:

    # "Odd. I think I used to be a little more responsible with my stuff."
    "変だな。前は自分のことはもう少しちゃんとしてたと思うけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3934
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_be4dc657:

    # "'Emi-ish,' huh?"
    "『笑美的』だって？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3936
translate jp a2_emi_track_meeting_ae06e3a1:

    # "Maybe that's not really a bad thing."
    "悪くないかもな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3953
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9104cbd5:

    # nk "You haven't been forgetting to take your medicine, have you?"
    nk "ここのところ薬は飲み忘れてないだろうね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3957
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_04e0a452:

    # nk "I'm catching a little murmur."
    nk "少し雑音が聞こえる"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3959
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4ef53a0f:

    # nk "You should take it easy for a few days."
    nk "数日は無理をしないほうがいいね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3961
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_cc7ec62e:

    # "The nurse's words hurt me far more than the exhaustion of the morning run ever could."
    "ナースの言葉が朝練の疲労なんかよりずっと深く胸に刺さる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3963
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bc525df4:

    # "Take it easy for a few days?"
    "数日は無理をしないほうがいい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3965
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c2e246e1:

    # "I knew I should have kept quiet."
    "やっぱり黙っておけばよかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3967
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ca97ba80:

    # "I keep my eyes on the floor, feeling like a complete idiot."
    "俺は床を見つめる。本当にバカみたいな気分だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3969
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3601906c:

    # "Of course I hadn't been remembering to take my medicine."
    "薬を飲むのなんて忘れてたに決まってるじゃないか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3971
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d62c8b16:

    # "I've been rushing out of my room to get to the track before Emi."
    "笑美より先に競技場に着くために、俺は毎朝大急ぎで部屋を出るようになっていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3973
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_52afa160:

    # "After the track meet a few days ago, I felt… inspired."
    "数日前の競技会が終わって、俺は……すごく刺激を受けた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3975
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_75f36723:

    # "So I've been running warm-up laps in the morning before Emi shows up."
    "それで俺は、笑美が来る前に何周か走ってウォーミングアップをしている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3977
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bcd24ee9:

    # "But then today while she and I were running, I felt a little pain in my chest."
    "でも今日いっしょに走っていたとき、胸に小さな痛みを感じた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3979
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_629e03df:

    # "It was only slight, and it was only for a second, so I mentioned it to the nurse."
    "本当に小さかったし、ほんの一瞬だけだったので、ナースにそれを伝えた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3981
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_55263bda:

    # hi "Honestly, it wasn't that bad."
    hi "ほんとに、ひどくはなかったです"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3983
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1840490b:

    # hi "I mean I kept running and finished just fine, so really it couldn't have been that bad…"
    hi "というか、走れてたし走り終わっても問題なくて、だからほんとにぜんぜんひどくはなくて……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3985
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_69dde4aa:

    # "Why do I feel like I'm making excuses to the nurse?"
    "ナースに言い訳をしているような気がするのはどうしてだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3987
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b632acc6:

    # "Moreover, why do I feel a need to justify continuing to run despite the pain?"
    "さらに、なんで俺は痛いにも関わらず走り続けるのを正当化しなきゃいけないと思ってるんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3989
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_97ba49af:

    # "Really, it comes down to my being unwilling to concern Emi, who seemed concerned anyway."
    "結局、俺は笑美を心配させたくないんだってことになる。とっくに心配してるみたいだけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3991
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_989bd887:

    # "I'm not sure how she was able to tell there was anything wrong, but she claims I stumbled a little."
    "なんで笑美が異常に気づいたのかわからないけど、俺が軽くよろけたと言っていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3993
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d89655cb:

    # "She's the one who insisted I tell the nurse, so now I feel bad for worrying her at all."
    "ナースにそれを伝えろと言い張ったのも笑美で、その笑美を結局は不安にさせてしまっていることが嫌だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3995
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_555fa8d9:

    # "The nurse is shaking his head ruefully while Emi paces outside the room."
    "医務室の外で笑美がうろうろしている間に、ナースは残念そうに首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3997
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ed5127e7:

    # nk "Hisao, I know it's difficult for you get into a new routine, but if you don't want to find yourself in a lot of trouble you're going to have to try harder."
    nk "久夫くん、新しい習慣を身につけるのが難しいのはわかるけど、あれこれ面倒なことになるのがいやならもっと努力しないとだめだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:3999
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_74a58e8f:

    # nk "You can't afford to forget your pills, and you can't push yourself too hard."
    nk "薬を飲むのも忘れちゃいけないし、頑張りすぎるのもいけない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4001
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6dcbe05c:

    # hi "But if I don't push myself, how will I improve?"
    hi "でも頑張らなかったら、どうやって上達するんですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4003
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ab68091c:

    # "I don't know where that came from."
    "どこからこんな言葉が出てきたのか、自分でもわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4005
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_dd54f9de:

    # "The nurse seems to have an idea."
    "ナースは見当がついているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4010
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_7b44c03f:

    # nk "Now where have I heard that before?"
    nk "あれ、どこかで聞いたような台詞だね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4015
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_fb56c34d:

    # "He laughs and pats me on the shoulder."
    "ナースは笑って俺の肩を叩く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4017
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e01c0d22:

    # nk "Ha! She's rubbing off on you, I guess."
    nk "はは！　あの子の性格がうつってるんだろうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4022
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_54a3ec30:

    # "His expression changes again, and he's back in serious mode."
    "ナースの表情がまた変わり、真剣な様子に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4024
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8c820eb4:

    # nk "Look, I'm not saying you shouldn't push yourself."
    nk "いいかい、べつに頑張るなと言ってるわけじゃないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4026
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8a0de978:

    # nk "But that doesn't mean you shouldn't be taking your medication, and it doesn't mean you shouldn't stop if your chest starts to bother you."
    nk "でもそれは薬を飲むなという意味じゃないし、胸が痛み始めてもやめるなという意味でもない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4028
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_53b086a9:

    # nk "I'd prefer not to have any fatalities while I'm on staff here."
    nk "僕がここのスタッフとして働いている間は、一人たりとも死人を出したくないと思ってるんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4033
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a2bbdfdc:

    # nk "A bit of a lofty goal, to be sure, but I'm always up for a challenge."
    nk "確かにちょっと大変な目標だけど、いつも努力はしているよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4035
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_5b504b3f:

    # "I hate to admit it, but I think he's right."
    "認めるのはしゃくだけど、ナースの言うとおりだと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4037
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f3c98e89:

    # "I've got to remember to take my medication."
    "薬を飲むのは忘れないようにしなきゃだめだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4039
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_5627077e:

    # hi "You're right. I'm sorry to worry you."
    hi "そうですね。心配させてすみません"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4044
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8470a8fd:

    # nk "Who's worried? You're a smart kid, right?"
    nk "誰が？　君は賢いから大丈夫、だよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4049
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_75179be3:

    # nk "I know you can be responsible, Hisao. A situation like yours, you've got to learn to be responsible fast."
    nk "君ならちゃんとやれるはずだよ、久夫くん。君みたいな状況なら、早くそれを学ばないとね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4051
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ee322606:

    # hi "I know, I know."
    hi "はいはい、わかってるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4053
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b47407ec:

    # "His expression suddenly becomes devious."
    "ナースの表情が急にうさんくさくなる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4058
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3967fe8b:

    # nk "I suppose you've started to enjoy your runs with Emi then, eh?"
    nk "じゃあ、笑美ちゃんとの練習が楽しくなってきてるってことかな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4060
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_13f3cfa2:

    # hi "Yeah, they've really been helping me."
    hi "ええ、自分にとっても本当にためになってますから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4062
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ec081ade:

    # hi "I mean, until today I was feeling a lot more healthy."
    hi "その、今日までは今までよりずっと健康になった感じがしてたんです"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4064
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b8385b1f:

    # hi "Plus it's really impressive to see Emi run. Did you see her at the track meet?"
    hi "それに笑美の走りは見ていてすごいと思うんです。陸上競技会の時の笑美、見ましたか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4066
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3bbc9230:

    # hi "She was incredible!"
    hi "本当にすごかったんですよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4071
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9efda7cf:

    # "The nurse nods, grinning all the while."
    "ナースはうなずきながらずっと笑っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4073
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8d3968e3:

    # nk "That she was, Hisao. I watched her first couple of races before I had some business to take care of, but she told me all about it."
    nk "まったくだね、久夫くん。用事があって最初の数レースしか見られなかったけど、あとで本人が全部教えてくれたよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4078
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ceb25c6d:

    # nk "Kind of you to loan her your jacket, by the way."
    nk "親切に上着も貸してあげたんだってね、そういえば"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4080
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6b622be4:

    # hi "Huh? Oh yeah, it wasn't that big of a deal."
    hi "え？　ああ、いえ別に大したことじゃ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4082
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bd199f72:

    # "I had honestly forgotten all about that. I still haven't gotten it back."
    "本当にすっかり忘れていた。まだ返してもらっていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4087
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a1b64653:

    # "The nurse gets a smile that makes me feel like he's just made a joke."
    "ナースが微笑むので、からかわれているような気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4089
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e38d4d06:

    # nk "Not to you, but Emi certainly appreciated it."
    nk "君にはそうじゃなくても、笑美ちゃんはとても感謝していたよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4091
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_14f47bce:

    # nk "And I know she appreciates your running with her in the mornings."
    nk "それと君が毎朝一緒に走ってくれていることも、だね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4093
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9936d3ce:

    # "This one catches me off guard a little. Sure, she mentioned that it's easier to keep to a schedule with an extra person, but I didn't think that I was doing her a favor at all."
    "不意打ちを受けた気分だ。確かに、朝練を続けるには誰かと一緒のほうが楽だとは言っていたけど、俺は親切で何かしているなんて気持ちは全くなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4095
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_bb36e31a:

    # hi "I thought she was doing me the favor of helping me follow the doctor's orders."
    hi "笑美の方が、僕が医者の指示に従うのを手助けしてくれてるんだと思ってましたよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4097
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e7eed434:

    # nk "She tries harder when you're around."
    nk "あの子はね、君がいると頑張るんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4099
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_135da16b:

    # nk "If there's someone else running with her, she's going to push herself more."
    nk "一緒に走ってくれる人がいたら、もっと頑張る"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4101
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_94bde393:

    # nk "And she tries even harder when you're around because, well, it's you."
    nk "そして君と一緒にいるときは、もっともっと頑張るんだ。君だから、だよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4103
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_0573a0ef:

    # hi "What the heck does that mean?"
    hi "それは一体どういう意味ですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4108
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a5f484c5:

    # nk "Oh ho, you'd love to know, wouldn't you?"
    nk "お、知りたそうだねえ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4110
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b4565309:

    # "He laughs in the style of evil megalomaniacs."
    "ナースは心底意地悪そうに笑った。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4115
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1bbeeebc:

    # nk "No seriously, it's because you're her friend."
    nk "いや、まじめな話、君があの子の友達だからさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4117
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6a51db97:

    # nk "If Rin ran with her, I'm sure she'd do the same."
    nk "手塚さんと走っても、同じように頑張るだろうと思うよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4119
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c86c45c2:

    # nk "Well, probably."
    nk "まあ、多分だけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4121
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d714ac6d:

    # nk "But that's not the point."
    nk "でも大事なのはそこじゃないんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4123
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_93c99ff8:

    # nk "The point is, you're helping her, even if you don't know you are."
    nk "君は笑美ちゃんの助けになっているんだよ、そう思っていなくてもね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4128
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_6597290a:

    # nk "And she's grateful for that, even if she never says it."
    nk "そして、笑美ちゃんはそのことに感謝している。何も言わないとしてもね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4130
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c655ed4a:

    # hi "What do you mean 'even if she never says it?'"
    hi "『何も言わないとしても』ってどういうことです？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4135
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a4585d71:

    # nk "Emi doesn't talk a lot, but she and I have known each other long enough that I can read her most of the time."
    nk "あの子は多くを語らないけど、僕は長い付き合いだから言わなくてもだいたいわかるんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4137
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d7df0e2b:

    # "I'll admit it. I have no idea what he's talking about."
    "なるほど、ナースが何を言っているのかまったくわからないな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4139
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e8fb71f6:

    # "Emi always seems pretty talkative to me."
    "笑美はいつもおしゃべりなタイプに見えるけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4141
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4143
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3454e207:

    # "The nurse suddenly realizes that he's been rambling and stops talking, looking a little embarrassed."
    "話がそれていることに突然気づいて、ナースは口をつぐむ。ちょっと決まり悪そうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4148
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1ba20d76:

    # nk "Anyway, you don't have to stop your morning exercise."
    nk "いずれにせよ、別に朝練をやめる必要はないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4153
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8bbfca7b:

    # nk "Just walk the track instead of running for a few days. Let things calm down."
    nk "ただし、数日は走らずに歩くこと。まずは落ち着かせよう"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4158
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_37c57c4d:

    # nk "And take your damned medicine!"
    nk "あと、薬は飲めよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4169
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_53bfda73:

    # "I laugh as I exit the office, bumping straight into Emi."
    "俺は笑いながら医務室を出て、そのまま笑美にぶつかる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4174
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_b27eb373:

    # hi "Whoops, sorry about that."
    hi "おっと、ごめん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4179
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_653e5cbb:

    # emi "Are you okay? What did the nurse say?"
    emi "大丈夫だった？　ナースくんはなんて？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4181
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_438a8b00:

    # emi "Do you need to go to a hospital?"
    emi "病院に行かなきゃいけないの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4186
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_be0288f3:

    # emi "Omigosh, it was my fault, wasn't it?"
    emi "どうしよう、あたしのせいだ、そうでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4191
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_18a403ca:

    # emi "I've been pushing you too hard, haven't I?"
    emi "無理させすぎちゃってたんだね、させてなかった？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4196
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_01c6ca24:

    # emi "I'm a horrible person!"
    emi "あたしって、ほんとバカ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4198
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1e191e33:

    # "The words pour forth like a torrent. She's really agitated."
    "せきを切ったように言葉があふれる。とても動揺している。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4200
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_41f7398a:

    # "I didn't expect her to be this concerned about me, to be honest."
    "正直にいって、こんなに俺のことを心配しているとは思わなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4202
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_afba2b32:

    # "Gotta calm her down… but how the hell do I do that?"
    "笑美を落ち着かせないと……でもいったい、どうすればいいんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4204
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1359bd2e:

    # "I do the only thing I can think of."
    "頭に浮かんだ唯一の行動を取る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4211
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_2f436cc1:

    # "I give her a hug. Emi tenses up slightly, so I pat her head in what I hope is a reassuring manner."
    "俺は笑美を抱きしめる。笑美が少しこわばったので、安心させようと頭をなでる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4213
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1466070d:

    # hi "Hey, settle down!"
    hi "おい、落ち着けって！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4215
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_0271060d:

    # hi "I'm fine, okay? No worries."
    hi "大丈夫だからさ。心配ないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4220
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_66746f83:

    # "I can feel Emi's body relax as I continue to assure her I'm fine."
    "大丈夫だと言い続けているうちに、笑美の体がリラックスしていくのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4222
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_1ce8dd6a:

    # "Her arms wrap around me, as if she's trying to confirm that I'm not about to fall over dead."
    "笑美が腕を背中に回してくる。俺が今すぐ倒れて死んでしまわないことを確認するかのように。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4224
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_58534f08:

    # "I catch a whiff of her hair. It smells like sweat, or how adrenaline should smell. It's the scent of activity."
    "髪の香りが鼻をくすぐる。汗のような、でもこれがアドレナリンの匂いなんだろうか。活発さの匂いだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4226
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_d8674e3e:

    # "And a hint of strawberries. From her shampoo, I suspect."
    "そして、ほのかなイチゴの香り。たぶんシャンプーだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4228
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_26227128:

    # hi "I just need to remember to take my medicine, that's all."
    hi "薬を飲み忘れないように言われただけだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4230
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_2b4b4f59:

    # hi "Don't worry about it. It's not your fault."
    hi "心配しなくていい、笑美のせいじゃない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4235
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f0ded6da:

    # emi "You're sure?"
    emi "本当に？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4237
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4995338e:

    # "Her voice is muffled, mostly because at the moment her face is pressed into my chest."
    "俺の胸に顔を押し付けてきたせいか、彼女の声がくぐもって聞こえる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4239
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4bdfaf88:

    # hi "Yeah, I'm sure. I just need to take it a little easy for the next few days."
    hi "本当だって、ただ数日間は激しい運動ができないだけだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4241
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_eb6c9745:

    # "It suddenly occurs to me how close the two of us are."
    "突然、俺たち二人の距離がとても近いことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4243
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_0459db22:

    # "It also occurs to me how nice being this close feels."
    "その近さがとても心地よいことにも気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4245
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_fc98512b:

    # "I can feel Emi's heartbeat calming down, and I have to resist the urge to rest my chin on the top of her head."
    "笑美の鼓動が落ち着いていくのを感じる。そして、俺は彼女の頭にあごを乗せたいのを我慢しなければいけなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4250
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_084f4f83:

    # emi "Thank goodness."
    emi "よかったあ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4252
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_8d14fb63:

    # emi "You really had me worried there, Hisao."
    emi "もう本当に心配だったんだよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4266
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ed72ff73:

    # nk "Emi, you going to come in here any time soon?"
    nk "笑美ちゃん、まだ入ってこないの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4271
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4ab70111:

    # nk "…Oh, I'm sorry. Was I interrupting?"
    nk "……ああ、ごめん。お邪魔だったかな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4276
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_3a0ed190:

    # "The two of us spring apart as if the other just caught on fire."
    "お互い火でもついたみたいに、俺たちはとっさに体を離す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4281
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f3c8eec3:

    # "Emi brushes her hair back nervously and laughs."
    "笑美はそわそわと髪をなでつけ、笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4285
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_a089010a:

    # emi "'Course not!"
    emi "んなわけないでしょ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4291
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_ff3df2ea:

    # emi "I'll uh… see you later, okay?"
    emi "えーっと、その、またね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4296
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_23e95fc3:

    # emi "Oh, and Hisao?"
    emi "あ、あと久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4298
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4305
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_7f390212:

    # emi "Take your damn medicine!"
    emi "薬は飲めよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4307
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_2be57438:

    # "This last phrase is punctuated by a punch to the shoulder."
    "最後の一言は肩へのパンチ付きだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4309
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_575088d7:

    # hi "Yeah, yeah, I'll remember."
    hi "わかった、わかった。覚えてるって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4311
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_181ad1e9:

    # hi "See you later."
    hi "またな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4316
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4a91de78:

    # "The nurse smiles again like he's in on some joke I don't know about and waves to me as I head for my room, feeling a burning in my cheeks."
    "俺には分からない冗談でウケているかのようにナースは再び笑い、俺に手を振る。部屋へと戻りながら、頬が熱くなるのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4323
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_9a837167:

    # "I need a shower."
    "シャワーを浴びる必要があるな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4325
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_521a602d:

    # "A cold one, if the thoughts running through my head now are any indication."
    "冷たいのをだ。いま俺の頭を駆けめぐっている思考がなにかの兆しだとしたら。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4327
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_c032d237:

    # "She was really soft."
    "笑美、とても柔らかかったな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4329
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_fb09b9d8:

    # "My pills are waiting for me when I make it to my room."
    "部屋に入ると薬が待ちかまえている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4331
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_03dc3717:

    # "I swallow them without a second thought."
    "何も考えずに、それを飲み込む。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4333
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_4f652f18:

    # "I don't know why I didn't think of waiting until after the runs to take them. For some reason I figured it was when I woke up or not at all."
    "練習が終わってから飲むことをなんで考えつかなかったんだろう。なぜか、起きたときに飲むか、ぜんぜん飲まないか、だと思い込んでいた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4335
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_f5fcd898:

    # "But no, they only need to be taken every twenty-four hours. The exact time of day doesn't factor into it."
    "でも違う、２４時間ごとに飲みさえすればいいんだ。一日のどの時間かは関係ない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4337
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_5cda4671:

    # "My thoughts drift back to the hug in the hallway."
    "廊下での抱擁に考えがふらふらと戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4339
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_61574813:

    # "It's weird, you'd expect someone to smell foul after a run, but for some reason, Emi smelled… right. That tinge of sweat just seemed to fit her."
    "変だな、運動した後の人なんて臭いはずなのに、どういうわけか、笑美の香りは……似合ってた。かすかな汗の匂いはぴったりだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4341
translate jp a2_emi_down_that_medicine_now_19b1712b:

    # "I really need that shower."
    "ほんとに、シャワーでも浴びなきゃな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4355
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4362
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f7b64135:

    # n "{vspace=60}Strange that it feels so natural for me to go up to the roof these days."
    n "\n\n最近、屋上に上がるのがごく自然なことと思うようになっている。妙な感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4364
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_cb2c2824:

    # n "I never would have done such a thing at my old school."
    n "前の学校だったらそんなことは絶対にしなかっただろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4366
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_b3d554b3:

    # n "In those days I liked to eat alone… no, that's not quite true. Though I liked to sit alone, I also liked to watch people."
    n "あのころは一人で食べる方が好きだった……いや、それは少し違う。一人でいるのも好きだったけど、人を観察するのも好きだったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4368
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9fe8a6a0:

    # n "I always figured that was the sort of person I was, but it appears I was wrong."
    n "ずっと自分はそういう人間なんだと思ってきたけど、それは間違いだったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4370
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_514577fb:

    # n "Then again, I also thought I was the sort of person who had a normal heart, so there you have it."
    n "とはいえ、自分はまともな心臓の持ち主だとも思っていたわけで、結果はご覧のとおりだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4372
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7ca1d29e:

    # n "I don't know myself that well."
    n "自分のこと、あんまりわかってないんだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4374
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a499e48e:

    # n "Now I'm on the roof so that I can have lunch with a couple of people."
    n "今じゃ、俺は二人の連れと昼飯を食べるために屋上に来ている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4376
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_93a175f0:

    # n "And they are both girls, which is even stranger."
    n "しかも二人とも女子、というのがなおさら妙な感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4378
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e9809d54:

    # n "Oddly enough, I feel closer to Emi and Rin than I felt to anyone at my old school."
    n "変な話だけど、前の学校の誰よりも、笑美と琳の方に親しみを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4380
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e90c2efe:

    # n "Somehow I get the feeling they'd at least visit me if I wound up in the hospital."
    n "もし俺が入院するはめになったら、少なくともお見舞いには来てくれるだろう、という気がなんとなくする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4386
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c56552b8:

    # nvl clear
    # "I focus on the view from the roof, banishing such thoughts from my head."
    nvl clear
    "そんな思考を頭から追い出して、屋上からの眺めに集中する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4390
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8b812c17:

    # "There's a light breeze blowing, and the sun is shining high in the sky."
    "そよ風が吹き、太陽は空高く輝いている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4392
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_af9c0e66:

    # "The sky itself is a deep blue, with hardly a cloud in it. It's gotten pleasantly warm, and as I sit down to wait for my friends, I close my eyes and enjoy the feeling of the sun seeping into my skin."
    "空は深い青色で、雲はほとんど見当たらない。暖かさが心地よく、俺は笑美たちが来るのを座って待ちながら、目を閉じて陽光が皮膚に染み込む感覚を味わう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4401
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dc590c55:

    # "Voices intrude upon the edge of hearing."
    "意識の端に声が割り込んでくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4403
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_eecf29ae:

    # emi "—seems to have fallen asleep on us, Rin."
    emi "――寝ちゃってるみたいだよ、琳"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4405
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_796495d9:

    # rin "Maybe he's faking, to lull us into a false sense of security."
    rin "寝たふりかもね、私たちを油断させようとして"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4407
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d4fa74d3:

    # emi "Why would he do that?"
    emi "どうしてわざわざそんなことするのよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4409
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c7cccc3e:

    # rin "No idea."
    rin "さあ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4411
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3eb64127:

    # emi "Still, you make a good point."
    emi "でも、いいとこ気づいたね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4413
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4eb65cc0:

    # emi "We should kick him or something to make sure he's really asleep."
    emi "蹴っとばすかなにかして、ほんとに寝てるのか確かめたほうがいいね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4417
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_867ff869:

    # hi "Huh? What?"
    hi "えっ？　なに？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4428
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_631a6ecb:

    # "Emi looms over me like only a short girl can, peering at me intently."
    "笑美が背の低い女の子にしかできない姿勢で俺の頭上を覆う。真剣にこっちをのぞき込んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4433
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1b92be72:

    # emi "Oh, you're awake. I guess we don't have to kick you then."
    emi "あ、起きてる。じゃあ蹴っとばさなくてもよさそうだね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4438
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_20b9aa48:

    # rin "Was it part of your master plan?"
    rin "それも君の大計画の一部だったの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4440
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c2ca05ef:

    # hi "What are you talking about?"
    hi "いったい何の話だよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4445
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6c58244c:

    # "Emi shrugs, her twin tails bouncing with the motion."
    "笑美は肩をすくめ、その動きでツインテールが跳ねる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4450
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1ba98fac:

    # emi "I'm not sure either."
    emi "あたしもよくわかんない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4455
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_81fdf20b:

    # emi "You must be pretty tired to fall asleep out here."
    emi "こんなところで居眠りしちゃうなんて、よっぽど疲れてたんだね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4460
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_451802f1:

    # emi "Although it's pretty comfortable, I suppose."
    emi "まあ、確かにすごく気持ちよさそうだけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4467
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c3460221:

    # "She plops down next to me and begins to eat."
    "笑美は俺のとなりにどすんと腰を下ろして食べ始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4476
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_607c0507:

    # "Rin sits opposite from the two of us, a move which only makes me more aware of the girl sitting next to me."
    "琳は俺と笑美に向かい合って座る。おかげで俺の隣にいる笑美の存在を余計に意識してしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4478
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f4a09856:

    # "If I didn't know any better, I'd swear Rin did it on purpose."
    "琳のことをよく知らなければ、きっとわざとやっていると思っただろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4480
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d679e94f:

    # "I concentrate on my food, trying to tune out the majority of the conversation that Rin and Emi are having."
    "俺は自分の食事に集中して、琳と笑美の会話をできるだけ頭に入れないようにする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4482
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_45636406:

    # "Despite my best efforts, however, I still find myself glancing over at Emi whenever she speaks."
    "しかし必死の努力にもかかわらず、笑美が口を開くと俺の目はついそちらに向かってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4487
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_373deafb:

    # "I notice how she purses her lips when she's thinking about something, squinting slightly as if that would improve her thinking ability."
    "笑美が考えごとをするとき、口をすぼめて目をちょっと細めるのに気づく。そうすると思考が深まるとでもいうように。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4495
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_538269a9:

    # "Rin says something that makes Emi laugh, and I notice, perhaps for the first time, how she laughs with her whole body, rocking back and forth, head thrown back, almost like she's about to fall over."
    "琳がなにか言って笑美が笑うと、たぶん初めてだけど、笑美は全身を前後に揺らして笑うということに気づく。頭は後ろに投げ出して、ほとんどひっくり返りそうなくらいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4497
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_98b5e433:

    # "I probably look like a creep."
    "今の俺はそうとう気持ち悪く見えるだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4502
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_12a44107:

    # "It's about this time that I realize Emi's looking at me. Her voice raised slightly, so she's probably just asked me a question."
    "このあたりで、笑美が俺の方を見ているのに気づく。声がちょっと高くなっていたので、たぶん質問をしただけだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4504
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dee1e459:

    # hi "Huh? Sorry, I kinda zoned out for a moment there."
    hi "えっ？　ごめん、ちょっと今ぼんやりしてた"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4510
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_364ba3fb:

    # "Emi rolls her eyes, while a slight quirk of the eyebrow is the only sign that Rin's even paying attention."
    "笑美はあきれた顔をする。一方の琳はただ怪訝そうに眉を上げるだけで、それが関心を示しているという唯一のしるしだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4512
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_58a3156e:

    # emi "I said, did you get a career survey in your class too?"
    emi "久夫くんもクラスで進路調査票もらった？　って聞いたの！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4517
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ccb305ed:

    # emi "You know, one of those 'What do you want to do after high school?' things?"
    emi "ほら、あの『卒業後はどんな進路を希望しますか？』ってやつ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4519
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4ca28fb9:

    # hi "I don't… think so. Maybe we'll get one tomorrow."
    hi "ない……と思う。明日もらうのかも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4524
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d7989ed2:

    # emi "What are you going to put down?"
    emi "なんて書くつもり？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4526
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a65c22a3:

    # "That's a really good question."
    "とてもいい質問だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4528
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ce5a4d8c:

    # "I guess I always figured I'd go to college after high school, but I've no idea what I'd do once I got there."
    "俺はずっと、高校を出たら大学に行くものだと思っていた。でも大学に入ってから何をするかなんて全然考えてない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4530
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_06a6ff19:

    # "And with the heart attack and all, I'd really been concentrating on each day as it came rather than making long-term plans."
    "心臓発作やらなにやらで、俺はずっと長期的な計画なんて立てず、やってくる毎日を過ごすだけで精一杯だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4532
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4ebe5fec:

    # "I suppose I can safely start planning ahead, again."
    "もうそろそろ、また先のことを考え始めても大丈夫な気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4534
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7ec08c9f:

    # "I've always liked having at least a vague plan for my future, so it'll be nice to come up with one again."
    "あいまいでもいいから将来のプランは持ちたい、といつも思っていた。だからプランを立て直すのはいいことだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4536
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dda18824:

    # "Of course, that doesn't change the fact that right now I've got absolutely…"
    "もちろん、だからといって今の俺にはまるっきり……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4538
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_931afad5:

    # hi "…No clue."
    hi "……わからない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4540
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_208036a4:

    # hi "I always kind of assumed I'd figure it out in college. That or just become a salaryman. That's pretty popular."
    hi "大学に行ってから考えるんだろうなって思ってた。それかサラリーマンにでもなるか。普通だろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4542
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_efe071c2:

    # "But do I really want to? That's a tough question."
    "でも、俺は本当にそうしたいのか？　難しい質問だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4544
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_97ac566c:

    # "I guess I don't really want to do anything."
    "たぶん、本当のところは何もしたくないんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4549
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_941e9a7e:

    # emi "You don't sound very excited about that one, do you?"
    emi "あんまり乗り気じゃなさそうな言い方だね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4553
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a639bfab:

    # "She laughs as she says this, and I'm caught up in her laugh again."
    "言いながら笑美は笑う。俺はまたその笑い声にとらわれてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4555
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9dbf7785:

    # "It's so… girlish. High and giggly, like a… well, pardon the cliché - like a babbling brook."
    "すごく……女の子っぽくて。くすくすと高い声は、なんというか……ありきたりな表現だけど……小川のせせらぎ、みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4557
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7667166f:

    # "It bubbles out of her, starting in her belly and working its way up her throat."
    "さらさらと笑美から流れ出てくるんだ。お腹から始まって、のどの方まで。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4559
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c6bc4755:

    # "I can't help but laugh myself - it's infectious."
    "俺も笑い出してしまうのを止められない。伝染性だな、これは。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4561
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0e80b5f2:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess I'm pretty unhappy with the salaryman idea."
    hi "そうだな、俺もサラリーマンはないなって思う"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4563
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d209318d:

    # hi "But to be honest, I haven't given much thought to the future recently."
    hi "でも正直言うと、最近は将来のことはあんまり考えてないな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4565
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_990852a9:

    # hi "I suppose that, these days, I've been more concerned with living one day at a time."
    hi "最近は、一日一日をどう過ごすかってことに集中してるんだと思う"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4570
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f356836e:

    # "Emi considers this for a moment and grins."
    "笑美はしばらく考えて、にっと笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4572
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4c7b6ac1:

    # emi "That's a pretty good idea, Hisao!"
    emi "すごくいい考えだね、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4577
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_98ee7cd9:

    # emi "I just wrote down, 'Pirate.'"
    emi "あたしは『海賊』としか書いてないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4579
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_795b3c15:

    # "I'm momentarily stunned, then I start laughing."
    "俺は一瞬あぜんとした。そして笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4581
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8d6fd139:

    # "I stop myself and manage to gasp out a question."
    "なんとか笑うのを止めて、息も絶え絶えに質問する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4583
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2c728cf2:

    # hi "You're… you're not actually serious, are you?"
    hi "おま……お前さ、それ、本気じゃない、よな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4588
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_970a22ee:

    # "Emi looks mock offended."
    "笑美はすねたふりをする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4590
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8aaa1f04:

    # emi "Well I've got the legs for it already, so I just kind of figured…"
    emi "だって、足ならもう準備できてるし、だからいいかなって思って……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4595
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4f95c161:

    # "Even Rin seems amused by this."
    "その一言に、あの琳まで面白がっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4600
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_63d0347c:

    # emi "Just you wait, I'll be the terror of the high seas!"
    emi "見てなさいよ、あたしは大海原の脅威になってやるんだから！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4602
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_20b7034d:

    # emi "I'll show you all!"
    emi "みんな首を洗って待ってろー！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4607
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4b9981ff:

    # emi "I've even been working on my pirate voice!"
    emi "海賊声の練習だってしてるんだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4615
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d2949eef:

    # "She suddenly springs up and begins swaggering up and down the rooftop shouting orders."
    "笑美は突然立ち上がり、命令をがなり立てながら威張った態度で屋上を歩き回る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4620
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_01e605d6:

    # emi "Yarr, me hearties, give 'em a broadside with the long guns!"
    emi "おらぁ野郎ども、やつらに大砲ぶち込んでやれ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4625
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_24a9888c:

    # emi "We'll wear their guts for garters!"
    emi "やつらのはらわたを引きずり出してガーターにしてやるぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4630
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_205d2146:

    # rin "Do you even know what that means?"
    rin "それ意味わかって言ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4635
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_effef57a:

    # "Rin's unexpected interruption stops Emi in her tracks."
    "琳が不意に割り込んだので、笑美はその場で止まってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4640
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8e68a8ae:

    # emi "Not really."
    emi "あんまり"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4645
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_85bb20e0:

    # emi "But it's all in the delivery!"
    emi "でもこういうのは言い方が大事なの！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4653
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a37e4a0e:

    # "The ringing of the bell prevents her from demonstrating her point further."
    "なおも実演を続けようとする笑美だけど、鳴り響くベルがその邪魔をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4660
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_71f457a3:

    # "Emi dashes off immediately, leaving Rin and myself alone on the roof."
    "笑美はすぐに走り去ってしまい、琳と俺だけが屋上に残される。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4670
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d1ed2d5d:

    # "Rin stares at me intently for a few moments."
    "琳はしばらく俺をじっと見つめている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4672
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_bd5814d1:

    # hi "Is there… something wrong?"
    hi "どうか……したのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4677
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_99fe60c5:

    # "Rin considers this question closely for a moment."
    "琳はしばらくその質問を真剣に考える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4679
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_26cba132:

    # "After a lengthy pause, she shakes her head."
    "そして長い沈黙の後、首を左右に振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4684
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6a594e55:

    # rin "Nope."
    rin "ううん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4686
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c9fbe424:

    # hi "Oh, um…"
    hi "ああ、そっか……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4688
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_82f6555c:

    # extend " why the staring, then?"
    extend "じゃあ、どうしてじっと見てたんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4693
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_fa7aec3f:

    # "Rin shakes her head again."
    "琳はまた首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4695
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e0829456:

    # rin "Nope, I don't get it."
    rin "ううん、わからないね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4697
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dad3a1f6:

    # hi "Get what?"
    hi "何が？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4702
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_786b0a33:

    # rin "The staring thing. You two seem to, but I don't."
    rin "見つめてるの。君と笑美はそうしてるみたいだけど、私は見つめられてない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4704
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1f720c41:

    # "Great. She saw me staring. Now she probably thinks I'm a pervert or something."
    "まいった。俺が笑美を見てるのを見られてたんだ。恐らく、もう俺のことを変態か何かだと思ってる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4706
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5ad86a37:

    # "Actually, probably not. This is Rin we're talking about, after all."
    "いや、そうでもないか。なにせ琳のことだからな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4708
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_da5ec933:

    # "Still, I feel the need to defend myself."
    "でも自己弁護はしておく必要がある気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4710
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5913ecd3:

    # hi "I wasn't staring, I was just tired."
    hi "見つめてたんじゃないよ。疲れてただけだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4715
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76fe2a8f:

    # "Rin actually snorts at this, but she doesn't say anything."
    "琳は文字通り鼻で笑うけど、でも何も言わない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4717
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f10bd427:

    # hi "No, really! I was just… distracted, is all."
    hi "いや、ほんとだから！　ただ……気が散ってたんだよ、それだけだから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4722
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_151ce4b7:

    # rin "Mmm."
    rin "んー"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4726
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3f63fd84:

    # "Eager to end this conversation, I head back down to class."
    "さっさとこの会話を終わらせたくて、俺は教室に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4735
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6eb76f0d:

    # "I'm greeted by the twin specters of Shizune and Misha, looking like they mean business."
    "静音とミーシャ、二人の化け物に出迎えられる。俺に用がありそうな感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4737
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d8db3cb0:

    # "Well, Shizune looks like she means business, anyway."
    "まあ、どっちみち、静音はなにか用がありそうな見た目だけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4739
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_125ea450:

    # "Misha just looks like she's about to start laughing at any minute."
    "ミーシャは、もう本当に今すぐにでも笑い出しそうな様子だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4746
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dba189fd:

    # mi "Up on the roof again, Hicchan?"
    mi "まーた屋上行ってたの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4751
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9b7534d8:

    # mi "You know that's dangerous, don't you~?"
    mi "屋上は危ないんだよ、知ってるでしょ～？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4756
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4761
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_bdd8350f:

    # mi "That's right~!"
    mi "そうだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4766
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1b11d035:

    # mi "The school cannot be held responsible for any injury that comes from being up there, you know!"
    mi "あそこで何かけがをしても、学校は責任取れないんだからね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4771
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c651530e:

    # mi "Furthermore, we could report you for breaking the rules~!"
    mi "それに、校則違反で言いつけたっていいんだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4776
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_66e0d0de:

    # "Misha leans in and whispers conspiratorially."
    "ミーシャは身を乗り出して、いわくありげにひそひそとささやく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4782
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ced3d317:

    # mi "But we won't, Hicchan!"
    mi "でもそんなことしないよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4787
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_09ce4f36:

    # mi "You three are too cute together~!"
    mi "三人いっしょにいるひっちゃんたち、かわいすぎるよ～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4792
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_4815021d:

    # "She straightens up again, laughing at my sudden blush."
    "急に顔を赤くした俺を見ると、ミーシャはまた体を起こして笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4794
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_69277904:

    # mi "Wahahaha~!"
    mi "わははは～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4799
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_58c2620f:

    # mi "You're too easy to tease, Hicchan~!"
    mi "ほんとにからかいやすいね、ひっちゃんってば～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4801
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_17c4ca90:

    # hi "Hey, come on."
    hi "おい、勘弁してくれよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4803
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9e8fdf17:

    # hi "I'm still new here, sort of."
    hi "こっちはまだ来て日が浅いんだぜ、一応"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4805
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d5de718e:

    # hi "Isn't it mean to pick on the newcomer like this?"
    hi "新入りをそんな風にいじめるのは意地が悪いんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4810
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3f22991d:

    # mi "Nope~!"
    mi "いいえ～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4815
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_30cd9e3c:

    # mi "It's to help you get acclimated to your new surroundings!"
    mi "ひっちゃんが新しい環境になじめるように手伝ってあげてるの！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4817
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6264a5de:

    # hi "Ah, I see."
    hi "ああ、なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4819
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8aad6d60:

    # hi "Well…do you have to be so overzealous about it?"
    hi "だったら……そこまで熱心になる必要はあるのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4824
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_59065e4c:

    # mi "Yep!"
    mi "うんっ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4829
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1e0011dc:

    # mi "Ah! That aside, Hicchan, we were looking for you this morning, but you weren't in your room!"
    mi "あ！　それはともかく、ひっちゃん、今朝探してたんだけど、部屋にいなかったよね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4831
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2d60156c:

    # hi "Of course I wasn't. I was out for my morning exercise, or here in class, bright and early."
    hi "そりゃいないよ。朝練に行ってたか、教室に来てたか、どっちにしても朝早かったんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4833
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f1805f4f:

    # hi "Unlike you."
    hi "お前とは違って"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4839
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_446e6fce:

    # "Shizune looks peeved, and a beat later, so does Misha. Or she tries to, at any rate."
    "静音は怒ったみたいだ。そこから一拍おいてミーシャも続く。まあ、怒ったふりかもしれないけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4841
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d876c233:

    # mi "That was because of student council business! You should be grateful that we work so hard for you~!"
    mi "生徒会の仕事があったからよ！　ひっちゃんのためにわたしたちががんばって仕事してることに感謝しなさいよ～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4843
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5703ac1d:

    # hi "Oh, I am, I am. So what did you need me for?"
    hi "あー、してるしてる。それで俺に用事って何だったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4845
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_01ab5f9b:

    # "Not another attempt to rope me in to do their dirty work, I hope."
    "またこいつらが俺を汚れ仕事に引っ張り込もうとしてるんじゃなければいいけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4850
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0d7e57e3:

    # mi "We had to give you something~ but since you weren't around, we dropped it off in your room!"
    mi "渡さないといけないものがあったんだけど～、ひっちゃんが見つからなかったから、部屋に置いてきたんだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4852
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7ca70422:

    # hi "Something? Like what?"
    hi "もの？　どんな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4857
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f5414b3c:

    # mi "Oh, you'll find out when you get back, Hicchan~! Wahahaha~!"
    mi "あー、部屋に戻ったらわかるよ、ひっちゃん～！　わははは～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4863
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_270b84ab:

    # "Mutou entering the room ends our conversation, and we all head to our seats."
    "武藤先生が入ってきて俺たちの会話は終わり、みんな自分の席に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4867
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6151a75f:

    # "It's only after I've settled down at my desk and the teacher's started talking about something or other that something odd strikes me."
    "なにか変だと気がついたのは、俺も自分の席に着いて先生がなにやら話を始めたころだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4869
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_5877251b:

    # "What did Rin mean, 'You two seem to?'"
    "琳が言ってた『君と笑美はそうしてるみたい』って、どういう意味だ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4871
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1946739c:

    # "Was Emi staring at something too?"
    "笑美も何かを見つめてたのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4873
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_28adf005:

    # "For a brief moment, I consider the possibility that Emi was staring at me the way I was staring at her."
    "一瞬、俺が笑美を見つめていたように、笑美も俺を見つめていたという可能性を考える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4875
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_591279b6:

    # "Of course, that's ridiculous."
    "そんなバカな。あるわけない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4877
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_008659bc:

    # "Still, I can't deny that I wouldn't mind if it were true…"
    "ただ、もしそうだとしても俺は構わない、という気持ちはある。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4879
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3a66fb61:

    # "But it's best not to think of that. No need to get my hopes up."
    "でもその可能性は考えない方がいい。期待をしすぎる必要はない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4881
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_219da5b3:

    # "Come to think of it, when did I start having hopes like that anyway?"
    "考えてみれば、いつから俺はそんな期待をするようになったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4883
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c9f751a9:

    # "I shake my head in an attempt to clear it, and focus on the lesson."
    "頭を振ってそんな思考を追い払い、授業に集中する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4888
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0413476a:

    # "After class, I make my way to my room. Mutou really piled on the homework today."
    "放課後、俺は寮の部屋へと向かう。今日は武藤先生が山のような宿題を出してきたからな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4895
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3b5e7b11:

    # "Before I can open my door, however, I am suddenly intercepted by Kenji, who has just exploded out of his own room in a flurry of papers."
    "でも部屋のドアを開ける前に、突然健二が自分の部屋から紙切れをまき散らしながら飛び出してきて、邪魔されてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4897
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_87466949:

    # ke "Hey, we need to talk."
    ke "おい、話がある"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4901
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7c617827:

    # ke "These rooftop shenanigans of yours, man."
    ke "お前が屋上で会ってるふざけた連中のことだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4903
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_1e802382:

    # ke "They've gotta stop."
    ke "奴らと会うのはやめるんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4905
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "なんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4907
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_dbbfed1f:

    # ke "Your running around on the rooftop with the limbless wonders!"
    ke "あの腕なし脚なしのビックリ人間どもと屋上で走り回ってるじゃねえか！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4909
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f87f6230:

    # ke "They're women, man! You'll get yourself killed running around like that!"
    ke "女だぞ、お前！　あんなのと走り回ってたら殺されちまうぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4911
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ed15e901:

    # hi "I don't follow."
    hi "なんだそれ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4916
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a3cbb49a:

    # "Kenji sighs and adjusts his glasses, before what could be understood as an attempt at explaining himself patiently."
    "どうやら、自分の言いたいことを辛抱強く説明するつもりらしく、健二は溜息をついて眼鏡を直す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4918
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_edf329d4:

    # ke "Look, we're friends so I'm telling you this for your own good."
    ke "なあ、俺たちは友達だ、だからお前のために言ってやってるんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4920
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a8f1cbf3:

    # ke "But if I were going to kill someone, I'd do it by throwing them off the roof and making it look like an accident."
    ke "だがもし俺が人を殺すとしたら、そいつを屋上から放り投げて事故に見せかける"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4925
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2becd5ea:

    # ke "And if I've thought of it, you can be sure they've thought of it too."
    ke "もし俺に思いつけるなら、奴らだって同じことを思いつけるのはわかるだろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4927
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f7102705:

    # ke "They're crafty - almost as crafty as I am."
    ke "あいつらは狡猾だ――ほとんど、俺と同じくらいにな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4929
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4934
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_02a1a8df:

    # ke "Good!"
    ke "わかってくれたか！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4936
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0e05690a:

    # ke "I'm glad we had this chat."
    ke "話ができてよかったぜ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4941
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_eeadf269:

    # ke "Loan me 500 yen."
    ke "５００円貸してくれ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4943
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2dfb8f13:

    # hi "…I'm sorry?"
    hi "……悪い、なんだって？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4948
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_e9e98be1:

    # ke "I need to get a drink, man!"
    ke "飲み物買いたいんだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4950
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_cc0e8c2e:

    # ke "I've been inside all day and the tap water's been compromised, as I'm sure you know."
    ke "俺は一日引きこもってたんだ。水道水はもう奴らの手で汚染されてる。知ってるよな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4952
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f52b51fd:

    # ke "So I need to stock up on something canned, got it? But to do that, I need 500 yen."
    ke "だから缶入りの飲み物を買いだめしないといけないんだ、いいか？　でもそのためには５００円いるんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4957
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_90ea7f01:

    # ke "And since I've just saved your life with my timely advice, you can at least spare me 500 yen."
    ke "それにお前は俺のタイミングばっちりのアドバイスで命拾いしたんだからな、５００円くらい恵んでくれたっていいだろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4959
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c242e84e:

    # "You know, if it'll make him go away, 500 yen is a bargain."
    "なんというか、こいつがどっかに行ってくれるなら、５００円なんて安いもんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4969
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_521270a7:

    # "I hand the money over to Kenji, who nods in thanks and dashes off down the hallway, but not before he locks his door."
    "俺が金を渡すと、健二はうなずいて感謝の意を示し、廊下の先へと走り去る。でもドアの鍵はかけ忘れたままだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4971
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ef6cd37e:

    # "What an exhausting person. I'd better go, in case he changes his mind."
    "なんて疲れるやつなんだ。あいつの気が変わる前に戻った方がいいな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4976
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_00ea3b67:

    # "Hm?"
    "ん？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4978
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_6dd40b9b:

    # "As I close the door, my heel taps against something lying on the floor."
    "ドアを閉じると、床に落ちていたものにかかとが触れる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4980
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c3406a0c:

    # "It's a brightly-colored rectangle of paper. Ah, this must be the 'something' Misha mentioned before."
    "明るい色の、長方形の紙切れだ。ああ、これがミーシャがさっき言ってた『渡さないといけないもの』か。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4982
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_55658247:

    # "Probably a student council leaflet she slid under the door."
    "たぶん、ドアの下から滑り込ませた生徒会のプリントだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4984
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f086bf97:

    # "However, when I pick it up, I find that I couldn't have been more wrong."
    "でもそれを拾い上げたとき、その予想はとんでもない間違いだったと思い知る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4986
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_8615a4ad:

    # "Someone actually wrote me an old-fashioned, hand-written paper letter."
    "誰かが俺に昔ながらの手書きの手紙を送っていたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4988
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f4dab597:

    # "Who bothers doing something like that in this day and age, anyway? Yet, as unlikely as the prospect of receiving one sounds, this is definitely a letter I have in my hands."
    "この時代にわざわざ手紙を書いてよこす人なんているのか？　でも、手紙を受け取る可能性がどんなにありそうになかろうと、俺が手にしているのは間違いなく手紙だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4990
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0c7518bc:

    # "I was planning on finishing my homework, getting some dinner, and going to bed in order to be ready for tomorrow morning's run."
    "宿題を終わらせて、夕食を食べて、明日の朝のランニングのために寝るつもりだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:4992
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_78ea0144:

    # "However, the letter has naturally caught my interest. I sit at my desk to examine it properly."
    "でも当たり前だけど、手紙は俺の関心をつかんでいた。俺は机に座り、よく見てみることにする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5001
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d21c5bd8:

    # "It's the first piece of mail I've received here at Yamaku, so it'd feel special even if it wasn't something as rare as a handwritten letter."
    "山久学園に来てから受け取った最初の手紙だから、仮に手書きの手紙という珍しいものでなかったとしても、格別な気分がしただろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5003
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_2beb101c:

    # "What causes me even more trepidation is the name of the sender, written neatly on the back of the envelope."
    "さらに俺を不安にさせたのは、封筒の裏に丁寧に書かれた差出人の名前だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5005
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a9c40d09:

    # "'Iwanako.'"
    "『岩魚子』"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5007
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_799ef6f3:

    # "I have no idea why she would write to me. I haven't been in contact with anyone from my old school since I transferred, and Iwanako is the last person I'd expect to want to write me a letter."
    "どうして岩魚子が俺に手紙を書いたのかまったくわからない。転校してきてから前の学校にいた連中とは誰とも連絡はとっていないし、岩魚子はいちばん俺に手紙を寄越しそうにない人間だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5011
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5014
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f94e2c99:

    # n "{vspace=150}The last time I saw Iwanako was terribly awkward; embarrassingly so. She came to my hospital room, peeled me an apple out of courtesy and then we practically sat in silence for half an hour."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n最後に岩魚子と会ったときは、ひどく気まずかった。恥ずかしくなるくらいに。彼女は俺の病室に来て、義理っぽくリンゴをむいてくれて、その後は３０分間お互いに一言も話さなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5016
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a36a2027:

    # n "She said 'goodbye' and didn't look me in the eye when she closed the door."
    n "そして、俺には目もくれずに『さよなら』と言って出て行った。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5018
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0051aa8c:

    # n "It might've been a natural end to the series of visits that were probably pretty painful for both of us."
    n "彼女の一連のお見舞いは多分俺たち両方にとって苦痛だったと思う。その終わり方としては自然なものだったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5020
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_0e1eccb2:

    # n "Every time she visited me in the hospital I wanted to talk to her, but something stopped me every time."
    n "岩魚子が見舞いに来てくれるたびに、話しかけたいと思った。でもそのたびに何かが俺を引き留めた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5022
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_3e5f58b5:

    # n "Every time that I didn't speak made the next time even harder."
    n "毎回俺は話すことができなくて、それで次はもっと話しづらくなった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5024
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_b4ee1ed1:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=120}She looked so guilty that I didn't want to say anything that might upset her, and I never could figure out the right words to say."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n岩魚子はあまりに後ろめたそうに見えて、俺は気分を悪くさせるようなことを言いたくなかった。どんなことを言えばよかったのか、俺にはさっぱり分からなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5028
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_d3fbad16:

    # n "I think Iwanako blamed herself for my heart attack. That's ridiculous, of course, but knowing it and believing it are two very different things."
    n "岩魚子は俺の心臓発作が自分のせいだと思ってたんだろう。そんなことはあるはずがないけど、でもそれを知っているのとそう信じこんでしまうのは全く別のことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5030
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_7f8abf22:

    # n "I told her that it wasn't her fault, she nodded and I really think she understood that if it hadn't been that, then sooner or later something else would've made my heart give out."
    n "岩魚子は悪くないんだと俺は言って、彼女もうなずいた。あの時のことがなくたって、遅かれ早かれ別の何かのせいで俺の心臓はやられてしまっていただろう、そう理解してくれたと本気で思っていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5032
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ade77ce8:

    # n "Yet she looked so hopelessly sad every time she opened that door and entered my room."
    n "それでも岩魚子は病室のドアを開けて入ってくるたび、どうしようもないほど悲しそうだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5034
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c8fc7c4a:

    # n "So I never managed to say the things I wanted to say. In the end, that might've hurt her even more."
    n "だから俺は、言いたいと思っていたことを一つも言うことができなかった。結局、それがなおさら岩魚子を傷つけていたのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5039
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5044
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ad45b62a:

    # "Carefully, I open the envelope and draw out the folded letter from within."
    "慎重に封筒を開けて、中から折りたたまれた手紙を取り出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5056
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_c4d0fca6:

    # "Yeah, I think I have had quite enough of this."
    "ああ、もうたくさんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5061
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_9049c309:

    # "I crumple up the sheet of paper and toss it across the room. My aim is off, so the letter rolls under my nightstand instead of going into my wastebasket."
    "手紙をくしゃくしゃに丸めて部屋の向こうに放り投げる。狙いが悪かったので、ゴミ箱を外れてナイトスタンドの下に転がり込んでしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5063
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_be3de3e0:

    # "That was an apology for abandoning me. Except I don't know that I really need it any more, at this point."
    "あれは俺を捨てたことへの謝罪だった。でも、今の俺にそれがまだ本当に必要か、よくわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5065
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_b07c4d50:

    # "The hospital seems like a lifetime ago, and here, now, I've got other things on my mind."
    "入院していたころのことは大昔のように思えるし、ここでは、そして今では、他に大事なことがある。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5069
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_a2492405:

    # "Emi, for starters."
    "笑美だってそうだし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5071
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_f012923b:

    # "It wasn't great to be abandoned during my stay, but it's not something I'm worried about any more."
    "入院中に捨てられることでいい気分はしなかったけど、それはもう気にするようなことではない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5073
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_543ed83e:

    # "In fact, I hadn't even thought about the hospital in what feels like forever until this letter came in. It's almost annoying to have received it."
    "事実、この手紙が来るまでは、入院中のことなんてずっと前から考えもしていなかった。手紙を受け取ること自体がうっとうしいとさえ思えてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5075
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_49580b70:

    # "I've got exams to study for, myself. I have no time for the past."
    "俺にだって、勉強しなきゃいけない試験がある。過去を振り返ってる時間はない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5077
translate jp a2_emi_piracy_on_the_high_seas_ae576d7f:

    # "Now, about that homework…"
    "さて、宿題しなきゃ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5090
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b8f57914:

    # hi "So what's the plan for today anyway?"
    hi "で、今日の予定はどうするんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5097
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_c98c7103:

    # "I'm waiting patiently in the hallway of the girls' dormitory just outside of Emi and Rin's rooms."
    "女子寮の中、笑美と琳の部屋のすぐ外の廊下で、俺は辛抱強く待っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5099
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f3c77901:

    # "Emi is apparently helping Rin with getting dressed."
    "どうやら笑美は琳の着替えを手伝っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5101
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_fade2441:

    # "I suppose that makes perfect sense, as I've no idea how Rin would get dressed otherwise."
    "まったく合理的だと思う。笑美の手伝いなしに琳がどうやって服を着るのか想像もつかない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5103
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_2d3b5d10:

    # emi "Picnic!"
    emi "ピクニック！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5105
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f07e216a:

    # hi "Picnic?"
    hi "ピクニック？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5107
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_48f9b0ce:

    # emi "That's what I said!"
    emi "そのとおり！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5109
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_760d24c9:

    # hi "Sounds pretty exciting."
    hi "なかなか楽しそうだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5111
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_ae7e8810:

    # emi "I know, right?"
    emi "うん、でしょー？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5113
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_0414a33d:

    # "Rin chooses this moment to make an observation."
    "琳がこのときを見はからって所見を述べる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5115
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_ceea0f64:

    # rin "The sky seems threatening today."
    rin "今日は空が怪しいよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5117
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_4aef54f7:

    # "Actually, I noticed that, too, on my way over. Despite the sunshine of the early morning, the afternoon seems to have taken a turn for the gloomy."
    "実はこっちに来るとき、俺も気づいていた。早朝は日が差していたのに、午後になるとうってかわって空が薄暗くなっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5119
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_aa69ab74:

    # "There's a heaviness to the air as well that usually heralds a rainstorm."
    "空気もなんだか重い。暴風雨の前触れだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5121
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_024af8b1:

    # "I wonder if I should have brought my umbrella…"
    "傘を持ってきた方がよかったかな……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5123
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_ad3bde6d:

    # hi "She's got a point."
    hi "琳の言うとおりだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5125
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_90475e9d:

    # hi "Emi, you sure that you still want to risk getting caught in the rain?"
    hi "笑美、雨に降られるかもしれないけど、本当にいいのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5127
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_e8ddae5b:

    # "I don't even know why I bothered asking."
    "なんでわざわざこんなこと聞いてるんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5137
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a87d0f0d:

    # "Emi pops out of Rin's room into the hallway looking shocked that I'd even suggest canceling our plans."
    "琳の部屋から笑美が廊下に飛び出してくる。止めようなんて口にすることさえ信じられない、といった顔だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5139
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_92bee20a:

    # emi "Of course!"
    emi "当たり前でしょ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5144
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f17dbaac:

    # emi "What, the threat of rain's supposed to stop me?"
    emi "なに、雨が降りそうってくらいであたしがやめるとでも思ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5146
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_139b7796:

    # "I can't help but grin at her belligerent response. It's almost like she's daring the rain to come."
    "笑美のけんか腰の態度に思わず顔がにやけてしまう。降るなら降ってみろと言わんばかりだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5148
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_ac3fc7db:

    # "If Mother Nature were walking down the street, I think Emi would probably start a fight with her."
    "大自然がその辺を歩いていたら、笑美はたぶん取っ組み合いのけんかを始めているだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5150
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_668e3caf:

    # "Or at the least challenge her to a race."
    "少なくとも競走で勝負を挑むだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5152
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_db27aba2:

    # "In fact, Emi seems almost aggressively cheerful today."
    "実際、今日の笑美はほとんど攻撃的なくらい元気だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5165
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b175025c:

    # "Rin wanders out into the hallway, looking her usual self."
    "琳はふらふら廊下に出てくる。いつも通りの見た目だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5167
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d8b1d56a:

    # hi "Well then, are we all ready to go?"
    hi "さて、じゃあみんな準備はいいか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5172
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f0a81699:

    # emi "I'm ready!"
    emi "いいよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5177
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a19ce415:

    # "Rin nods and says a single word."
    "琳はうなずき、一言つぶやく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5182
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d4967bcf:

    # rin "Basket."
    rin "バスケット"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5184
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_4de7bb72:

    # hi "Beg pardon?"
    hi "なに？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5189
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_837d8e42:

    # rin "The basket. In Emi's room. You should carry it."
    rin "バスケット。笑美の部屋の。久夫が持って"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5194
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_957321a0:

    # "Emi claps a hand to her mouth, embarrassed."
    "笑美はきまり悪そうに口の前で手を合わせる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5199
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_3427ecf8:

    # emi "Omigosh! I almost forgot all about it! Nice save, Rin!"
    emi "あっちゃー！　忘れるところだった！　助かったよ、琳！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5209
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_6962681d:

    # "Emi darts into her room and emerges with what looks like a very well-stocked picnic basket."
    "笑美は自分の部屋に飛び込むと、たっぷり荷物が詰まったピクニック用のバスケットらしきものを持って出てくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5213
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_70fc2c69:

    # "As she hands it over to me, I note that it feels heavy enough to be one, too. Good Lord, how much food did she pack?"
    "手渡されたバスケットはずっしりと重い。なんだこりゃ、どれだけ食べ物を詰め込んだんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5215
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_4c6f5b2e:

    # "…More to the point, where'd she get the money for all of this?"
    "……それよりも、どうやってこれだけの物を買うお金を手に入れたんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5217
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_ac9d873c:

    # hi "So, are we set to head out?"
    hi "じゃあ、もう大丈夫だな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5222
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_53c526f9:

    # emi "Yep!"
    emi "うん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5227
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8415af97:

    # "Rin gives another nod, and we head out of the dormitory."
    "琳はまたうなずいて、俺たちは寮を出る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5232
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_5146d2bc:

    # "I can't help but frown when I notice how gray the sky's gotten in the ten minutes I was inside."
    "１０分ほど中にいた間に、空はあっという間に灰色になっていて、俺はつい顔をしかめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5234
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_093c1dec:

    # "Still, Emi does not seem concerned by such petty concerns as the color of the sky. She's positively skipping as we walk."
    "それでも、笑美は空の色なんてささいなことを心配しているようには見えない。俺たちが歩くそばで、笑美はまさにスキップしている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5236
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_97136e65:

    # "Which reminds me…"
    "それで思い出した……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5238
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_2cb0d183:

    # hi "Where are we going?"
    hi "どこに行くんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5240
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_fffb8e5b:

    # "This brings Emi up short and she shoots me an embarrassed look."
    "その問いに笑美は急に立ち止まって、俺にきまり悪そうな目を向ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5245
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_01787086:

    # emi "You know, I hadn't really thought of that."
    emi "えっと、実はあんまり考えてなかったんだよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5247
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a4baa961:

    # emi "What do you think, Hisao?"
    emi "久夫くん、どこか行きたいところある？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5249
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_4fa4ad22:

    # "Well, there's the spot where we ate during the festival, but it might be nice to leave the campus for a while. However, I'm not sure if there's any good places to do that in town."
    "そうだな、学園祭の時に食事をしたところが浮かぶけど、せっかくだし学校から出るのもいいかもな。でも町中にちょうどいい場所があるかどうかはわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5251
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_104a2570:

    # "Just as I'm about to open my mouth, Rin unexpectedly interjects with a suggestion."
    "口を開こうとしたちょうどそのとき、予想外にも琳が割り込んで意見を述べる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5260
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b3b1f226:

    # rin "There's a park in town near the art shop."
    rin "町の画材屋の近くに公園があるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5265
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_c2e88fa9:

    # emi "Great idea, Rin! I totally forgot all about that place!"
    emi "ナイスアイディア、琳！　あそこのこと完全に忘れてたよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5267
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_01336b06:

    # "Crisis averted."
    "ピンチは避けられたな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5269
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_73a315a4:

    # hi "Do you know how to get there, Rin?"
    hi "行き方は知ってるのか、琳？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5274
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_4387f3ee:

    # "Rin shrugs."
    "琳は肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5279
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_406d1ee6:

    # rin "It's pretty likely."
    rin "たぶん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5284
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_0758bf99:

    # emi "Good enough for me!"
    emi "それで十分！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5286
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_22b7e64f:

    # "I would prefer knowing for sure… but, what the hell."
    "ちゃんと知ってる方がありがたかったけど……でもまあ、いいか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5288
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8e356b95:

    # hi "Lead on, Rin."
    hi "案内頼むよ、琳"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5293
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_82d5a0ee:

    # "The three of us quickly make our way off campus and take the road down into town."
    "俺たち３人はさっさと校門を出て、町へと向かう道を下る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5298
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d3bf0bf6:

    # "This basket's a bit heavy. I hope that the park is close by."
    "バスケットがちょっと重い。公園が近くだといいけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5303
