    hi "冗談だろ？　またすぐに雨が降り出すぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6102
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_637458b7:

    # "In fact, I think I just felt some raindrops."
    "実際、雨粒が落ちるのを感じた気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6107
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d4baf6de:

    # emi "Hmm… you may be right."
    emi "うーん……そうかもね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6112
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_1c15c086:

    # emi "Well okay, I'll let you off the hook this time, but you owe me a picnic now. Got it?"
    emi "しかたないね、今日のところは許してあげる。だから今度あたしをピクニックに連れて行くこと。わかった？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6114
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_56c13b9c:

    # "I don't know if she's addressing me, Rin, or the both of us."
    "俺に言ってるのか、琳になのか、二人にか、よくわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6116
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_87be1db0:

    # hi "Fine, fine."
    hi "分かった、分かった"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6121
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_9c3cf3ac:

    # emi "Now hurry up! I wanted to get some laps in at the track, and it would be nice to do it without the rain."
    emi "ほら急いで！　トラックで何周か走ろうと思ってたの。雨が降らないうちに走る方がいいでしょ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6123
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a2d73909:

    # hi "I thought this was your day off!"
    hi "今日はお前のオフじゃなかったのか！？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6131
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_18a4d9ce:

    # emi "Well…"
    emi "それは……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6133
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a814048d:

    # "Emi suddenly seems reluctant to explain herself."
    "笑美は急に説明するのをためらい始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6138
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a923c6aa:

    # emi "I need the practice."
    emi "練習しないとだめなの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6143
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_5ee44875:

    # emi "And I need to burn off that cake, anyway."
    emi "それにどっちみち、今日食べたケーキは燃やさなきゃいけないし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6145
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_58cc9a6e:

    # "Why do I get the feeling that she's leaving something out?"
    "なにか大事なことを省略しているような気がするのはなぜだろう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6147
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d5ebf0e6:

    # hi "Are you sure? It wasn't that much cake…"
    hi "本当か？　あんなの大した量じゃ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6152
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_13272b0f:

    # emi "No, it wasn't that much cake for {b}you{/b}. I ate most of it."
    emi "そりゃ、{b}久夫くんが{/b}食べた分は大したことないわよ。あたしがほとんど全部食べたんだもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6154
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_5bee595c:

    # "She's got a point there."
    "それもそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6179
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_1fbb1160:

    # "As we approach the girls' dormitory, it starts to rain again."
    "女子寮に近づくころには、雨がまた降り出している。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6184
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b5a2012b:

    # "Emi's expression sours slightly."
    "笑美の顔が少し不機嫌そうになる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6186
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8a727639:

    # emi "Aw, man…"
    emi "えー、まじで……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6188
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_79a4f32b:

    # emi "Stupid rain."
    emi "いやな雨"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6190
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_92ba0fea:

    # hi "Hey, it'll let up soon enough. You can go running then, right?"
    hi "気にするなよ、すぐに止むって。そしたら走りに行けるだろ、な？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6195
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b71a3875:

    # "Emi snorts, seemingly amused."
    "おもしろがるように笑美が鼻を鳴らす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6200
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8100f11d:

    # emi "Like I'm not going to run in the rain."
    emi "あたしが雨の中で走ったりしないって思ってるでしょ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6202
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_07a50215:

    # hi "Well you shouldn't! You could catch a cold!"
    hi "おい止めたほうがいいって！　風邪ひくぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6207
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a3e443a7:

    # "Emi waves her hand airily."
    "笑美は陽気に手を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6209
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_0561226c:

    # emi "Ridiculous! I don't get colds."
    emi "んなわけないでしょ！　あたしは風邪なんてひかないの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6214
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_eb5ccf45:

    # emi "My immune system is far too strong for something like that."
    emi "あたしの免疫力なら風邪なんて引くわけないんだから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6216
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b7fd02df:

    # "I can't help but laugh."
    "俺は笑い出さずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6218
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_85d565a3:

    # hi "Well, I'll see you tomorrow then, okay?"
    hi "わかった、じゃあまた明日な？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6223
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b286e85a:

    # emi "Yeah!"
    emi "うん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6228
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_3dff13f9:

    # emi "Thanks for coming! Oh, and for carrying the picnic basket!"
    emi "来てくれてありがと！　あっ、バスケット持ってくれたのもね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6233
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f8e2e460:

    # emi "I'll bring it for lunch tomorrow. We can have our picnic on the roof!"
    emi "明日のお昼にまた持ってくるからね。屋上でピクニックしよう！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6235
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_bf9d18bd:

    # hi "Sounds good to me. See you then!"
    hi "いいね。じゃあまたな！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6240
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_9b3afd52:

    # "Emi grabs the basket from me and shoots through the door."
    "笑美は俺からバスケットを受け取ると、ドアを抜けて部屋に飛び込んでいく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6242
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_4b108f56:

    # "Rin gives me a sort of half-nod and ambles inside as well."
    "琳は半分うなずくようなしぐさをして、同じくふらりと中へ戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6244
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_ee9dde8b:

    # "Damn, it's wet out here."
    "くそ、このへん濡れてるじゃないか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6246
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_35524d2a:

    # "I need to get back to my room and into some dry clothes."
    "部屋に戻って乾いた服に着替えないと。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6253
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_c133bff3:

    # "I'm soon in front of my door, but I am intercepted by the sudden appearance of Kenji, who appears to be carrying a stack of books."
    "やがて自室の前に着いたけど、突然現れた健二に邪魔される。本を山ほど抱えているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6258
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_01f5a8ee:

    # ke "Hey man, give me a hand, would you?"
    ke "おう、ちょっと手伝ってくれよ、な？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6260
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6266
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_511b1d18:

    # "The books are unceremoniously dumped into my arms as Kenji fumbles with his room key."
    "その本がいきなり俺の腕に積まれて、健二は自分の部屋の鍵をごそごそと手探りする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6271
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_3250fc10:

    # ke "Thanks, you're a lifesaver."
    ke "わりいな、助かったぜ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6273
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_79dab7ad:

    # ke "If you weren't around I'd have to keep my door unlocked, and that's just begging for trouble."
    ke "お前がいなかったらドアの鍵を開けっぱなしにしないといけなかったし、そんなことしてもトラブルを呼ぶだけだからな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6278
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_40111e99:

    # ke "The perfect opportunity to set up an ambush, or maybe just plant a bomb if they don't want to get their hands too dirty."
    ke "待ち伏せを仕掛けるには絶好のチャンスだ、手を汚したくないやつなら爆弾だって仕込めるかも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6280
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_936ad778:

    # ke "Probably don't."
    ke "奴らは恐らく手を汚したくないのさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6282
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_786d6d03:

    # ke "Afraid they'll break a nail or something if they have to stab me."
    ke "いざ俺を刺すとなったら、爪とか割れるのをいやがるんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6284
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_5a50af32:

    # ke "Women."
    ke "これだから女は"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6286
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_5e01faf9:

    # "My mind thinks about digesting the verbal torrent that's just been unleashed, but elects to remain comfortably in the dark."
    "たった今解き放たれた、この言葉の洪水を認識するべきかどうかと俺の精神は考えるけど、やっぱり無視することに決める。その方が楽だし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6288
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_3abc1135:

    # hi "Uh… huh."
    hi "あー……そう"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6293
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a12e6e19:

    # ke "Anyway, where have you been, man?"
    ke "まあいいや、どこ行ってたんだお前？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6298
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f6868f0c:

    # ke "I could have used some help carrying these back from the library!"
    ke "これを図書室から持って帰るのを手伝ってくれりゃ良かったのに！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6300
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8dfb95c8:

    # ke "I knocked on your door, but you weren't there."
    ke "部屋をノックしたけどいなかったし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6302
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_9b8ec38e:

    # hi "Oh, sorry."
    hi "ああ、悪い"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6304
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_0bb93cbb:

    # "Not really. You appear to think I'm some kind of pack mule."
    "とは特に思ってない。俺は荷物運びのラバかよ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6306
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_78613848:

    # hi "I was out with Emi and Rin."
    hi "笑美と琳と出かけてた"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6311
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_597149c2:

    # "Kenji staggers back in shock."
    "健二はショックで後ろによろめく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6313
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b9f3b241:

    # "It looks like I just shot his dog, if he had a dog."
    "俺が健二の犬を射殺でもしたみたいな感じだ。もし犬を飼ってたとしたら、だけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6315
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_6ddf70bb:

    # ke "The limbless ladies again?"
    ke "またあの腕なし足なしレディースどもか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6320
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d48bed5a:

    # ke "What'd you do this time?"
    ke "今度は何をやらかした？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6322
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a6ba33e8:

    # hi "Well, we wound up at the Shanghai—"
    hi "いや、いろいろあって上海に――"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6324
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8f3d8b26:

    # "I'm prevented from continuing by a sudden exclamation of despair."
    "突然、絶望的な叫び声が響いて俺はそれ以上続けることができない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6329
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_c3c6001d:

    # ke "The Shanghai?"
    ke "上海？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6331
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f9ed436c:

    # ke "Why the Shanghai?"
    ke "なんで上海なんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6333
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_f8a5c9db:

    # ke "No no no no, man, you can't just go to the damn Shanghai!"
    ke "だめだだめだだめだだめだ、お前、よりによって上海なんかに行くやつがあるか！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6335
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_75080c59:

    # ke "It's the most dangerous place in the city!"
    ke "あれはこの町で一番危険な場所なんだぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6337
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_0acdf0fb:

    # ke "A veritable stronghold of their best agents!"
    ke "奴らの最強のエージェントたちが集まる真の牙城だ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6339
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_1cb6164d:

    # ke "I know! I've met them!"
    ke "知ってるんだよ！　俺は会ったんだ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6341
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_842b4ea6:

    # ke "They'll stop at nothing to lull you into a false sense of security, and then BAM!"
    ke "奴らは手を尽くして俺たちをなだめすかして偽りの安心感に浸らせておいて、そしたらバン！　だ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6346
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d6b352d6:

    # "He hits his door for emphasis."
    "健二は自室のドアを叩いて強調する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6348
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_46bc6065:

    # ke "Wallet's gone. Bus pass? Gone. Identity? Fuckin' {b}gone{/b}, man!"
    ke "財布をやられた。バスの定期？　やられたよ。学生証？　{b}やられちまったよ{/b}、ちくしょう！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6353
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_33e9708b:

    # ke "Promise me you won't go there again!"
    ke "二度とあんなところに行かないと約束しろ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6355
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_1d5349ef:

    # "He seems so vehemently opposed to the idea of the Shanghai that I'm willing to lie a little in order to get to my room."
    "健二は上海という概念そのものに激しく反発しているようなので、部屋に戻りたい俺は少しばかり嘘をついてもいいかという気になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6357
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_babcb504:

    # hi "Sure, I won't go there again."
    hi "いいよ、あそこにはもう行かない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6359
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_0a011a80:

    # "Or at least, I won't ever tell you I've gone there again."
    "というか少なくとも、また行ったってことは絶対お前には言わない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6361
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_5d1407d1:

    # "This seems to mollify my bespectacled companion."
    "その返事に、健二は落ち着きを取り戻す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6366
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_5645daa4:

    # ke "Good, good."
    ke "よし、よし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6371
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_fe10349b:

    # ke "Sorry to come on so strong, but I know the danger there too well to let you just wander into the lion's den again."
    ke "うるさいこと言って悪かったな。でも俺は、あの場所の危険さをよく知ってるんだ。あんなライオンの巣にお前が迷い込むのを放っておけなくてさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6373
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_2e330485:

    # ke "You got out of there alive once, but twice is pushing it."
    ke "一度は生きて戻れたかもしれないが、二度はないぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6375
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_1d3e49b6:

    # hi "Yeah, well I need to get changed and uh, do homework. So… I'll see you later."
    hi "ああ。じゃあ俺着替えとか、その、宿題とかしないといけないから……またな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6380
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_1e477de6:

    # ke "Huh?"
    ke "はあ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6385
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_e1781ee8:

    # ke "Oh, sure. Whatever."
    ke "ああ、そうか。じゃあな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6387
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_17c011b0:

    # "I suddenly remember that I'm still holding his books."
    "突然、自分がまだ健二の本を抱えていることを思い出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6389
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_9b37b247:

    # hi "You'd better take these."
    hi "これ持っていけよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6391
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a378284c:

    # "I catch a glimpse of one of titles, something about cryptography."
    "そのうち一冊の題名が目に入る。暗号学がどうとか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6393
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8fd2ae2e:

    # "What a weirdo."
    "なんて変なやつだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6400
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_476fb2b0:

    # "Kenji grabs his precious cargo from me and disappears through his doorway."
    "健二は大切な荷物を俺から奪い取り、自分の部屋へと消える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6408
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8ceca8a3:

    # "I open my own door and walk in, grateful to get out of my soaking wet clothes."
    "俺は自分の部屋のドアを開いて中に入る。ようやく濡れた服を脱げるのがありがたい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6410
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b300bdfd:

    # "The rain outside picks up, and I find myself hoping that Emi's not out running in this weather. She seemed so adamant about doing the run alone, I can't help but wonder if her leg's still bothering her."
    "雨が強くなってくる。笑美がこんな天気に外で走ったりしてなければいいけど、と願っている自分に気づく。一人で走ることにひどくこだわっているみたいだった。まだ足が不調なのかとつい勘ぐってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6412
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_8673179e:

    # "I try to remember whether or not I've seen her limping at all today, but I can't. Guess I was too caught up in enjoying the day, even if it did rain on us."
    "今日の笑美が少しでも足を引きずっていたかどうか思い出そうとするけど、思い出せない。俺もきっと楽しむことに夢中になりすぎていたんだろう、雨に降られたとはいえ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6414
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_7d701ea2:

    # "And as I think back over the events of today, I keep finding myself focusing on my running partner."
    "今日のできごとを思い返していると、すぐに思考が俺のランニングパートナーに戻ってきてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6416
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_a6f6f723:

    # "Her complete refusal to allow the rain to spoil her plans was incredibly cute."
    "雨に予定を邪魔されるのを徹底的に拒否する笑美は、信じられないくらいかわいかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6418
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_d723f38f:

    # "But there was something else there, too."
    "でもそこには他にも何かがあった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6420
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_b99e582a:

    # "Sort of an unflappable attitude when it comes to enjoying the day as it comes."
    "やってくる一日を楽しむことについて、なんというか、取り乱さない、落ち着いた態度。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6422
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_6c8e1918:

    # "I really like that quality."
    "あの性格はすごく好きだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6424
translate jp a2_emi_famous_last_words_276db480:

    # "Maybe I need to do a little of that myself."
    "俺も少し見習わないとな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6445
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_8c329500:

    # "The sound of my alarm brings me out of a dream involving pirates and some other stuff I can't really remember."
    "アラームの音が、海賊やその他よく思い出せない夢から俺を覚ます。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6454
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_87761859:

    # "I'm a little bleary-eyed, and it feels like it takes me longer than usual to get dressed and down to the track."
    "目が少しぼやけていて、着替えて競技場に来るまで普段より時間がかかった気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6456
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9c185493:

    # "A glance at my watch reveals that I was right, and I am in fact running a little late."
    "時計をちらっと見ると、自分が正しかったことがわかる。確かに少し遅刻している。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6458
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c1b1cc52:

    # "The thing is…"
    "問題は……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6460
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_10f46017:

    # "There's no Emi."
    "笑美がいないことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6462
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_997d0c2a:

    # "That's odd. She should be here."
    "おかしいな。もういるはずなのに。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6464
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_67dec535:

    # "She definitely should be here."
    "絶対いるはずだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6466
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_f487f26f:

    # "I mean, I was {b}late{/b}."
    "というか、俺は{b}遅刻{/b}したんだし。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6468
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_63d693fd:

    # "I guess I wasn't the only one who had trouble getting up this morning."
    "今朝起きるのに手間取ったのは俺だけじゃなかったということだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6470
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9e0a6ca9:

    # "The thought crosses my mind that it never quite stopped raining yesterday. Did she go running anyway?"
    "まったく止まなかった昨日の雨のことが脳裏をよぎる。それでも笑美は走ったんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6473
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_8199c4b2:

    # "It seems likely. Emi's a lot of things, but cautious isn't one of them. She probably figured the rain wouldn't stop, and that's why she was so adamant about running alone."
    "あいつならやりそうだ。笑美にはすごいところがいろいろあるけど、慎重ではない。たぶん笑美は雨が止まないと思ったんだろう、だから一人で走ることにあそこまでこだわったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6475
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_4359bea0:

    # "Still, I would have gladly run with her, even if it was in the rain."
    "けど、俺はたとえ雨の中でも、喜んで笑美と一緒に走っただろうと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6477
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_aea2716b:

    # "Heck, if anything I would have been able to convince her to come in once it got really bad. That would be why she didn't want me along, of course."
    "ちくしょう、それならそれで雨が本当にひどくなったときは建物に入るように説得できたのに。もちろん、それが分かっていたから笑美も付いてきてほしくなかったんだろうけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6479
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c6285978:

    # "I should have offered to run with her."
    "笑美と一緒に走ると言うべきだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6481
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ec6bff48:

    # "Then I could have talked her out of the idea, or at the least known that she was okay. What if she got struck by lightning or something?"
    "そしたら俺は笑美を説得できていたか、でなければ少なくとも笑美が無事だったことくらいは知っていられたのに。もし笑美が雷に打たれたりしていたらどうしよう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6483
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_b2fa9faa:

    # "I'd never forgive myself."
    "俺は決して自分を許せないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6485
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6487
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_3f7f65f7:

    # "Okay, that's probably a little stupid."
    "いや、今のはちょっと馬鹿らしいな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6489
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_37676b44:

    # "Emi's a resourceful girl. I doubt even she'd stay out in a thunderstorm."
    "笑美は機転がきく。雷雨の中、ずっと屋外に出ているとは思えない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6491
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_4f112735:

    # "I trust her judgment on that matter, at least."
    "少なくとも、そのへんの判断は信じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6493
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_0fbdd48d:

    # "Even so, I can't help wanting to know where she is."
    "それにしても、笑美がどこにいるか知りたくてしょうがない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6495
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_456a0a58:

    # "…Well, nothing for it. I'd better stretch and run, and hope that Emi shows up with a grin and an excuse."
    "……まあ、しかたない。ストレッチをして走ったほうがいいだろう。笑美が笑って現れて言い訳をしてくれることを願おう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6503
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1be7b618:

    # "On my cool down lap, I am forced to admit that Emi isn't showing up."
    "クールダウンの１周で、俺は笑美が現れないことを認めざるを得なくなった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6505
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_d73a041c:

    # "Furthermore, I have no idea where she is. Anxiety gnaws at me while at the same time I wonder just why I'm so worried over her."
    "そのうえ、俺には笑美がどこにいるのかわからない。不安が俺を蝕むのと同時に、どうしてこんなに笑美のことが心配になったのか不思議になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6507
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_955bea6f:

    # "The run helped to take my mind off it for a little while, but now that I'm finished I'm back to worrying."
    "走っていればそのことはしばらく忘れていられたけど、今は走り終えて心配に逆戻りだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6511
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6515
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_04eab752:

    # n "{vspace=60}It was weird not having her here."
    n "\n\n笑美がここにいないのは変な感じだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6517
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1e05035b:

    # n "Downright unnerving."
    n "ひどく落ち着かない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6519
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_64feca4b:

    # n "It suddenly dawns on me that I've been running to hang out with Emi as much as I've been running to stay healthy - probably more to be with Emi, now that I think of it."
    n "突然、俺は気づく。俺が走っているのは健康維持のためと同時に、笑美と一緒にいるためなんだと――たぶん笑美の方が大事なんだろうな、考えてみれば。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6521
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_a734c3cf:

    # n "It's one of those things that are completely obvious yet somehow, I never realized it."
    n "そんなことはまるっきり明らかなのに、どういうわけか全く気づかなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6523
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_184c7b83:

    # n "She really is someone I enjoy being with."
    n "笑美はほんとうに、一緒にいて楽しい人だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6525
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_3d681119:

    # n "As revelations go, it's hardly world-shaking."
    n "別にそれほど重大なことが明らかになったわけではない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6527
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_d1733ad7:

    # n "All the same, I find myself feeling slightly shocked."
    n "それでも、少しだけ驚いている自分もいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6529
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1084fb4f:

    # n "When did this happen?"
    n "いつからこんなことになったんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6531
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9e086cbe:

    # n "Well, no time to think about this - though I want to ponder this new development, I have a greater desire to find out what's happened to Emi."
    n "まあ、今はそれを考えている暇はない――この新しい変化をじっくり考えてはみたいけど、それより笑美に何が起こったのか調べたいという欲求のほうが大きい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6533
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c96bc927:

    # n "I'll ask the nurse when I stop in to see him."
    n "ナースに会いに行ったら聞いてみよう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6538
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6546
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_0740aedb:

    # nk "Well, you seem to be in good shape, Hisao."
    nk "ふむ、調子はいいみたいだね、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6548
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_352b7d96:

    # hi "That's good to hear."
    hi "それはよかったです"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6550
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_07c37885:

    # "I replace my shirt and stand to leave, as usual."
    "いつも通り、俺はシャツを戻して出ていこうと立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6552
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_b2c0930a:

    # "Except instead of leaving, I ask a question."
    "ただし出ていく代わりに、俺は質問をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6554
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1ebe115c:

    # hi "Hey, where's Emi? She didn't show up this morning."
    hi "あの、笑美はどこですか？　今朝は来なかったんです"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6556
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_d92cf5ac:

    # hi "Is she okay?"
    hi "大丈夫なんですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6561
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9b60457e:

    # "While I try valiantly to conceal the anxiety in my voice, the nurse's expression suggests that I've failed miserably."
    "声の不安をちゃんと押し隠そうとしてみても、俺が哀れにも失敗していたことはナースの表情でわかる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6563
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1fa74ca3:

    # nk "You mean she didn't tell you?"
    nk "笑美ちゃんは君に言ってなかったんだね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6565
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_05fc082f:

    # nk "She's sick in bed."
    nk "笑美ちゃんなら病気で寝てるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6567
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_8eaa0ce8:

    # hi "What? Sick?"
    hi "えっ？　病気？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6572
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_81fd2592:

    # "The nurse shrugs."
    "ナースは肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6574
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_18afe979:

    # nk "Yeah, she came to my office early this morning with a fever."
    nk "ああ、けさ早く熱が出て医務室に来たんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6576
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_a70f24e8:

    # nk "To be honest I'm surprised she made it here."
    nk "正直に言うと、ここにたどり着けたのは驚きだね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6581
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_47b8268e:

    # nk "She was burning up when she arrived."
    nk "来たときはひどい熱だったんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6583
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_6bd1f5da:

    # nk "I believe she'd planned to let you know, but she asked me to tell you - oh shoot!"
    nk "笑美ちゃんは君に知らせるつもりでいたんだと思うけど、僕から伝えてくれって頼まれ――ああしまった！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6590
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_fe3a7981:

    # "The nurse gives me a sheepish smile that seems at least partially sincere."
    "ナースは俺に恥ずかしそうな笑顔を見せる。少なくとも、ある程度は本気みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6592
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_4a77e825:

    # nk "I told her I'd stop by the track to let you know in case she forgot to. Sorry about that."
    nk "僕が言ったんだった、笑美ちゃんが忘れたときは僕が競技場に寄って君に知らせるって。ごめんよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6599
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ea8d0b15:

    # nk "But we don't need to tell Emi I forgot, right?"
    nk "でも僕が忘れたってことを笑美ちゃんに伝える必要はないよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6601
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2e3f0e3b:

    # "I return the nurse's smile with a devious one of my own."
    "俺はナースの笑みに意地悪く笑顔を返す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6603
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_7f627108:

    # hi "Oh, of course not."
    hi "ええ、もちろんですよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6605
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c9acba56:

    # hi "This is fine blackmail material."
    hi "これはいい強請りのネタですからね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6607
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_5f082e72:

    # hi "I'll save it for whenever I need a favor from you."
    hi "あなたに頼み事をしたいときのためにとっておきます"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6612
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1a26db20:

    # "The nurse laughs."
    "ナースは笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6614
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_075d56eb:

    # nk "Well, I guess I deserve that."
    nk "まあ僕の落ち度だし、しかたないね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6616
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_e841eca9:

    # nk "But you know, I've got tons of blackmail on you that you're not even aware of."
    nk "でも言っておくけど、僕は君が気づいてもいない強請りのネタを大量に持っているんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6621
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ebcee4b4:

    # nk "So don't push your luck, okay?"
    nk "だから調子には乗るなよ、いいね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6623
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_f5b925d0:

    # "My expression earns another laugh from the nurse."
    "俺の表情を見て、ナースはまた笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6628
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_0ae5c739:

    # nk "I'm just kidding, Hisao."
    nk "ただの冗談だよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6633
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_a010bbf7:

    # nk "But seriously - don't tell Emi I forgot, okay?"
    nk "でも冗談抜きに――僕が忘れたことは笑美ちゃんには言うなよ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6635
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_39cb7134:

    # hi "Your secret is safe with me."
    hi "秘密は守りますよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6640
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_e3ab67c4:

    # nk "Oh good. Now go on, get out of here."
    nk "ああよかった。さあ、もう行っていいよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6642
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_a8ffb7fc:

    # hi "Wait, I've got one more question."
    hi "すみません、もう一つ質問が"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6647
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_eae343b0:

    # nk "Shoot."
    nk "どうぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6649
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ddc1e56e:

    # hi "Is she going to be okay?"
    hi "笑美はよくなるんですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6654
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c43a427b:

    # nk "Oh yeah, definitely."
    nk "ああもちろん、なるとも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6659
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_d259a064:

    # nk "Her fever was high, but it was already starting to go down by the time she came by my office."
    nk "熱は高かったけど、医務室に来たときにはもう下がり始めていたよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6661
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_87a92e49:

    # nk "I'll probably check up on her again at lunch to be sure, but I expect she'll be up and about by the evening no matter what I tell her."
    nk "もちろんお昼にはもう一度診るつもりだけど、たとえ僕が何を言っても、笑美ちゃんは夕方にはもう起き上がって動き回っているだろうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6663
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ad5afd39:

    # hi "Hmm, maybe I should visit her after class."
    hi "うーん、放課後に見舞いに行ったほうがいいかも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6665
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_02426b0a:

    # "It takes me a second to realize I've spoken aloud."
    "少しの間をおいて、俺は自分が声に出して喋っていたことに気がつく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6670
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_8beb2df1:

    # "The nurse raises an eyebrow and gives me a searching glance for a moment."
    "ナースは眉を上げて、一瞬、ちらっと俺に探るような眼差しを向ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6672
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_04ea4e98:

    # nk "Hmm…"
    nk "ふーむ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6677
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_d511b71b:

    # nk "Well, it might not be a bad idea."
    nk "そうだね、それも悪くないかもしれないな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6679
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_69d04c07:

    # nk "You could let me know if she'd taken a turn for the worse, I guess."
    nk "もし笑美ちゃんの具合がもっと悪くなっていたら、僕に伝えてもらえるし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6684
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_3b08ee9e:

    # nk "But no funny business, you got it? I know what meds you're on, after all."
    nk "でも怪しいことはするなよ、いいね？　君が使ってる薬は知ってるんだからね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6686
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_7dc53cf4:

    # "I think that's a threat against my life, but I'm not sure."
    "今のは俺の命に対する脅しのような気がするけど、確信は持てない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6693
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_7582a255:

    # "Either way, I assure the nurse that my intentions are chaste and exit the office."
    "ともかく、よこしまな意図はないんだとナースにはっきり伝えて、俺は医務室を出る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6695
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_915d80df:

    # "Interesting that the nurse sees me as some sort of potential suitor to Emi."
    "ナースが俺のことを、笑美の彼氏候補のように見ているのはおもしろい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6697
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1892afec:

    # "Even more interesting is how pleased that makes me feel."
    "もっとおもしろいのは、おかげで俺はすごく喜んでいるってことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6699
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9a837167:

    # "I need a shower."
    "シャワーを浴びる必要があるな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6706
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_df421f90:

    # "The lunch bell rings, and I find myself disinclined to make my way up to the roof."
    "昼休みのベルが鳴り、俺は屋上に上がろうとはあまり思っていないことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6708
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ed560ab1:

    # "After all, I'm betting Rin knows where Emi is, and if that's the case then I doubt she'd bother going up there."
    "どうせ、琳は笑美のいる場所を知っているはずで、そんなときでも琳はわざわざ屋上に上がっているのだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6710
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_3686ca7b:

    # "More to the point, I doubt we'd have any sort of scintillating conversation if she did. Chances are she'd prefer to be alone up there anyway, so I don't accidentally ruin her train of thought or something."
    "もっと言えば、仮に琳がいたとしても、二人で気のきいた会話ができるとは考えにくい。たぶん琳は一人きりでいたいだろう。俺の不注意で自分の考え事やらなにやらを邪魔されないように。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6712
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_55fef60b:

    # "Unfortunately, I don't really feel like heading to the cafeteria either."
    "あいにく、食堂に向かう気もまったくない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6714
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_390f848e:

    # "Guess I'll go to the library instead."
    "代わりに図書室にでも行こうか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6716
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_b84e60b6:

    # "I need a new book to read anyway, having finished my other one yesterday before bed. Maybe I can find more by the same author."
    "昨日寝る前に残りの一冊を読み終わったので、どっちにしろ新しい本は必要だ。同じ作者の本がもっと見つかるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6723
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_29a00a49:

    # "I love libraries."
    "図書室は大好きだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6725
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2bd03b20:

    # "They smell like dust and paper and ink."
    "埃と紙とインクみたいな匂いがする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6727
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1ade6424:

    # "All these stories and facts and opinions crowded together in one place makes the air come alive with potential."
    "あらゆる物語や事実や考え方が一カ所にぎっしり詰め込まれて、活気を秘めた雰囲気になっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6729
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9128fa24:

    # "I'm not sure how to navigate Yamaku's library yet, having mostly stuck to books I brought with me, so I search for the librarian to ask for help."
    "ずっと自分が持ちこんだ本ばかり読んでいたおかげで、図書室の本の並びがまだよく分からないので、手伝いを頼める司書の人を探す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6731
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6733
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_0c5b0f47:

    # "Hmm. I suppose she's not arou—{w=0.5}{nw}"
    "うーん。優子さんはどうもこのへんにはいな――{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6743
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_57c2d882:

    # yu "…can't believe it."
    yu "……信じられない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6745
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_a8f69565:

    # "Yuuko, looking rather distracted, suddenly emerges from one of the aisles."
    "優子さんが突然、ずいぶん取り乱した様子で、たくさんある通路の１つから現れる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6747
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_7aba37c7:

    # hi "Er, excuse me."
    hi "あの、すみません"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6752
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_72b89b86:

    # yu "Oh, can I help you?"
    yu "あら、何かご用？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6754
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_80748a53:

    # hi "Actually, I was looking for a book…"
    hi "実は、本を探していたんですが……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6759
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_fe62e514:

    # yu "So am I!"
    yu "私もよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6764
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_38d67974:

    # yu "'Advanced Cryptography.' We just got it in, and now it's gone missing."
    yu "『上級暗号学』。仕入れたばかりなのに、もうなくなってるの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6769
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_b52f457c:

    # yu "I really, really wanted to read that one!"
    yu "私、本当に、ほんとうにあの本が読みたかったのに！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6771
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1b51c966:

    # hi "Cryptography?"
    hi "暗号学？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6776
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_3c681e3f:

    # yu "Yeah, my… er, that is…"
    yu "ええ。わたしの……えーっと、そのお……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6778
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2190bcee:

    # yu "This guy I knew. Know. Um."
    yu "わたしの知り合いだった人。知り合い。うん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6780
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_74cc7acc:

    # yu "Not sure how to describe it…"
    yu "どう説明したらいいのかしら……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6782
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_6363a0d2:

    # hi "Skip to the end."
    hi "要点だけ言ってください"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6787
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_19570e66:

    # yu "He got me interested in cryptography only now the book's gone, and I think it's been stolen!"
    yu "彼のせいで暗号学に興味を持ったのに本がなくなっちゃって、盗まれたんだと思うの！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6789
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_5e58b3d0:

    # hi "Sounds pretty terrible."
    hi "それはちょっとひどいですね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6794
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c7077b46:

    # yu "Yeah, especially because now I have to search the whole library for it!"
    yu "ほんとよ、そのおかげで図書室ぜんぶ探さなくちゃいけないんだから！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6796
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_145179bc:

    # yu "Even though it's probably not even here!"
    yu "たぶんないだろうとは思うんだけど！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6798
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_5c2bcfcf:

    # hi "You seem… busy."
    hi "優子さん……忙しそうですね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6803
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_acf61eb8:

    # yu "A little."
    yu "ちょっとね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6808
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_214fb7dc:

    # "She dashes off down another aisle, and I resign myself to finding my own damn book."
    "優子さんは他の通路に走り去って、俺は観念して自分で自分の本を探す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6810
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_5fd5b846:

    # "Hmm, plenty of choices."
    "うーん、どれにしようか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6817
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2983a0a0:

    # "Oh come on, how did I get lost?"
    "いや、ちょっとまて。いつの間に俺は迷子になったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6819
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_409b1c88:

    # "These aren't even printed books! They're all in Braille."
    "これは印刷された本ですらないじゃないか！　全部点字になっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6821
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_b3c16a0c:

    # "I guess that makes sense in a school like this, but honestly, it's a little annoying."
    "こんな学校なら納得できるけど、正直なところ、俺にはちょっとうっとうしい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6823
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_20686807:

    # li "I'm sorry, is someone there?"
    li "すみません、どなたかいらっしゃるんですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6825
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c903c136:

    # "A lilting voice drifts out from behind one of the cubicles set up for research."
    "自習用に設けられたブースの１つから軽やかな声が流れてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6830
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_f61c93f1:

    # "As I approach, I see that Lilly's been reading a book while I've been stomping about the aisles."
    "近づくと、俺が通路でどたばたやっていた間もリリーがそこで本を読んでいたことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6832
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9734ad8b:

    # hi "Oh no, I should be apologizing. I didn't mean to make so much noise."
    hi "ああもう、謝らないと。あんなに音を立てるつもりじゃなかったんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6837
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ee96a5fb:

    # li "My, is that you Hisao?"
    li "あら、久夫さんですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6842
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_861ff926:

    # li "I've not heard from you in quite some time."
    li "ずいぶんごぶさたでしたね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6847
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2216716b:

    # li "I was beginning to think you'd forgotten all about me."
    li "もう私のことなんて全部忘れてしまっているんだろうと思い始めていたんです"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6849
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_5ef97bdf:

    # hi "Er, sorry."
    hi "あー、ごめん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6856
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ab7ee3c5:

    # "Lilly laughs in that refined manner of hers and shakes her head."
    "リリーは洗練された振る舞いで笑い、首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6861
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_e2b9cdf6:

    # li "I'm only teasing you, Hisao."
    li "からかっただけですよ、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6863
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_254943e9:

    # li "From what I hear, you've been busy."
    li "聞いたところでは、忙しかったみたいですし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6868
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9edde637:

    # li "Morning runs with Emi Ibarazaki {b}and{/b} lunch on the rooftop, if I'm not mistaken."
    li "茨崎笑美さんとの早朝ランニング{b}と{/b}屋上での昼食、ですよね。私が間違っていなければですけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6870
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_f2186f54:

    # hi "Heh, yeah."
    hi "へ、ああ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6872
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_1ccf0d23:

    # hi "Guess word gets around pretty quickly."
    hi "話が広まるのは早いもんだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6877
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_79872182:

    # li "That and I can't coax poor Hanako on the roof any more."
    li "それに、おかげでかわいそうな華ちゃんを屋上でなだめることができなくなりました"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6882
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_5c8eaf50:

    # li "You three are always up there, claiming the spot for yourselves."
    li "あなたがた３人がいつも屋上にいて、あの場所を独り占めしているんですから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6884
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_a03d44fb:

    # "She chides me gently, though it's pretty clear she's just teasing me again."
    "リリーはやんわりとたしなめるけど、今度もからかっているのは明らかだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6886
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_dd9a351e:

    # "Still, I feel an odd need to apologize."
    "でも、どうも謝らなきゃいけないような気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6888
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_86d11e92:

    # hi "Sorry, we could eat lunch somewhere else if it's a real problem—"
    hi "ごめん、もし本当にまずいのなら俺たちはどこか別の場所で――"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6893
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_20c574f8:

    # li "Oh no, I wouldn't worry about it."
    li "いえいえ、それは気にしていませんよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6898
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_cf4a7ae3:

    # li "Hanako and I have other things to do at lunch, too."
    li "華ちゃんも私も、お昼にはいろいろとすることがありますし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6900
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_55102577:

    # li "Such as read in the library, as you can see."
    li "見てのとおり、例えば図書室で読書をしたり"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6902
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_aac70433:

    # hi "Oh, Hanako's here too? I didn't see her."
    hi "あれ、華子もいるんだ？　見なかったけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6907
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_790a59df:

    # "Lilly smiles, a bit enigmatically."
    "リリーは少し謎めいた微笑みを浮かべる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6909
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_840e0786:

    # li "Oh, she's around somewhere."
    li "あら、どこかそのあたりにいますよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6914
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_4b1abe40:

    # li "But I'm surprised, Hisao. You're in here, instead of up there."
    li "でも驚きましたよ、久夫さん。あなたがここにいるんですもの、屋上ではなくて"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6916
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_4966e2b9:

    # li "What brings you to the library?"
    li "どうして図書室に？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6918
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ea964981:

    # hi "Well, Emi's ill, so there's no lunch on the rooftop to keep me occupied…"
    hi "その、笑美が病気でさ、だから屋上でのランチもなしってわけで……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6923
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_4b4dde96:

    # "Lilly raises an eyebrow at my statement before giving another chuckle."
    "リリーは俺の言葉に眉を上げて、また含み笑いをする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6925
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_0c398c48:

    # li "My, poor Rin must feel left out."
    li "まあ。かわいそうな手塚さんは、のけ者にされたと思っているでしょうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6927
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_44f83214:

    # hi "It's not like that!"
    hi "そんなんじゃないよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6932
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_a88dfec8:

    # li "Ah, but I'm sure it isn't. Emi tends to be the life of whatever group she's in."
    li "ええ、私も違うと思います。笑美ちゃんはどのグループにいても活気の源になるような子ですからね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6937
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ba30994b:

    # li "It's a shame to hear she's fallen ill. Will she be okay?"
    li "笑美ちゃんが病気というのはお気の毒です。大丈夫なんですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6939
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_953baf9d:

    # "Somehow I get the feeling that Lilly's just inquiring out of politeness, but I respond anyway."
    "どうもただ礼儀として聞いているような感じが少しするけど、とにかく俺は返事をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6941
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9df6f907:

    # hi "The nurse thinks so. I'm going to swing by and see how she's doing after school myself."
    hi "ナースはそう思ってるよ。俺、放課後に笑美がどうしているか見に寄っていくつもり"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6946
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2b162d95:

    # "Another raised eyebrow."
    "また眉を上げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6948
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_d1180ed1:

    # li "My, what a noble gentleman you are, Hisao."
    li "まあ。とても紳士的なんですね、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6950
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_ecd291d9:

    # hi "It's nothing, really. Just checking up on my friend, after all."
    hi "たいしたことじゃないよ、本当に。ただ友達の様子を見るだけだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6955
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_0ef9b922:

    # li "Ah, so it's just friends, is it? How disappointing."
    li "あら、ただの友達なんですか？　がっかりです"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6957
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_f82f1332:

    # "I blush, glad that Lilly can't see it."
    "顔が赤くなる。リリーには見えなくてよかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6962
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_c83497e7:

    # "But somehow she knows that I've been flustered by her comment anyway, and laughs."
    "でもどういうわけか、俺がリリーの言葉でうろたえていることがわかるようで、リリーは笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6964
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_e7fbe940:

    # li "I'm sorry, Hisao. I'm teasing you again."
    li "ごめんなさい、久夫さん。またからかってしまいました"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6969
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2426cede:

    # li "Please do tell Emi that I hope she feels better, won't you?"
    li "おだいじにと笑美ちゃんに伝えてもらえませんか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6971
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_5caa6f31:

    # "A glance at my watch reveals that I'm very nearly out of time to find my book."
    "腕時計をちらっと見ると、本を探す時間はほとんどないことがわかる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6973
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2f6a93ba:

    # hi "Of course."
    hi "ええ、もちろん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6975
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_9f2ea3d6:

    # hi "Hey, I've got to find a book before lunch is over, so I'd better get moving."
    hi "その、昼休みが終わる前に本を見つけたいんだ。だからもう行かないと"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6977
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_181ad1e9:

    # hi "See you later."
    hi "またな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6979
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_e39af9f2:

    # "That was probably not the best phrase to use."
    "今のは、リリーに言うのにはベストな言葉ではなかっただろうな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6981
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_daa84b9a:

    # "Lilly, however, takes my gaffe in stride."
    "けどリリーは俺の失言をうまく受け流す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6988
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_161766b4:

    # li "Until we meet again, Hisao."
    li "また会いましょうね、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6993
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_6a7a17bd:

    # "I never do find the book I was looking for, but I walk out with something else instead."
    "探していた本はぜんぜん見つからないけど、代わりに見つけたものを持って図書室を出る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6995
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_e734cb30:

    # "My stomach growls slightly, letting me know that I should have had something for lunch."
    "腹が軽く鳴って、昼食に何か食べたほうがいいと俺に教えてくれる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6997
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_2521d867:

    # "Oh well."
    "ああ、そうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6999
translate jp a2_emi_tracking_absences_50276528:

    # "I'll grab something before I visit Emi later."
    "あとで笑美のところへ行く前に、ちょっと何か食べよう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7012
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ef7cb43f:

    # "It seems as if time has decided to slow down for the express purpose of annoying the hell out of me."
    "時間がまるで俺にひどい嫌がらせをするというはっきりとした目的を持って遅く進むことにしたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7014
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b74e32a6:

    # "Class feels like it drags on for ages."
    "授業がずるずる延々と続くように感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7016
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_398a54ff:

    # "I suspect that my being consumed with worry probably has something to do with it."
    "心配事で頭がいっぱいになっていることも関係があるんだろうな、とは思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7020
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a8c92e8e:

    # "Blessedly the bell rings and I dash out of class, drawing a few raised eyebrows, I'm sure."
    "幸いなことにベルが鳴って、俺は教室から飛び出す。眉をつり上げる人が何人かいたに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7025
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3eb0adc0:

    # "I have spent the majority of the day fretting as unobtrusively as I could."
    "今日ほぼ一日、やきもきする気持ちをできるだけ表に出さないようにして過ごした。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7027
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ed35cd16:

    # "Even though the nurse thinks that Emi is perfectly okay, I want to see for myself."
    "笑美ならすっかり大丈夫だとナースは言っていたけど、自分の目で確かめたい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7034
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_9c39e3ee:

    # "It doesn't take long to get to the girls' dormitory and make my way to Emi's room."
    "女子寮に入って笑美の部屋まで行くのには時間がかからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7036
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3133b83c:

    # "Standing outside her door, I suddenly pause. What if she's resting?"
    "部屋の前に立って、俺は突然ためらう。もし笑美が寝ていたら？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7038
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f8eb2ddc:

    # "I'd hate to wake her up, especially if she's still feeling ill."
    "起こすのはいやだ。まだ具合が悪いなら、なおさらだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7040
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_26b18f5d:

    # "Then again, if she sleeps all day then it could throw off her sleeping schedule."
    "だけど、もし一日中寝ているとしたら笑美の睡眠サイクルを狂わせてしまうかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7042
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_98b34ac8:

    # "But rest is important if you're ill, isn't it?"
    "でも病気の時は休息が大切、じゃないのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7044
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f63d809f:

    # "I can't decide what to do, so I settle for standing outside the door looking like an idiot."
    "どうするか決めかねて、俺は馬鹿みたいにドアの前に突っ立っていることになった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7046
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c29722e7:

    # "Then I hear Emi's voice from behind the door."
    "するとドア越しに笑美の声が聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7048
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0e6ed5f9:

    # emi "Thanks for your concern, but I really am okay."
    emi "心配してくれてありがとう、でも本当に大丈夫"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7050
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3cb4c53d:

    # "Is she talking to me?"
    "俺に話しているんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7052
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_79c8422f:

    # emi "I'll see you at practice tomorrow!"
    emi "それじゃまた明日練習で！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7054
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_606b9053:

    # "Guess not."
    "違うみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7056
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a7ace483:

    # "Still, clearly she's not asleep, so I can knock without worry."
    "それでも、笑美が寝てないのは確かだ。だからノックは気兼ねなくできる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7058
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_fb9fe023:

    # "So why this clenched feeling in my gut? I wasn't nervous about dropping by the other day, so why today?"
    "ならこの内臓が掴まれてるみたいな感じはなぜだ？　前に来たときは緊張してなかったのに、なんで今日は？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7060
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_85b08c1b:

    # "Granted, I still haven't really had time to figure out this newfound interest in Emi's well-being."
    "笑美の健康状態に関心を持つという、自分の新たな気持ちをちゃんと検討する時間はまだ取れていないけど、それにしてもだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7062
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_74c6244d:

    # "I don't have a lot of experience in the matter, of course, but certainly this seems to go beyond feelings of mere friendship."
    "もちろんこういう経験はそんなにないけど、ただの友情なんて思いを越えそうなのは間違いない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7064
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_18574878:

    # "But could I take that step? Could I even bring myself to risk what I have right now?"
    "でも次のステップを踏めるだろうか？　俺は今あるものを失うリスクを負うことができるだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7066
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_dd164a57:

    # "I mean it's enough to be friends with her, isn't it?"
    "つまり笑美とは友達でも十分、じゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7068
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3ac405e6:

    # "Either way, shouldn't I just open the door and see how she's doing? That's why I came here… right?"
    "どっちにしろ、ドアを開けて笑美がどうしているか見るくらいはするべきじゃないか？　そのために来たんだ……よな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7072
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_17461f2e:

    # "What if she's not dressed yet?"
    "でももしまだ服を着ていなかったら？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7078
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c2e69b55:

    # "The image that flashes through my mind causes my heart to skip a beat, literally."
    "頭にちらつくイメージが、文字どおり心臓をドキッとさせる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7082
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a3304c70:

    # "I should probably not ever think those thoughts again. Not if I want to avoid a heart attack."
    "もうこんなことを考えるのはやめたほうがいい。心臓発作を避けるためにも。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7084
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_38a7b25c:

    # "I suddenly realize I'm still standing in the hallway looking like an idiot."
    "俺は突然、まだ自分が馬鹿みたいに廊下の真ん中で突っ立っていることに気がつく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7088
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3e6c1bf5:

    # "Emi still seems to be in the middle of a conversation, but I knock anyway. Hopefully she won't mind the interruption."
    "笑美はまだ会話の途中みたいだけど、気にせずノックする。邪魔をしても気にしないでくれるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7090
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a4478a9f:

    # emi "You worry too mu— Come in! The door's unlocked."
    emi "心配しすぎ――どうぞ！　鍵あいてるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7092
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_42ed4737:

    # "So it is. I open the door and step in, which is about where my thought process comes to a grinding halt."
    "そういうことだ。俺はドアを開けて中に入り、その時点で俺の思考には急ブレーキがかかってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7102
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_7bdc66a4:

    # "Emi is sitting up in bed, her hair tousled from a day spent asleep. I think this is the first time I've seen her without those familiar beads in her hair."
    "笑美がベッドで起き上がっていて、髪は一日中寝ていたからかボサボサだった。あのいつものビーズの髪留めをしていないところを見るのは初めてだと思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7104
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_469ba94f:

    # "Her gym shirt and bloomers, obviously hastily pulled on before I came in, are creased and folded from less than proper storage."
    "体操服とブルマは、俺が入る前に急いで身につけたのだろう。しまうときにきちんと畳まれていなかったのか、しわくちゃになっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7111
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_67fc11bd:

    # "Her legs lay bare on the sheets."
    "脚がむき出しでシーツの上に横たわっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7113
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c271b4cc:

    # "I've never seen Emi without prosthetics before. Yet here she is, slender legs terminating in stumps just below her knees."
    "義足をつけていない笑美を見たことはなかった。でも笑美はここにいる。膝のすぐ下で切れて終わっている細い脚で。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7115
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_bee8152e:

    # "But as odd as the sight is, I find myself more captivated by everything north of the waist."
    "でもその光景と同じくらい奇妙なことだけど、自分が笑美の腰から上の部分にもっと気を引かれていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7123
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f530fd8a:

    # "It seems that Emi had finished her conversation with whoever was on the phone with her, and is now watching my reaction closely out of her one open eye as she wipes sleep from the other."
    "どうやら笑美は誰かとの電話の会話を終えたようで、今は片方の寝ぼけ眼をこすりながらもう片方の目で俺の反応をじっと見ている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7125
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_be99b68f:

    # "Her expression, far from being embarrassed, is rather one of a surprisingly wide yawn. One perhaps appropriate from such a small mouth."
    "彼女の表情は、恥じらいから遠く離れていて、やたらと大きいあくびを見せた。こんな小さい口にはぴったりかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7127
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_da31bc0c:

    # "A grin that for a brief moment seems almost flirtatious tugs at the corner of her mouth as she takes the sight of me in."
    "俺を視界に入れるときに口の端で一瞬見せた笑いは、俺を誘っているように見えた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7129
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_de2476bd:

    # "I can do nothing but remain in a state fluctuating between fear, confusion, and not a little bit of lust."
    "俺はなにもできずに、恐怖と混乱と、少なからぬ欲望の中に取り残される。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7131
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_aacf539d:

    # "Emi hastily sweeps her hair out of her eyes, fixing it back into place before addressing me."
    "笑美はあわてて髪の毛を目から払い、元の位置に戻してから俺に話しかける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7137
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4f30954e:

    # emi "You seem a bit caught off guard, Hisao."
    emi "ちょっと油断してたみたいね、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7139
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b68611b4:

    # "A wave of laughter erupts from her, and I find myself grinning and rubbing the back of my head ruefully."
    "笑美の満面の笑いがうつって、自分も笑いながら頭をかいてしまっていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7141
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_76651ca1:

    # hi "Sorry, I've just…"
    hi "ごめん、俺はただ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7143
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_64e32e14:

    # "Never seen someone so disheveled look so attractive."
    "だらしない様子がこんなに魅力的な人なんて見たことがなかったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7145
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ec333982:

    # "Never seen you without your legs on."
    "義足のない君を見たこともなかったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7147
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_23421273:

    # "Never seen you look so…"
    "君がすごく……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7149
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4f48a656:

    # hi "Um, sorry."
    hi "その、ごめん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7154
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_72f5f4ad:

    # "Emi giggles again and moves to sit up a little straighter."
    "笑美はまたくすくす笑って、ちょっと座りなおす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7156
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_687d353a:

    # "I'm caught up in the movements of her shirt, very nearly losing myself."
    "シャツの動きが気になって、我を失いそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7161
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ca737fe5:

    # emi "I was wondering what your reaction would be."
    emi "久夫くんならどんな反応するかなって思ってたの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7166
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_48fadb88:

    # emi "The nurse called and told me you were going to drop by, you see."
    emi "あのね、ナースくんから電話があって、久夫くんが来るって言ってたから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7171
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a810b9a7:

    # emi "And I know you haven't seen me… well, you know."
    emi "それに、久夫くんが見たことないの知ってるし、あたしの……えっと、ほら"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7176
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_00a072a3:

    # emi "Without legs."
    emi "足がないとき"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7178
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_022d760b:

    # "I respond in a tone of casual surprise."
    "俺は軽く驚いたように返す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7180
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_d00e69fb:

    # hi "Oh, you don't have them on? I didn't notice."
    hi "あ、付けてなかったんだ？　わからなかったよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7182
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_2a6c5559:

    # "This is almost the truth. I very nearly didn't."
    "ほぼ本音だ。ほとんど気づかなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7184
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f941e843:

    # "I'm not trying to be suave or anything, mind you. Somehow I think Emi would get offended by that."
    "人当たりをよくしようとか、そんなのじゃないんだ。なんだか、笑美はそういうことをされたら怒るような気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7191
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a3e992a8:

    # "Instead, she sticks her tongue out at me and chucks a pillow at my head."
    "かわりに、笑美は舌を出して枕を俺の頭に投げてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7193
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_da07edab:

    # emi "Ass."
    emi "バーカ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7195
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_932daf6b:

    # "I deftly catch the pillow and take careful aim before throwing."
    "俺はその枕をうまく受け止めて、慎重に狙ってから投げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7206
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c6a5a43f:

    # "Emi laughs and rolls to one side, dodging my shot, the shifting of her shirt distracting me enough so that the next thrown pillow hits me right between the eyes."
    "笑美が笑いながら転がって枕を避ける。ずれたシャツに気を取られて、次の枕が俺の眉間を直撃する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7210
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_75415527:

    # hi "Oof!" with hpunch
    hi "おぅふ！" with hpunch

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7212
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f053e5f5:

    # "I retaliate, of course."
    "もちろん、反撃する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7214
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_bd4fa3a4:

    # "And once I've retaliated twice, well, a war was bound to break out sooner or later."
    "そして二回も反撃すれば、まあ、遅かれ早かれ戦争になるに決まってる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7216
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_832ae5b3:

    # "And really, when Emi appears to have far better aim than me, well…"
    "それに、笑美は狙うのが俺よりずっとうまいみたいで、だから……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7218
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5875d971:

    # "It was just a matter of time before I'd have to resort to a suicidal charge."
    "捨て身の攻撃を強いられるようになるのは時間の問題だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7229
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b0d74d7c:

    # hi "Gotcha!"
    hi "つかまえた！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7234
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5c74aadc:

    # emi "Eep!"
    emi "きゃあ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7269
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_07072cc3:

    # "And once the charge was accomplished, well, of course I'd have to wrestle the pillows away from her."
    "そして一度捨て身の攻撃が成功したら、まあ、枕を取り上げるのに取っ組み合いすることになるのは当然で。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7271
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ee374098:

    # "And with that kind of struggle, of course we'd wind up in this sort of position."
    "そんなふうにやりあってれば、しまいにはこんな体勢になっちゃうのも当然だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7282
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_755636cf:

    # "And so I find myself staring down at her from my position atop her."
    "そうして俺は、自分が笑美に乗りかかって見下ろしているのに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7284
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_66702d6f:

    # "She's grinning, eyes sparkling with amusement, maybe a little sweaty now from our tussle."
    "笑美は笑っていて、目はおかしそうにきらきらしている。今のじゃれあいでちょっと汗ばんでいるかも。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7286
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_05323cc8:

    # "Her chest is heaving up and down, sucking in air."
    "笑美の胸が上下に動き、空気を吸っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7288
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ecd4247f:

    # "The small bit of my brain that is not currently enraptured by the sight and the smell of her observes that she must still be ill, because her stamina's not what it should be."
    "いまのところはこの光景や匂いにとらわれていない俺の頭のほんの一部分が、笑美はまだ調子悪いな、と分析する。笑美のスタミナはこんなものじゃないはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7290
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_2d909687:

    # "We stay that way for a while."
    "俺たちはしばらくそのままでいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7292
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_8cee9218:

    # "I'm not sure how long, because everything seems to go fuzzy. Everything that isn't her, anyway."
    "どれくらい長い間かわからない。すべてがぼやけているみたいだ。笑美以外のすべてが、だけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7294
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5e7e078d:

    # "Her eyes meet mine, and deep inside them I almost catch a glimpse of… what, fear? Longing?"
    "笑美と目が合って、その奥にはかすかな……なんだろう、恐れ？　愛しさ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7296
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_12bdd339:

    # "Hope?"
    "希望？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7298
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4932c45f:

    # hi "Emi…?"
    hi "笑美……？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7305
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a725250c:

    # "A cough suddenly convulses her, and I'm almost stumbling in my haste to get off, to apologize for everything."
    "咳が突然笑美の体を震わせる。俺はいろいろ謝ろうとして、ほとんど転げ落ちるような勢いで笑美から離れる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7309
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_aedd61b5:

    # hi "Sorry, I shouldn't have…"
    hi "ごめん、こんなことはしちゃ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7314
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3dd87fd4:

    # emi "It's fine, it's fine."
    emi "平気、へいき"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7316
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3ae69760:

    # "She gives me a reassuring pat on the shoulder."
    "笑美は安心させるように俺の肩をたたく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7321
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_d73512f3:

    # emi "So… what brings you here?"
    emi "で……なんでここに来たの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7323
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f2d9fe58:

    # "She's still breathing hard, and that causes her voice to shake slightly."
    "笑美はまだ荒い息をしていて、そのせいで声が少し震えている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7325
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_82595690:

    # hi "Well, before I was so rudely assaulted by pillows, I came to see how you were doing."
    hi "ええと、枕でいきなりやられる前は、笑美がどうしてるか見に来たんだけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7342
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_48ee4bb9:

    # "This earns me another shove, and I very nearly fall off her bed."
    "俺はもう一度突き飛ばされて、笑美のベッドから落ちかける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7347
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_2a2f4794:

    # "Emi's eyes sparkle again, and I wonder how I never noticed how attractive they are before."
    "笑美の目がまた輝き始める。それがこんなに魅力的なことに、どうして今まで気づかなかったんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7352
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_2cfb1de9:

    # emi "Consumed with worry, were you?"
    emi "心配でたまらなかったんでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7354
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b985fd9e:

    # "Her tone is mocking, haughty. Teasing."
    "馬鹿にしているような、えらそうな調子だ。からかってるな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7356
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c137796b:

    # "She throws her arm across her forehead dramatically, grin still apparent from underneath."
    "笑美は芝居がかったしぐさで額に腕を置いて、その下からはっきりと笑顔を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7361
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_660c5a88:

    # emi "Couldn't bear the thought of me laying deathly ill?"
    emi "あたしが病気で死にそうになって寝込んでいるなんて思うと耐えられなかった？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7363
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_dd7dace3:

    # "As we both recover from our brief wrestling match, Emi appears to fall back on teasing me."
    "俺たち二人でさっきの格闘戦から回復する間、笑美は俺をからかうことにしたようだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7365
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ebec6404:

    # hi "Well, I wouldn't say consumed with worry, but after you didn't show up this morning like a total wuss…"
    hi "まあ、心配でたまらなかったとは言わないけど、今朝、笑美が弱虫みたいに出てこなかった後ではね……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7370
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_1d7bc5fa:

    # "Emi pouts, crossing her arms petulantly and sticking her lower lip out."
    "笑美は拗ねる。不機嫌そうに腕を組んで下唇を突き出している。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7372
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_1cc1bd9a:

    # emi "It's not my fault."
    emi "あたしのせいじゃないもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7374
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f408f7df:

    # emi "Nurse wouldn't allow it."
    emi "ナースくんがだめだって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7376
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_d2f42122:

    # hi "Sure he wouldn't. I completely believe you."
    hi "そうだろうさ。笑美を信じるよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7378
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_de7084b1:

    # "Emi sticks her tongue out again."
    "笑美はまた舌を出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7380
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_14a1acc7:

    # emi "You're such a jerk, Hisao."
    emi "久夫くん、最っ低"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7382
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c4d6eced:

    # hi "So how was your day then, eh? Did you enjoy slacking off?"
    hi "で、今日はどうだった？　さぼりを満喫したか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7387
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c641e61b:

    # emi "Not really, the phone woke me up pretty early on."
    emi "そうでもないよ、電話でけっこう早く起こされちゃったし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7389
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ac2d8ba8:

    # hi "The phone?"
    hi "電話？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7391
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ce28f319:

    # emi "Yeah, the captain of the team called to make sure I was doing okay."
    emi "そう、陸上部の部長が大丈夫かって電話してきたの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7393
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_141b3331:

    # emi "Also to let me know it was okay to skip practice."
    emi "あと練習休んでいいって"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7395
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_212a70b5:

    # "Good, at least she wasn't alone all day. Someone checked up on her."
    "よかった、少なくとも一日中ひとりじゃなかったんだ。誰かが確認をしたんだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7397
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_56069f9d:

    # "Although I can't help but think that it should have been me."
    "でも、そうすべきなのは俺だったという考えが止まらない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7399
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_54aa636c:

    # hi "Oh, that's good."
    hi "ああ、それはよかった"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7401
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f80aef76:

    # hi "He really keeps an eye on you, huh?"
    hi "笑美のこと本当に気にしてるんだな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7406
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_18357699:

    # "Emi shrugs."
    "笑美は肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7408
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_7ba4d731:

    # emi "It's his job."
    emi "それが仕事だもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7410
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_696d22ee:

    # emi "Part of being the captain means you know where your team members are when they're not in school."
    emi "メンバーが学校にいないときにどこにいるかを知っておくのも、部長の役目の一つだから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7412
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_dcfbe713:

    # emi "Still, I guess it was nice of him to call, huh?"
    emi "でも、電話くれたのって親切だよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7414
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f017c3ce:

    # hi "Yep. Sure was."
    hi "うん。そうだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7416
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_7b08d651:

    # "Emi yawns and shimmies down into a more comfortable position."
    "笑美はあくびをしながら少し楽な姿勢になった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7421
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5b5aa4f4:

    # emi "So how was your day?"
    emi "で、久夫くん今日はどうだった？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7423
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5887a7ef:

    # hi "Kind of uneventful, you know?"
    hi "まあ平凡なもんだったね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7425
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_66f235b5:

    # hi "I went ahead and ran by myself, and talked with the nurse about how you were doing…"
    hi "ひとりで行って自分で走って、笑美がどうしてるかナースと話して……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7432
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5b83f0ef:

    # "I meander through the day's events, none of which are particularly engrossing."
    "特に面白くもない今日のできごとを、だらだらとあれこれ話す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7434
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_17329eaa:

    # "That's when I'm distracted by an arm finding its way across my waist."
    "ふと気づくと笑美の腕が俺の腰にあって、話が止まってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7436
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_cbfd9c53:

    # "It seems that Emi fell asleep while I was talking so I draw her blanket to cover us."
    "話している間に寝てしまったみたいなので、毛布を引っぱって二人いっしょにかける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7443
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3d6efdcb:

    # "She's rolled over on to her side, and now one leg is thrown over my legs, effectively trapping me."
    "笑美が寝返りを打つと、片足が俺の足の上に投げ出され、ほぼ身動きがとれなくなってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7445
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_20a67d9a:

    # hi "Hey."
    hi "なあ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7447
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_747bc777:

    # "It seems a shame to wake her, but I have things to do."
    "起こすのも気の毒だけど、しなきゃいけないことがあるしな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7451
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_de921d83:

    # "I gently shake her, but in response she only tightens her arm's grip on me and sighs a little."
    "俺はそっと笑美を揺さぶるけど、もっと強く抱きしめられて、ちょっとため息をつかれただけだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7453
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_425d6471:

    # "My resistance to this position crumbles rather quickly."
    "俺の抵抗はずいぶんあっさり砕け散った。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7455
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3832a633:

    # "The feeling of her body breathing steadily is both calming and incredibly stimulating at the same time."
    "笑美がゆっくりと息をしているのを感じるのは、落ち着くと同時に、信じられないほど刺激的だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7457
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a887bfd1:

    # "My breathing cannot decide if it wants to relax or speed up."
    "自分の呼吸も静まりたいんだか早まりたいんだかわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7459
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0d158b40:

    # "Relaxation wins, and I find myself putting an arm around Emi."
    "結局安心感が勝ち、俺は笑美に腕を回していた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7464
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_e3c94eb3:

    # hi "I think I'm in love."
    hi "好きかも"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7466
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b7b9e9ee:

    # "The words slip out and hang in the air unnoticed."
    "漏れた言葉が、気づかれないまま宙に漂う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7468
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5fd52044:

    # "At least I hope they've gone unnoticed."
    "少なくとも今のは気づかれないまま消えてほしい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7473
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0681d79e:

    # "Emi whimpers weakly through her dream, and her grip suddenly tightens again."
    "笑美は夢の中で弱々しく涙ぐんで、またぎゅっと抱きしめてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7475
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0d0b2460:

    # "For the first time since I've known her, I see tears running down Emi's face."
    "笑美に会ってから初めて、笑美の顔に涙が流れるのを見た。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7477
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_93dd11d0:

    # "It feels like my heart is about to break."
    "心臓が壊れてしまいそうな気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7479
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_17bdcb30:

    # "I instinctively tighten my own grip and stroke her hair in what I hope is a soothing manner."
    "俺は思わず抱きしめ返して、落ちつかせるように笑美の髪をなでる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7481
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_1b01371e:

    # "Words of comfort, meaningless in this situation, spring to mind."
    "こんな状況では意味のない慰めの言葉が、頭に浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7483
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0e158b35:

    # "Maybe I should wake her. Are you supposed to wake people having nightmares?"
    "起こしたほうがいいのかも。悪い夢を見ている人って起こすものなんだっけ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7485
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_7f74854a:

    # "I can't for the life of me remember."
    "どうしてもそれが思い出せない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7487
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_e9883e49:

    # "The decision is taken from me as Emi suddenly jerks awake with a cry."
    "笑美が突然叫んで目を覚ましたのに驚いて、それどころではなくなる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7492
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_21a67a0f:

    # emi "Dad!"
    emi "パパ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7494
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c218ccde:

    # "This is… more than I think I want to hear without her knowing. I quickly sit upright and gently shake her shoulder to stir her."
    "これは……俺が聞いたことを笑美が知らないままにできる話じゃないと思う。俺はさっと起き上がって、笑美をちゃんと起こすように肩を優しく揺さぶる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7499
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4b3de8b2:

    # hi "Hey, you okay?"
    hi "おい、大丈夫か？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7501
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c1a18342:

    # "What a silly question."
    "なんともまぬけな質問だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7506
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_20863c68:

    # emi "Huh? What?"
    emi "へ？　なに？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7511
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a18df911:

    # emi "Hisao?"
    emi "久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7513
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_83625526:

    # "She shakes her head as if to clear it and quickly wipes her eyes."
    "笑美は何かを払いのけるように頭を振って、さっと涙をぬぐった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7515
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_61382e86:

    # hi "You had a nightmare. I think."
    hi "悪い夢でも見たんだよ。たぶん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7520
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ff04155e:

    # "Emi shudders again and glances up at me a little cautiously, as if unsure whether or not she's actually up."
    "笑美はまた震えて、少し怖がった様子でちらっと俺を見上げる。自分が本当に起きているのかどうかわからないみたいに。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7522
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4b84c74d:

    # emi "Y-yeah, I guess so."
    emi "う、うん。そうみたいだね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7524
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3f4a33df:

    # hi "You wanna talk about it?"
    hi "話してみる？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7526
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_19972527:

    # emi "Hmm?"
    emi "へっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7528
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_d9326b4f:

    # "A speedy internal debate seems to be going on in her head, which resolves itself with a shrug."
    "頭の中でめまぐるしく行われているらしい議論が、肩をすくめることで終わる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7533
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_9dedb4a6:

    # emi "Nah, I don't really remember much of it."
    emi "いいよ、あんまり覚えてないし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7535
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ef6f08ad:

    # "I'm pretty sure she's lying to me, but somehow I don't think I should press the issue."
    "嘘をついているのは見え見えだけど、なぜか、深入りはしないほうがいいと思った。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7540
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0ce28ae2:

    # "Emi shudders again and turns toward me, looking a little sheepish."
    "笑美はまた震えてこっちを見る。少し恥ずかしそうな顔だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7542
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ec47b8ac:

    # emi "Sorry for falling asleep on you like that."
    emi "あんなふうに寝ちゃってごめんね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7544
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b47e375f:

    # "I keep my voice as soothing as I can."
    "俺はできるだけ安心させるような声のまま言う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7546
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_69393502:

    # hi "Hey, don't worry about it. You've been ill."
    hi "いや、気にするなよ。病み上がりだし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7548
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_58e8e0b4:

    # emi "Yeah, I guess that cold medicine's just made me a little drowsy."
    emi "うん、あの風邪薬で少し眠くなっちゃったみたい"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7550
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_92de4009:

    # hi "I guess so."
    hi "みたいだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7552
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_d2290dc9:

    # "Emi does not strike me as the sort of person who'd fall asleep at the drop of a hat."
    "笑美はあんなにあっという間に寝るようなタイプには見えない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7554
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a8271bf0:

    # "Rin, maybe. But Emi's far too energetic."
    "琳ならそうなるのかもしれないけど、笑美は活発すぎる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7559
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_06f18373:

    # "Emi gives a half-smile at my response, and then just like that she's back to her old self."
    "笑美は俺の返事に半笑いを浮かべて、そしてあっけなく元の笑美に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7564
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0d805659:

    # emi "Well, prepare yourself for tomorrow morning Hisao!"
    emi "じゃあ、久夫くんはちゃんと明日に備えること！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7569
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3829ca07:

    # emi "We'll have to go twice as hard to make up for today!"
    emi "二人とも今日の分を取り戻すために二倍がんばらなきゃいけないからね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7571
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b3d7bc56:

    # hi "But I went running this morning!"
    hi "俺は今朝走りに行ったぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7576
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_11c4476e:

    # emi "No excuse!"
    emi "言いわけしない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7578
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4bf91997:

    # hi "Oh fine, I'll be ready for you!"
    hi "わかったよ、覚悟しておくよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7583
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_aa9844f1:

    # "Emi nods, satisfied."
    "笑美は満足げにうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7585
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_481d5cf5:

    # emi "Good."
    emi "よし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7587
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_aec6ec4f:

    # "I take this as my cue to exit."
    "それを、ここを出るきっかけにする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7589
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_eeee8aa0:

    # hi "Well, I'd better get going. Especially if I want to get enough sleep for tomorrow."
    hi "じゃ、俺はもう行ったほうがいいな。明日のためによく寝ておこうっていうなら、なおさらな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7594
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4d40ead6:

    # "I hop off the bed and head for the door."
    "俺はベッドから飛び降りてドアへ向かう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7599
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a39497ad:

    # emi "Hey, Hisao…"
    emi "ねえ、久夫くん……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7601
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7603
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_00cf1d24:

    # "I pivot neatly on my heel and face Emi."
    "俺はきれいに回れ右して笑美のほうを向く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7608
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b6fcb4bc:

    # "She opens her mouth to say something, and then in another first, I see her falter slightly."
    "笑美は何かを言いかけて口を開き、それをもう一度繰り返す。少しためらっているのがわかる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7610
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_c8ab8658:

    # "She closes her mouth and opens it again."
    "口を閉じて、また開く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7615
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_e49af0b9:

    # emi "…Thanks."
    emi "……ありがとう"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7617
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_fb780ae8:

    # emi "For dropping by, I mean."
    emi "その、来てくれて"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7619
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_6344dfa0:

    # emi "You're kind of the first visitor I've ever had who wasn't Rin."
    emi "琳以外で部屋に来てくれたのは久夫くんが初めてなんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7621
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_13b2d47a:

    # "Now that's surprising. I would figure that Emi'd have people dropping by all the time."
    "これには驚いた。笑美なら誰かがいつも来ているものだと思っていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7623
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ede4a31a:

    # "She's certainly popular enough, or so I thought. Always talking to people in the hallways."
    "笑美は人気者のはず、だと思っていた。いつも廊下で誰かと話している。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7628
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_630f8aae:

    # "Emi hesitates again."
    "笑美はまた躊躇する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7630
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4f57fdca:

    # emi "And thanks for staying around after I… well."
    emi "あと、あの後もいてくれてありがとね、あたしが……えっと"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7635
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_972601e9:

    # "A look of pain flits across her face."
    "表情に痛みがよぎる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7637
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_a662fcab:

    # emi "You know."
    emi "その"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7642
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ccec68ab:

    # emi "It helped."
    emi "たすかった"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7647
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_83ed0d12:

    # "She brightens back up and waves cheerily at me."
    "笑美はまた明るい表情に戻って元気に手を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7649
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f7f342fd:

    # emi "See you tomorrow!"
    emi "また明日ね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7651
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_0dbc8435:

    # hi "Yeah, see you later."
    hi "ああ、またな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7653
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b215cc7c:

    # "I'm just about to exit the door when something makes me turn around again."
    "部屋から出ようとしたけど、何かが俺をまた振り向かせる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7655
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_7312930a:

    # hi "Hey, Emi."
    hi "なあ、笑美"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7660
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_19972527_1:

    # emi "Hmm?"
    emi "へっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7662
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_d37878cf:

    # hi "Anytime you need to talk, let me know, okay?"
    hi "もし何か話したいことがあったら、言ってくれよ、な？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7667
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3ef41a6f:

    # "Emi seems taken aback by this offer."
    "この言葉に笑美はびっくりしたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7672
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_be2f29bd:

    # "Her grin gets even wider."
    "笑美の笑い顔がさらに広がる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7674
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_65344442:

    # emi "Sure thing, Hisao."
    emi "わかったよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7679
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_5af7dcf0:

    # emi "See you in the morning!"
    emi "また明日の朝にね！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7684
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_b9e91565:

    # "I exit Emi's room with my head in a whirl."
    "頭が混乱したまま笑美の部屋を出る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7686
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_06455ca0:

    # "Should I have even left?"
    "ほんとうに出てくるべきだったのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7688
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_3e3dda2b:

    # "Was she really okay?"
    "ほんとうに笑美は大丈夫なんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7690
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_f44a8fc1:

    # "I want to turn around and march back down the hallway, open the door and tell her…"
    "引き返して廊下を戻って、ドアを開けて、笑美に……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7694
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7698
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_841527aa:

    # n "{vspace=60}Tell her I love her, tell her I think she's beautiful, tell her that I'll be there when she needs me."
    n "\n\n好きだと伝えたい、きれいだと思っていると伝えたい、必要な時はそばにいると伝えたい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7700
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_7a809be3:

    # n "I want to stay with her, to hold her close as she falls back to sleep."
    n "いっしょにいたい、笑美がまた眠るまでそばで抱きしめていたい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7702
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_6879110b:

    # n "How many nights has she woken up like that?"
    n "笑美はどれだけの夜をあんなふうに過ごしたんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7704
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_38920d78:

    # n "Only to find that nobody's there."
    n "目が覚めても誰もいないと気づくだけで。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7706
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_53d16df2:

    # n "I want to be that person she can be with when that happens."
    n "そんなことがあったとき、いっしょにいられる人になりたい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7708
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_94309e21:

    # n "It's a silly thought, I know."
    n "ばかげた考えなのは、知っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7710
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ff796171:

    # n "We don't know each other that well, do we?"
    n "まだそんなにお互いのことを知らないのに？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7712
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_48ca31f9:

    # n "The whole idea, while exhilarating, also makes me feel worry."
    n "それらの考えが、気分をうわつかせるけど、不安にもさせる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7714
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_6b27b717:

    # n "Worry, perhaps, that I'd overstep my bounds."
    n "心配、なのかもしれない。踏み込みすぎじゃないのかって。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7716
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_491db9bc:

    # n "And now to add to my troubles, it seems as if Emi herself already has an interest in someone else."
    n "さらにやっかいなことに、笑美はもう他の誰かに興味を持っているように思える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7718
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_337ed761:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=180}This track captain of hers who seems so interested in her well-being."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n笑美の健康状態にやけにご執心の、例の陸上部の部長。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7722
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_da79a3c9:

    # n "True, I've only seen the two of them together a few times, but that doesn't change the fact that they seem better suited to one another."
    n "確かに、そいつが笑美と二人でいるのを見たことは数回しかないけど、二人がお似合いっぽいことに変わりはない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7724
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_372e8aa4:

    # n "There's really nothing to be done about that."
    n "それについては何もできることはない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7726
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_d7596770:

    # n "I need to take my mind off of this whole situation."
    n "どうにかしてこの状況から気をそらさないといけない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7730
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7734
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_ff4cbdea:

    # "I've got homework to do."
    "宿題やんなきゃな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7736
translate jp a2_emi_dropping_by_4c9cc1da:

    # "Maybe that will distract me."
    "それで気も紛れるかも。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7754
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_06c9ea85:

    # "A night of restlessness has left me feeling fairly groggy this morning."
    "眠れない夜のせいで今朝はけっこうふらふらだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7758
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_121d5b92:

    # "The events of the previous day keep intruding upon my mind."
    "前日のできごとが頭の中に割り込み続けている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7760
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_be702d91:

    # "The memory of how Emi felt against me."
    "俺によりかかる、笑美の感触の記憶。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7762
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b0bdae75:

    # "The memory of our wrestling match."
    "俺と笑美の取っ組み合いの記憶。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7764
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_f2a466b7:

    # "And most bothersome, the memory of her nightmare."
    "そしていちばんやっかいな、笑美の悪夢の記憶。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7766
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_2996566d:

    # "She was in so much pain."
    "笑美はとても苦しんでいた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7768
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_04db8264:

    # "I can't stop wondering what it must be like for her to wake up with nobody there."
    "目が覚めても誰もいないなんてどんな感じなんだろうと思わずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7776
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_657182bf:

    # "The shower shocks me awake with hot water. Awake, but still worried."
    "シャワーの熱いお湯で目が覚める。目は覚めたけど、心配だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7783
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_85c0a972:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=30}What will happen today?"
    nvl clear
    n "\n今日は何が起こるのだろう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7787
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_2dd34a53:

    # n "Will things just go back to normal?"
    n "全部普段どおりに戻るだけなのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7789
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_aec40269:

    # n "End of the episode, back to the status quo?"
    n "あの話はあれで終わって、今までどおりに？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7791
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_98ec3b16:

    # n "There was a connection yesterday. Something that nearly pushed us past the boundaries of normal friendship."
    n "昨日はつながりがあった。二人の関係を、それまでのただの友情という一線から押し出しそうになった何かが。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7793
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_9b86fe37:

    # n "Would that have been so bad?"
    n "それはそんなに悪いことだったのだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7795
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_5dd6681b:

    # n "My mind goes back to the look in Emi's eyes after our pillowfight. It almost seemed like she was daring me to go on."
    n "枕投げの後で見た笑美の目を思い出す。あれはまるで、もっと踏み込むよう俺を挑発しているように見えた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7797
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_c5c9d4a5:

    # n "Almost."
    n "たぶん。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7799
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_51372aa3:

    # n "But I can't know for sure."
    n "でも確信はない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7801
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d833d4ec:

    # n "Anyway, the track captain's probably first in her affections."
    n "とにかく、笑美が一番お気に入りなのは陸上部の部長なんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7803
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d0ea5122:

    # n "But even as I say that, my mind is already snorting derisively. I'm just looking for an excuse. A reason for everything to go wrong."
    n "そう思いながらも、俺の意識はあざけるように鼻を鳴らしている。自分は言いわけを探しているだけだ。とにかくうまくいかない理由を。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7805
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_8033b3d4:

    # n "A reason to not try."
    n "挑戦しない理由を。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7807
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_76debfb8:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=120}It's not as if I've even seen the two of them together outside of track practice."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n部活の練習の時以外に二人でいるところを見たわけでもない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7811
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_188e73c1:

    # n "And clearly he's never visited. Emi said as much herself. If they were close, surely he'd visit."
    n "そして彼が笑美のところに行ったことがないのは明らかだ。笑美自身が言っていた。もし仲が良かったら、訪ねているはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7813
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_31d6c62c:

    # n "I'm such a wuss."
    n "ほんとに臆病者だな、俺は。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7815
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7fadfb5b:

    # n "I ought to just go for it anyway, damn the consequences."
    n "とにかくやってみりゃいいんだ、結末なんて知ったことか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7817
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_1c6315db:

    # n "That's what Emi would do, I think. Hell, I {b}know{/b} that's what she'd do."
    n "笑美ならやるだろう、と思う。そうだ、笑美なら{b}絶対に{/b}やるに決まってる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7819
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_09179b1a:

    # n "Which is partially why I'm convinced there's no interest on her end. She hasn't acted either."
    n "笑美が俺に興味がないと確信する理由の一つがそれだ。笑美だって何も行動を起こしていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7821
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_db627a2e:

    # n "Maybe because of this track captain. It's possible she's got a bit of an unrequited crush thing going on."
    n "それは陸上部の部長のせいなのかもしれない。報われない片思いの恋みたいな状態なのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7823
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_ad5d1819:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=180}But who would be able to clarify their relationship?"
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\nでも誰があの二人の関係をはっきりとさせられるんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7827
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a49cbcba:

    # n "It sure as hell can't be Emi. She'd probably just laugh and ask why I wanted to know… and I'm not ready to answer that yet."
    n "笑美には聞けるわけがない。たぶん笑美はただ笑って、どうして知りたいのかと聞いてくるだけだ……そして答える準備はできていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7829
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_baf5f781:

    # n "Rin… Rin would probably just give me some cryptic answer or something. And then with my luck, she'd just ask Emi, who would ask me why I wanted to know, and I've already covered that problem."
    n "琳……琳ならたぶん謎めいた返事かなにかをするだけだろう。それに下手をすると、琳は直接笑美に聞いて、笑美はなぜ俺がそんなことを知りたいのか聞いてくるんだ。これについてはもう検討済みだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7831
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_e1ae3ba5:

    # n "I wonder…"
    n "もしかしたら……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7833
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d94c114c:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=150}Could I get away with asking the nurse? He seems pretty protective of Emi. I'm sure he'd know if something was up…"
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n\nナースに聞けばどうにかなるか？　笑美をとても気遣っているように見える。もしなにかあったら知っているはず……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7837
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_481a6a27:

    # n "And he owes me for not letting Emi know he forgot to tell me about her being ill, so he'll keep quiet."
    n "それに笑美が病気だったことを俺に伝えなかったという貸しがあるから、黙っているだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7839
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d5ce5d8f:

    # n "What if he asks me why I want to know, though?"
    n "でも、もしなぜ俺が知りたがっているかを聞いてきたらどうする？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7841
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_32591f86:

    # n "I can shake him off. Just say I'm curious as a friend. He'll buy that, won't he?"
    n "なんとかごまかせるな。友達として気になると言うだけだ。それで納得するだろう、するよな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7843
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a685f116:

    # n "Of course!"
    n "するだろ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7845
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_9f1bffba:

    # n "That's settled, then."
    n "じゃあ、これで解決だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7847
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7098156e:

    # n "After the run, I'll talk to him while Emi's waiting outside the office."
    n "走った後で、笑美が医務室の外で待っている間に話そう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7851
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7860
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_4d486ea3:

    # n "{vspace=120}There's no sign of Emi when I arrive at the track. Is she still too ill?"
    n "\n\n\n\n俺がトラックに来ても笑美がいる様子はない。まだ具合が悪いんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7862
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_959e5ffe:

    # n "I decide to give her ten minutes."
    n "十分ほど待つことにする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7864
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7e6afbd6:

    # n "I'm a little early, and she was ill yesterday, so if she takes a while to show up it shouldn't be surprising."
    n "俺は早めに着いているし、笑美は昨日風邪を引いていたので、ここに来るのに時間が掛かっても不思議じゃない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7866
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_ab68624b:

    # n "Still, I'd hate to just waste my time, so I occupy myself by stretching and pacing back and forth anxiously."
    n "でも、時間を無駄にするのも嫌で、結局ストレッチをしたり不安でうろうろしたりする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7868
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_bfcb5e98:

    # n "What if I went too far yesterday?"
    n "もし昨日自分がやり過ぎていたらどうしよう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7870
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b25ea60b:

    # n "What if she doesn't come because she's embarrassed?"
    n "もし笑美が恥ずかしがって来なかったらどうしよう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7872
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_fab85d57:

    # n "What if…"
    n "もし……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7877
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7886
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_3fb6275e:

    # emi "You're early again, Hisao!"
    emi "今日も早いね、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7891
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_3e7ff356:

    # emi "I'm impressed!"
    emi "感心感心！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7893
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_41d98294:

    # "Just like that, I feel some of the tension leaving my body."
    "あっけなく、身体から緊張がいくらか抜けていくのを感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7895
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_c5d25ae0:

    # "Emi seems to be bright and cheerful as usual, with no sign that she even was ill the other day, much less had a less-than-restful sleep."
    "笑美はいつもどおり明るく元気そうで、昨日まで寝込んでいたそぶりも見せないどころか、眠れぬ夜を過ごしたなんてこともなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7897
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_1b46bbbc:

    # "Still, I have to ask."
    "でも、聞かなきゃいけない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7899
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7a9d21da:

    # hi "Sleep well last night?"
    hi "昨日はよく眠れたか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7903
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_4b5ca971:

    # "It's just a throwaway question. Small talk."
    "ただの、その場だけの質問だ。雑談だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7905
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_86ab043d:

    # "The sort of thing people ask someone they bump into in the café while getting their morning coffee."
    "喫茶店で朝のコーヒーを注文していたら知り合いにばったり会ったようなときにするようなものだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7907
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b0eb03c2:

    # "But not for us. At least, not for me."
    "でも俺たちの間では違う。少なくとも、俺にとっては。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7909
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b230b862:

    # "I don't know if Emi realizes that I'm actually concerned about how well she slept last night, but the question does give her pause."
    "笑美が昨日よく寝られたかを俺が本気で心配していることに気づいたかはわからないけど、その質問で笑美は一瞬止まった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7914
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_8674f693:

    # "After a short moment of what seems like her genuinely pondering this, she nods."
    "しばらくしっかりと考え込んだように思えるような間の後、笑美はうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7919
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a51bbd10:

    # emi "Yep! Sure did!"
    emi "うん！　もちろん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7921
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_69e77971:

    # "Was it because of me?"
    "俺のおかげか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7923
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_2928f9d3:

    # "Did I actually help?"
    "俺は本当に助けになったのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7925
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_0371afc3:

    # "Or are you just saying that to get me to stop asking questions?"
    "それとも俺の質問をやめさせるためにそう言っているだけなのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7927
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a9e9c2b9:

    # hi "Good to hear."
    hi "そりゃよかった"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7932
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_14483e75:

    # "Emi grins and begins warming up."
    "笑美は笑って準備運動を始めた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7937
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_6bb65f85:

    # emi "So, ready to begin?"
    emi "それで、始める準備はいい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7939
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_3c0303f3:

    # hi "Pfft, am I ready? Of course I'm ready! I was born ready!"
    hi "ふっ、準備はいいかって？　もちろんいいよ！　生まれたときからＯＫさ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7944
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7e92ac70:

    # "Emi laughs at my bravado, and we take off running."
    "笑美は俺の見栄に笑って、二人で走り始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7949
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7802c46e:

    # "I keep a steady pace the whole time, breathing steadily."
    "俺はずっと一定のペースで走り、一定のペースで呼吸をする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7954
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_95b7b89f:

    # "I still feel dead at the end, but at least I don't gasp like a fish out of water now."
    "走り終えたら死んだような気分にはなるけど、水から上がった魚みたいに息を切らす事はもうなくなった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7964
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_994a54dd:

    # "Emi is positively beaming after the run today."
    "今日の笑美は走り終わってからとても晴れやかな顔をしている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7966
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_ea7cbf15:

    # emi "Nice job, Hisao! You're improving!"
    emi "よくやったね、久夫くん！　進歩してるよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7971
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_14870a8d:

    # emi "You'll be half as fast as me in no time!"
    emi "もうすぐあたしの半分ぐらいの速さになれるよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7973
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_ac9d510e:

    # "This last line is delivered with a teasing grin that I've grown all too used to."
    "最後の台詞は俺もすっかり慣れてしまった、からかうような笑顔で言った。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7975
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_07d40820:

    # hi "Oh, how exciting."
    hi "ああ、それは楽しみだな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7986
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_562d3bc4:

    # "Emi begins to run her sprints while I take a cool-down lap."
    "俺がクールダウンするあいだに、笑美は全力で走り始めた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7988
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_6d032046:

    # "She's really pushing herself today."
    "今日はやけに頑張っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7997
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_44c0b47e:

    # "By the time I'm done with my lap, she's laying across one of the bleachers, looking exhausted."
    "俺がクールダウンを終えると、笑美は疲れ切ったみたいにベンチで横になっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:7999
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7ffd0a2f:

    # hi "Goodness, not pushing it a little too much today, are you?"
    hi "おいおい、今日はちょっと頑張りすぎてないか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8001
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_8402747c:

    # hi "You did just have a cold, you'll recall."
    hi "風邪ひいてたんだぞ、覚えてるだろ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8006
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_17742603:

    # "Emi gives an annoyed snort and sits up."
    "笑美は鼻を鳴らして起き上がる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8008
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_6c60b568:

    # emi "Bah! I'm just trying to make up for lost time, that's all."
    emi "ふん！　遅れた分を取り返そうとしてるだけだもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8013
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_22333fd8:

    # emi "I went twice as hard today, you know."
    emi "今日はいつもの二倍がんばったんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8018
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b55284e6:

    # emi "A good run always gets the kinks out, you know."
    emi "いい走りをするとすっきりするんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8023
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_9d76e97a:

    # emi "Clears the mind, too."
    emi "頭もはっきりするし、ね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8025
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_f9075882:

    # hi "Oh?"
    hi "ほう？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8030
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_6ec5217f:

    # "Emi nods vigorously."
    "笑美は元気よくうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8035
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_86af1619:

    # emi "Yep! It's a great outlet for that sort of thing."
    emi "うん！　そういうのを解消するには最高なんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8037
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_99cccf62:

    # "She does not explain further, and I don't ask."
    "笑美はそれ以上説明しないし、俺も聞かない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8039
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_4897b1d8:

    # "I suspect I know the real reason she went so hard today."
    "笑美が今日はあんなにがむしゃらになった本当の理由を知っている気がする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8041
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b14126fa:

    # "Being sick had nothing to do with it. Something's bothering her."
    "風邪だったことは関係ない。何かが気になっているんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8043
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a5bfef6f:

    # "Maybe the nightmare. Maybe something else."
    "もしかしたらあの悪夢なのかもしれない。もしかしたら他のことかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8045
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_c973726d:

    # "But it's not my place to pry."
    "でもそれは俺が首を突っ込むところじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8047
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_fef62c52:

    # "She'd tell me if she wanted me to know."
    "もし知ってほしいなら向こうから言ってくるはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8049
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_603631d7:

    # hi "I'm sure that comes in handy."
    hi "そりゃ便利だな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8054
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_456da2cc:

    # emi "You have no idea."
    emi "久夫くんにはわからないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8056
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_c9caf9ff:

    # "The sincerity in her voice confirms my suspicion."
    "その声の正直さが俺の疑いを裏付ける。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8058
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_4314f904:

    # "The only problem is…"
    "ここで問題がひとつ……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8060
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_df3d253f:

    # "Even though I know she'd tell me if she wanted me to know, I still want to know."
    "俺に知ってほしかったら笑美が話すだろうけど、それでも俺は知りたい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8062
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_5288d787:

    # hi "Something on your mind, then?"
    hi "じゃあ、なにか悩みでもあるのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8064
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_822d4258:

    # "Emi doesn't seem surprised by my question."
    "笑美は俺の質問に驚いた様子はない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8069
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_5a5581e5:

    # "Instead, she shrugs."
    "かわりに、肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8074
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_afc5700f:

    # emi "Nah, it's nothing worth getting worried about."
    emi "んーん、心配するようなことじゃないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8076
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_20db812c:

    # "She seems as if she's trying to convince herself as much as she's convincing me."
    "まるで、俺への説得と同じくらい、自分にも納得させようとしているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8078
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_6775c31f:

    # "I open my mouth to ask if yesterday is responsible for her current state of mind, but think better of it."
    "そんな気持ちになるのは昨日のことのせいなのかと聞こうと思って俺は口を開きかけるけど、考え直してやめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8080
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_73e9cd77:

    # "Too much risk of her taking the question the wrong way."
    "その質問を笑美が変なほうに受け取るリスクが高すぎる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8082
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_673197a9:

    # "Besides, I'm not even sure myself what to think about yesterday."
    "それに、自分でも昨日のことをどう考えたらいいのかわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8084
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_0f0d6003:

    # "Really I can only get about as far as how it felt to have Emi sleeping next to me before my brain shuts down."
    "隣で寝ている笑美の感触を思い出そうとすると脳がシャットダウンしてしまうのが本当のところだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8086
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7e066615:

    # "Having her before me now, covered in sweat and looking wryly at me, she's making it difficult to think."
    "汗まみれのまま顔をしかめてこっちを見ている笑美を前にすると、考えるのが難しくなる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8088
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_2a5381ea:

    # hi "Yeah, I hear you."
    hi "ああ、そうか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8093
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_83cf391c:

    # emi "We'd better hurry to see the nurse. We're running short on time."
    emi "急いでナースくんのところに行ったほうがいいね。時間もなくなっちゃってるし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8095
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_27d97058:

    # hi "Aren't we always?"
    hi "いつもそうじゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8100
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_7e0e22f5:

    # "Emi laughs at this, a dry chuckle that seems most un-Emi-like."
    "笑美が笑う。一番笑美らしくない乾いた笑いだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8105
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_392c39aa:

    # emi "Too true."
    emi "ほんと、そうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8107
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_c0fe8064:

    # "For a brief moment, she looks old, worn down by some old hurt."
    "ほんの一瞬、笑美は古傷で衰えてしまったかのように、老いて見えた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8109
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_cce4c4c8:

    # "But just like yesterday I can almost see her shouldering the burden and straightening up slightly."
    "でも昨日のように、重荷を背負って、か細くても真っすぐに立っているように思える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8111
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_13a1fed1:

    # "And then she's back to being Emi again."
    "そして笑美はいつも通りに戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8116
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_703d23af:

    # emi "Come on then Hisao. Race ya!"
    emi "じゃ行くよ、久夫くん。競走しよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8127
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_c54a1fcb:

    # "With a sudden smile, she darts off."
    "笑美はいきなり笑って、駆け出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8129
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_208ff265:

    # hi "Hey! No fair!"
    hi "っておい！　ずるいぞ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8131
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_6308e785:

    # "I take off after her, knowing I won't catch her but not caring."
    "俺は笑美を追って駆け出す。捕まらないだろうけど知ったことか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8133
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_8482ac2f:

    # "Even if there's no chance of catching her, I'll still run after her."
    "勝算なんかなくても、笑美を追いかけて走る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8141
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b3dffac6:

    # "Emi's waiting for me at the door as I arrive."
    "俺が到着すると笑美がドアのところで待っている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8146
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d258c77e:

    # emi "Well well, look who's finally shown up!"
    emi "あれあれ、ビリはだーれだ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8148
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a22c5637:

    # hi "Yeah, yeah."
    hi "はい、はい"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8150
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_9d575024:

    # hi "Enjoy your victory while you can."
    hi "今のうちに勝ち誇ってればいいさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8155
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d980a954:

    # "Emi grins as the nurse pokes his head out of the door."
    "笑美がにやにやしているとドアからナースが頭を出す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8165
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_6fdaaec6:

    # nk "Well, there you are."
    nk "ああ、そこにいたのか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8167
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_15a6b644:

    # nk "Come on in, Hisao."
    nk "入ってくれ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8175
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_f536660a:

    # "In what has become a familiar routine by now, he checks my blood pressure and my heart rate."
    "俺にもすっかり習慣になった手順で、ナースが血圧と心拍数を計る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8180
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_36dc2ca4:

    # nk "A bit fast today, isn't it?"
    nk "今日はちょっと速いんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8182
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_3f888388:

    # hi "Yeah, I kind of raced Emi here."
    hi "ええまあ、ちょっとここまで笑美と競走したっていうか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8187
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_1a26db20:

    # "The nurse laughs."
    "ナースは笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8189
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_2ae6a59f:

    # nk "That's never a good idea!"
    nk "それはよくないな！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8194
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_3f35ef74:

    # "He leans in to whisper to me in a conspiratory manner."
    "ナースは俺のほうにかがんで内緒話をするようにささやく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8199
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_e05c2104:

    # nk "I don't know if you've heard… but Emi's a bit of a track star."
    nk "もう聞いてるかどうか……でも笑美ちゃんは陸上ではちょっとしたスターなんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8204
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_ca9e7dff:

    # "I reel back in mock surprise."
    "俺は驚いたふりをしてのけぞる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8206
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_934c4941:

    # hi "Really? She never mentioned it before!"
    hi "そうなんですか？　そんなこと一言も言ってなかったですよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8211
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_075c1eec:

    # "The two of us share a laugh."
    "二人で笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8216
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_e8791c08:

    # nk "Did she do okay today?"
    nk "今日の笑美ちゃんは大丈夫だったかい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8218
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_5b90672e:

    # nk "Cold seemed to bother her?"
    nk "風邪の影響はなかったかな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8220
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_3196a269:

    # hi "Why don't you ask her?"
    hi "どうして自分で聞かないんですか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8225
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_f3efb64d:

    # "He rolls his eyes in exasperation."
    "ナースはあきれたように空を仰ぐ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8227
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_e93df9df:

    # nk "Of course I'm going to ask her too, but she'll tell me that she didn't have any problems, regardless of whether or not she did."
    nk "そりゃもちろん笑美ちゃんにも聞くよ。でも全然問題ないって答えるさ、問題があってもなくてもね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8232
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_ac02ab17:

    # nk "So I'm asking you, because you're her friend and would probably tell me if she had trouble today."
    nk "それで君に聞いてるんだ。君は笑美ちゃんの友達だし、笑美ちゃんに何かあったら僕に話してくれるだろうからさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8234
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_994d96b3:

    # "When he puts it that way, it makes a lot more sense."
    "ナースがそう言うと、すごく納得できる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8236
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_db558086:

    # hi "She seemed pretty good today, if a little more tired than usual."
    hi "今日はずいぶん調子よさそうでしたよ、普段よりちょっと疲れてたかもですけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8238
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_5335c353:

    # hi "She was already feeling better when I dropped by yesterday, so I'm not that surprised."
    hi "昨日行ってみた時はもう大丈夫だったから、驚きはしないですけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8243
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_df15a765:

    # "The nurse nods, though I notice he tenses slightly when I mention yesterday's visit."
    "ナースはうなずくけど、俺が昨日お見舞いに行ったことを話す時ちょっと緊張するのに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8245
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_3fcd7ee8:

    # nk "Well, that's good to hear."
    nk "まあ、それならよかった"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8247
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_1581f3ce:

    # nk "I figured it was just a 24-hour thing. Emi tends to recover quickly from colds and the like."
    nk "あれは一日あれば治る程度のものだとみていたんだ。笑美ちゃんは風邪みたいなことの治りはいい方だし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8249
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_bbd2932d:

    # hi "Hey, speaking of Emi…"
    hi "そういえば、笑美の話なんですけど……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8251
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_26326fe3:

    # hi "Are she and the track captain…? Well, you know."
    hi "笑美と陸上部の部長って……？　その、ほら"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8256
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_29519868:

    # "A look of suspicion crosses his face."
    "疑惑の表情が顔を横切る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8258
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a79a8ca8:

    # nk "Why do you ask?"
    nk "どうしてそんなこと聞くんだい？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8260
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_da01a3dd:

    # hi "Well, it's just that they seem kind of close, and I was just curious, you know?"
    hi "その、仲よさそうに見えるし、ただの好奇心なんですけどね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8262
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_13c9d9c9:

    # hi "And I'd never ask her, because that would be kind of embarrassing."
    hi "それに俺から本人には聞けないですよ、なんか恥ずかしくて"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8264
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_ca29d7af:

    # "So far, so good. Now to really sell it."
    "ここまでは、大丈夫だ。もう一押ししよう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8266
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_f980b75e:

    # hi "Besides, I think they'd make a cute couple."
    hi "それに、二人だったらお似合いだと思いますし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8271
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_1a26db20_1:

    # "The nurse laughs."
    "ナースは笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8273
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_32d5ab5c:

    # nk "Well, I don't suppose you're the first to think that."
    nk "まあ、そう思うのは君が初めてじゃないだろうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8275
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_eca39a2f:

    # nk "But I think I can say with some certainty that the two of them will never do anything like that."
    nk "でも、わりと確信を持って言えるけど、二人は絶対そんなことにはならないと思うよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8277
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b870d7e4:

    # hi "Certainty?"
    hi "確信？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8282
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_cdd7cf29:

    # nk "Yep."
    nk "ああ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8287
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_e5c18736:

    # nk "Not that I could tell you, of course. Confidentiality and all that."
    nk "もちろん、僕が言えることじゃないけどね。守秘義務やら何やらでさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8289
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_acf16eb4:

    # hi "Yeah right, you just like holding a secret over my head."
    hi "よく言いますよ、俺に隠しごとするのが好きなだけでしょ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8294
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d693f796:

    # nk "That too."
    nk "それもあるかな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8299
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_52c9136e:

    # nk "Right. Get out of here. I'm a busy man, you know."
    nk "よし。もう行っていいよ。なんたって、僕は忙しい男だからね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8307
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_492d4fed:

    # "I roll my eyes at his last statement and head out the door, motioning to Emi to go in."
    "最後の台詞にあきれながらドアを出て、部屋に入るよう笑美に合図する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8317
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_37df3339:

    # "The whole time, I'm trying to keep from doing a celebratory dance."
    "その間、踊りだしそうになるのをこらえるので必死だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8321
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_a7994c62:

    # centered "The two of them will never do anything like that."
    centered "二人は絶対そんなことにはならないよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8323
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_d9ef2e95:

    # "That's precisely the sort of thing I wanted to hear."
    "それこそが俺が聞きたかったことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8325
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_99d006a1:

    # "I'm half-tempted to make some sort of a move on Emi right now, but I think the nurse would probably disapprove."
    "今すぐに笑美に何らかのアプローチをかけようと思ったけど、多分ナースは反対するだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8327
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_62ad3107:

    # "Besides, I still don't know exactly how Emi feels about me."
    "それに、まだ笑美が俺のことをどう思っているかがよくわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8329
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_15dd6b0e:

    # "I mean it's obvious that she cares about me as a friend, but something more than that? I can't be certain."
    "友達として大事にしてくれてるのは当たり前だけど、それ以上はどうだ？　確かなことは言えない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8331
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_b3408729:

    # "Even so, I can't help but feel hopeful. I just need to figure out a good time to tell Emi exactly how I feel."
    "それでも、期待できると思わずにはいられない。あとは俺がどう思っているかを笑美に伝えるいいタイミングを見つけるだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8333
translate jp a2_emi_the_first_morning_after_e2685367:

    # "That puzzle should keep me occupied for the rest of the day, at least."
    "少なくとも、このパズルは一日中頭から離れないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8349
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_6e340a55:

    # "The rooftop is completely deserted."
    "屋上は完全に無人状態だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8351
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_f13dba25:

    # "Normally I could count on Rin to be up here before me, but she's strangely absent."
    "普通なら俺より先に琳が上がってきていると思っていたけど、妙なことにいなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8353
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_8288ee4f:

    # "I wonder if she decided to accompany Emi to the cafeteria for once. That seems pretty unlikely, but it's all I can think of right now."
    "今回だけは笑美と一緒に食堂に行くことにしたんだろうか。そんなことはなさそうだけど、今はそれぐらいしか思いつかない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8355
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_0321709c:

    # "Part of me wants to go look for Rin, but a far larger part of me is too pleased with the way the sun feels on my skin to care."
    "琳を探しに行きたいと思うけど、この日だまりの感触を味わっていたいという思いのほうが大きかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8357
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_9a806d57:

    # "I pick idly at my lunch while I wait for Emi and Rin to show up."
    "俺は笑美と琳が来るのを待ちながらぼんやりと昼飯を食べる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8359
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_baa07966:

    # "It does not take long for me to hear the sounds of someone coming up the stairs."
    "誰かが階段を上がってくる音が聞こえるまでそんなに時間はかからなかった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8364
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e0c4a103:

    # "I wait until the door begins to open before talking."
    "俺は扉が開き始めると口を開く。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8366
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_aebe48ce:

    # hi "Took you long enough."
    hi "ずいぶん時間かかったな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8368
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a140c53a:

    # hi "Keeping me waiting for you, honestly."
    hi "待たせておいて、まったく"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8370
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_495af350:

    # hi "The two of you are…"
    hi "二人とも……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8372
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8374
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_152ecc61:

    # "Well that's odd."
    "おかしいぞ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8379
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_6cf48b0c:

    # "The only person standing in the doorway is Emi, who looks mildly confused."
    "そこに立っているのは笑美だけで、少しとまどっているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8381
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_d2f3f913:

    # emi "What do you mean, 'huh?'"
    emi "『え？』ってなによ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8386
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_dde4ed1b:

    # emi "It's me! You know, Emi! We run in the mornings."
    emi "あたしよ！　ほら、笑美だよ！　今朝一緒に走ったよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8388
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_081904b4:

    # "She grins, and I feel my heart jump slightly in my chest at the sight."
    "笑美が笑う。それを見て俺は心臓が少し跳ねるのを胸に感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8390
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_594d3d53:

    # hi "Yes, I knew that. I'm just confused…"
    hi "ああ、それは知ってたけど。その、ちょっと混乱してて……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8392
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_17e7e47d:

    # hi "…Where's Rin?"
    hi "……琳はどこだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8397
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_db0d141e:

    # "Emi's grin is replaced by a rather guilty-looking expression."
    "笑美の笑顔は悪いことをしてしまったような表情に変わる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8399
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_45f3b15b:

    # emi "Yeah, about that…"
    emi "ああ、そのことなんだけど……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8401
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_98cb7fac:

    # emi "I kind of… sort of…"
    emi "その……なんていうか……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8406
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_5b028538:

    # emi "Gavehermycold."
    emi "風邪うつしちゃったみたい"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8411
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_69dad350:

    # hi "Oh dear."
    hi "ありゃ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8413
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_4ac4806e:

    # hi "Am I at risk too?"
    hi "俺も危ないかな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8415
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_687436d6:

    # "It would make sense, after all. Emi and I were in close contact the other day…"
    "ありそうなことだ。笑美と俺は先日ぴったりくっついていたし……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8417
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ab6ea233:

    # "So what did she and Rin do that got her ill?"
    "じゃあ笑美と琳が何をしたせいで琳が風邪になったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8419
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8421
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e01c9f1c:

    # "Steady on, old lad. Don't go down that road."
    "とりあえず、落ち着け。それ以上はいけない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8423
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_2c495eb8:

    # "Rin's just probably got a worse immune system than me."
    "たぶん琳は俺より免疫力が弱かったんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8428
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_0f68be6f:

    # "Emi seems shocked by my comment, like she hadn't considered that before."
    "笑美は俺の発言にショックを受けたようだ。まるでそんなこと考えもしなかったみたいに。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8430
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_d927d398:

    # emi "I hope not!"
    emi "そんな！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8435
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_9223fbb0:

    # emi "I'll feel terrible if you get ill because of me, Hisao!"
    emi "もしあたしのせいで久夫くんが風邪ひいちゃったらいやだよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8437
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_34037d29:

    # hi "Oh man, I think I feel a fever coming on…"
    hi "ああ、なんだか風邪で気分が悪く……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8442
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_7842db96:

    # "Emi looks horrified, and then quickly shifts into a more angry expression."
    "笑美はぞっとしたみたいだけど、すぐに怒った顔に変わる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8444
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_625a31b5:

    # emi "Hisao!"
    emi "久夫くん！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8446
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_20e58e1d:

    # emi "You stop getting sick this instant!"
    emi "今すぐ風邪になるのをやめて！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8451
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a3cf10e3:

    # emi "I won't have it!"
    emi "そんなの認めない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8456
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_0678d4b7:

    # "Impulsively she seizes me by the collar."
    "笑美は衝動的に俺の襟をつかむ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8458
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_613565fb:

    # emi "Are you listening to me, Hisao's immune system?"
    emi "聞いてる、久夫くんの抗体たち？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8463
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_d6bd6732:

    # emi "Get your ass in gear!"
    emi "さっさと働きなさい！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8465
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_313d9758:

    # "I give a smart salute."
    "俺はパッと敬礼する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8467
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_988af9d3:

    # hi "Duly noted, ma'am."
    hi "了解です、隊長"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8472
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_d9b7b111:

    # "Emi steps back and nods, satisfied."
    "笑美は後ろに下がって、満足げにうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8477
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_481d5cf5:

    # emi "Good."
    emi "よし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8482
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_b02e5b6b:

    # emi "You are not allowed to miss any of our morning runs, after all."
    emi "もうこれ以上朝のランニングさぼるの禁止だから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8484
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3c858fde:

    # hi "But you missed a morning run!"
    hi "でも笑美は一回さぼったじゃないか！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8489
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_52214dcd:

    # "Emi crosses her arms and looks at me haughtily."
    "笑美は腕組みをして横柄に俺をにらむ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8491
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_13e22dbc:

    # emi "Yes, but that's a special case. It was me, and not you."
    emi "そうだよ、でもそれは特例。あたしだったから、久夫くんじゃなくて"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8493
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e9014558:

    # hi "That's not an explanation at all."
    hi "それ全然説明になってないぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8498
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_40e49f4e:

    # "Emi looks flabbergasted."
    "笑美はぽかんとしている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8500
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_445e5b0b:

    # emi "You're kidding, right?"
    emi "冗談、だよね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8505
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e3b26804:

    # emi "That explanation makes perfect sense!"
    emi "その説明で完璧にわかるじゃない！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8507
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ce4883ee:

    # hi "No it doesn't! It's a blatant double standard!"
    hi "全然だろ！　あからさまなダブルスタンダードだ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8512
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_51cc3965:

    # emi "I don't see what that has to do with anything."
    emi "それがなんの関係があるのか全然わかんない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8514
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_b7e9e3ae:

    # hi "Oh, fine."
    hi "ああ、もういいよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8519
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_dfde6cfd:

    # "Emi seems pleased by her victory."
    "笑美は自分の勝利に満足げだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8521
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_61e3ab34:

    # hi "Anyway, is Rin going to be okay? She's not terribly ill, right?"
    hi "どっちにしろ、琳は大丈夫なのか？　そんなにひどい風邪じゃないんだろ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8526
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_4a72a162:

    # "Emi shakes her head."
    "笑美は首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8528
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_aaa41775:

    # emi "Nope! She'll be fine."
    emi "うん！　大丈夫そう"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8533
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_57cde403:

    # emi "I got her some cold medicine that should help her."
    emi "よく効く風邪薬あげたから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8538
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c37b266f:

    # emi "Although I probably should have made sure she didn't try to take them all at once…"
    emi "でもいっぺんに全部飲まないように確認しておけばよかったかも……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8543
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a071b32c:

    # emi "She's done it before, you know."
    emi "その、前にやったことあるから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8545
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ac073ff6:

    # "Somehow, I don't find this all that surprising."
    "なぜか、それを聞いてもそれほど驚かない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8547
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_24e238ce:

    # "I doubt Rin is one to pay attention to maximum dosages and such."
    "琳が薬の用量用法みたいなことを気にするかどうか怪しいもんだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8549
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_7052ca65:

    # hi "You should probably check in on her later, then. Just to make sure."
    hi "だったら、あとで確認したほうがいいと思うぞ。念のために"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8554
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_18357699:

    # "Emi shrugs."
    "笑美は肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8556
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_b12e3623:

    # emi "I'll stop by after practice. She'll be fine until then."
    emi "練習が終わったら寄ってみるね。それまでは大丈夫でしょ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8558
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e0c633f9:

    # "I nod, figuring that line of conversation is over."
    "この話題が終わったことを察して、俺はうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8560
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e9a5408a:

    # "The only problem is, I don't know what else to talk about."
    "問題は、他に何を話せばいいかわからないことだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8562
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c85221a4:

    # hi "So…"
    hi "それで……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8564
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_5571e34b:

    # hi "You got any more track meets coming up?"
    hi "この先も陸上の試合とかってあるのか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8566
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8570
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c30402f9:

    # n "{vspace=240}This is a terribly roundabout way of trying to see if she's free on the weekend."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n週末の予定が空いているか確認するにしては、ひどく遠回りな方法だ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8572
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_1c09e001:

    # n "If she's free, then maybe I can ask her on a date or something."
    n "もし暇なら、デートに誘えるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8574
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_118492ef:

    # n "Well, assuming I can get myself to actually form the words."
    n "まあ、うまい具合に言葉を探せればの話だけど。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8576
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8583
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_4a72a162_1:

    # "Emi shakes her head."
    "笑美は首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8588
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_bca31bf0:

    # emi "Nah, not for another couple weeks, I think. The season's winding down."
    emi "んーん、あと何週間かはないと思うよ。そろそろ落ち着いてくる時期だし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8590
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a13fdbb3:

    # "Oh yeah. I came in right in the middle of things, didn't I?"
    "そうか。俺は学期のど真ん中にやってきたんだったよな？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8592
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_fff3d03f:

    # "Does that mean exams are coming up soon? I should probably look into that."
    "ということはもうすぐ試験なんだろうか？　それも頭に入れておこう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8594
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_cbfa9324:

    # hi "What do you do on weekends if there's not a meet?"
    hi "試合がない週末は何してるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8599
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_835bf36c:

    # "An eyebrow goes up, and Emi gets a teasing look on her face."
    "笑美の眉が上がって、からかうような表情になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8601
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a0a2897f:

    # emi "You're awfully inquisitive today, aren't you?"
    emi "久夫くん、今日はやけに知りたがりだね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8603
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_5f2fc6dd:

    # "I shrug and hope it looks casual."
    "俺は冷静に見えるように願いながら肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8605
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_65f35b77:

    # hi "Just making conversation."
    hi "会話をしようとしてるだけさ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8607
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_720225d8:

    # hi "I don't know what it's like to be a track star, after all."
    hi "やっぱり、陸上のスターでいるのってどんな感じかわからないし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8612
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3e53c3a2:

    # emi "Pfft, flattery."
    emi "ふふ、お世辞ね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8614
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_383667f0:

    # "She waves a hand idly."
    "笑美は手をぶらぶらと振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8619
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_6ac4e003:

    # emi "I'm not actually that good, you know."
    emi "ほんとはそんなすごくないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8624
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_f87f5aa8:

    # emi "You just so happened to see me on a good day, is all."
    emi "久夫くんはたまたま調子のいいときに見に来ただけだもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8626
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_421081cc:

    # hi "You liar."
    hi "うそつけ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8633
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_93580cbd:

    # emi "Heh, yeah."
    emi "あはは、そうね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8635
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_34bc13f2:

    # emi "But humility is the sign of a good athlete."
    emi "でも謙虚なのはいいアスリートの条件だよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8640
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_505348ef:

    # emi "At least that's what my dad used to say."
    emi "少なくとも、パパはよくそう言ってた"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8642
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_64306ac3:

    # "She shrugs and tries unsuccessfully to hide the rather troubled expression her face has taken on."
    "笑美は肩をすくめる。顔に浮かんだ暗い気持ちを隠そうとするけど、うまくいっていない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8644
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3c29bccb:

    # hi "Hey, what's up? You seem bothered by something."
    hi "なあ、どうしたんだ？　なにか悩みでもあるみたいに見えるぞ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8646
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e4ffef01:

    # "Emi starts to deny it, then sighs in defeat."
    "笑美は否定し始めるけど、くじけたようにため息をつく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8648
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_689edcd1:

    # "I wonder if she's too tired from being sick to get herself to deny it like usual."
    "病み上がりで疲れていて、いつものように否定する元気がないんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8650
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_6c2cbdc0:

    # "Or if she actually just trusts me enough at this point to open up."
    "それとも、大事なことを打ち明けられるくらい本当に信頼してくれているんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8657
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_224f6158:

    # emi "Well, you remember last night?"
    emi "あのね、昨日の夜のこと覚えてる？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8659
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_7eca3316:

    # "Do I ever. I settle for nodding, however."
    "もちろんだ。でも、とりあえずうなずくだけにしておく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8664
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3de01983:

    # emi "That's not the first time that's happened to me."
    emi "あたしがああなったのは初めてじゃないんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8666
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_bb0aa483:

    # emi "Actually, I get them kind of…"
    emi "っていうより、あれは……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8668
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_970a5952:

    # "She pauses, as if it's suddenly occurred to her what she's doing."
    "笑美は言葉を切る。自分がいま何をしているか突然気づいたように。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8670
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_f8b2a211:

    # "It's almost like she's breaking some sort of personal rule, here."
    "まるで、自分で作ったルールを破っているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8672
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_fdcf526c:

    # "But she starts up again, choosing her words carefully."
    "でもまた、慎重に言葉を選んで話し始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8674
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_392dbd4a:

    # emi "Well, not often, but…"
    emi "まあ、よくあるわけじゃないんだけど、でも……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8679
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_918c16a5:

    # emi "On occasion."
    emi "ときどきね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8681
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_f0048e4e:

    # emi "It's just been one of those weeks where that's what happens."
    emi "それがたまたま起きたときだったの"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8686
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_17a4af8c:

    # "A sigh escapes her, and she looks terribly frustrated."
    "笑美からため息が漏れる。まるでひどく打ち負かされたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8691
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_60cdedc7:

    # "I reach over and give her a hug, which unlike last time doesn't seem to shock her."
    "俺は笑美に近づいて抱きしめる。前の時とは違って、笑美はそれほど驚いていないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8693
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ce0cc822:

    # "Instead, she seems to relax as my arms wrap around her."
    "というより、俺の腕の中で安心しているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8695
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_2d909687:

    # "We stay that way for a while."
    "俺たちはしばらくそのままでいる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8697
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a8a74faf:

    # hi "Hey, you know I was serious last night."
    hi "なあ、昨日言ったことは本気なんだ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8699
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a59dcbb0:

    # hi "You really can talk to me if stuff like this is bothering you. It's always difficult to do this sort of thing solo, you know?"
    hi "もし何か悩みがあるなら話してくれていいんだ。そういうのは一人でどうこうするのは大変だしな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8704
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_42f3d54b:

    # "Emi smiles and breaks the embrace, but stays leaning on my shoulder."
    "笑美は笑って、抱いた腕をほどく。でも俺の肩に寄りかかったままだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8706
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_eca1f13a:

    # emi "Thanks, Hisao."
    emi "ありがと、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8711
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_6d58e409:

    # emi "I'll be fine, I think."
    emi "大丈夫だよ、たぶん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8713
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_7b15c247:

    # "I can already see her reassembling herself, getting ready to bottle it all up again."
    "笑美が早くも自分を立て直して、また全てを封じ込めようとしているのがわかる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8715
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a332e480:

    # "Guess that topic's closed, now."
    "この話は終わったみたいだな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8717
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_0f92ac4c:

    # hi "So hey, given any more thought to that career survey?"
    hi "ところでさ、進路調査のこと何か考えたか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8722
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_4b13de8d:

    # emi "Can't say I have."
    emi "そうとは言えないかな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8727
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_bc1ff5a6:

    # emi "I don't tend to plan very far ahead, you know."
    emi "あたし、あまり先のことまで計画したりしないから"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8729
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e7189cb1:

    # emi "Although I suppose I could at least start looking into college, huh?"
    emi "でもそろそろ大学のことを調べるくらいはしてみてもいいのかもね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8731
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_8619f2c6:

    # "I shrug."
    "俺は肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8733
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_2e7845e3:

    # hi "I suppose, unless you were serious about that pirate thing."
    hi "かもな、例の海賊のこと本気じゃなければだけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8735
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_69f40f36:

    # hi "Last I checked, pirates didn't have much need for universities."
    hi "前に確認したら、海賊は大卒でなくてもよさそうだし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8737
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_b93d8c8c:

    # hi "Unless there's like, a pirate university out there somewhere."
    hi "世間のどっかに海賊の大学みたいなのがあったら、話は別だけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8742
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3673e1bc:

    # "Emi giggles and starts to look a little like her old self, but there's a new element to her expression."
    "笑美はくすくす笑いながら元の自分に戻っていく。でもその表情には新しい要素が加わっている。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8744
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3496f456:

    # "Impish. That's how I'd describe it."
    "いたずらっぽさ、だな。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8746
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3002ae83:

    # "Emi looks impish, looking up at me with her head nestled into my shoulder."
    "笑美は、いたずらっぽく、俺の肩に頭をあずけたままこっちを見上げる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8751
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a0577eed:

    # emi "Would you come with me if I ran off to be a pirate?"
    emi "もしあたしが海賊になったら一緒に来てくれる？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8753
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_07cd2414:

    # hi "Of course I would!"
    hi "もちろん行くよ！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8755
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_455005ae:

    # hi "Who in their right mind would pass up the opportunity to be pirates with you?"
    hi "正気の人間で笑美と一緒に海賊になれるチャンスを逃すやつなんかいないだろ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8760
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_13e5ae4a:

    # emi "Well, when you put it that way, I'm not sure."
    emi "まあ、そんなふうに言われると、どうだかわからないけど"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8765
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_5b24fe21:

    # "She giggles again."
    "また笑美は笑う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8767
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_7bdfbbe9:

    # "I notice that my heart seems to have sped up. It's probably due to Emi's proximity to me."
    "自分の心臓が速くなった様子に気がつく。たぶん笑美が近づいてきたのが原因だろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8769
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_cf6745b2:

    # "That hint of strawberries, again."
    "また、あの微かなイチゴの香り。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8771
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_d341cbff:

    # "I can't help but grin as I gaze down at her."
    "笑美を見下ろす。どうしても笑顔になってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8773
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e1bc3de8:

    # "She's happy again."
    "笑美はまた元気になったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8778
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_963cdfac:

    # emi "Hey, Hisao."
    emi "ねえ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8780
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "え？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8785
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ad59654f:

    # emi "If you're going to kiss me, you should probably do it soon. I think the lunch bell is about to ring."
    emi "もしキスするつもりなら、早くしたほうがいいよ。もう昼休みのベル鳴るだろうし"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8789
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_97e5273b:

    # "My thoughts grind to a sudden halt."
    "俺の思考が緊急停止する。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8791
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_9a6f8888:

    # "I'm pretty sure my mouth is hanging open in shock."
    "口は確実にショックで開いたままなんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8793
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_249eac34:

    # "All I can manage is a strangled 'Huh?'"
    "かろうじてできたのは、息が詰まったような『は？』という声を出すことだけだった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8798
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_9238e6fc:

    # "This amuses Emi even more."
    "それで笑美はもっと面白がる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8803
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_e5fa778c:

    # emi "You were thinking about it, weren't you?"
    emi "そう思ってたんでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8805
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_55c427db:

    # "She sits up, bringing her face level with mine."
    "笑美は座りなおして、俺と同じ高さまで顔を上げてくる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8810
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ddb4ebba:

    # emi "I'd probably enjoy it, you know?"
    emi "あたしもきっとうれしいし。ね？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8815
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_4e42e3f8:

    # emi "You're a really…"
    emi "久夫くん、本当に……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8820
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_418e89a9:

    # emi "…Well."
    emi "……その"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8822
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_054a530f:

    # "She briefly composes herself, looking like she's about to say something important."
    "笑美は、なにか大切なことを言いかけているみたいに、少しの間自分を落ちつかせる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8827
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_98512793:

    # emi "If you hadn't figured it out by now, I think I've developed a bit of a crush on you."
    emi "もし気がついてないとしたらだけど、あたし、久夫くんのこと本気で好きになっちゃったみたい"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8832
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_6bb86586:

    # emi "You're going to have to do something about that."
    emi "どうにかしてくれるんだよね"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8834
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_0cfa493e:

    # "This time her grin short circuits several important thought processes."
    "その笑顔で今度は大事な思考プロセスのいくつかがショートする。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8836
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ec9f2809:

    # "At some point I turned toward her, and at another point her arms moved to around my neck."
    "いつの間にか俺は笑美のほうを向いていて、いつの間にか笑美の腕は俺の首に回っていた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8838
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c8ff836c:

    # "At yet another, my arms wrapped around her waist."
    "そして、俺の腕が笑美の腰を包んでいた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8840
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c5adc0aa:

    # "I'll be damned if I could tell precisely when that happened."
    "いつのまにそうなっていたのか、自分でもわからない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8842
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_9e2dd8e7:

    # "Because at the moment, there's only a voice in the back of my head yelling at me to kiss her."
    "その瞬間、頭の中はキスをしろという声でいっぱいだったからだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8844
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_5d0ea276:

    # "I look into Emi's eyes."
    "俺は笑美の目を見つめる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8846
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_993bef03:

    # "There it is."
    "あの感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8848
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_98562970:

    # "The thing I saw yesterday on the bed. It's there again."
    "昨日ベッドで見たのと同じ。またあの感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8850
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_984cb1f2:

    # "It suddenly strikes me that she's worried that I'll reject her."
    "それで突然、笑美は俺が拒絶するのを怖がっていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8854
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_47dac5af:

    # "What a silly worry for her to have."
    "なんておかしな心配だろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8869
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8872
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_046f7ee3:

    # n "{vspace=120}Her lips taste faintly of strawberries."
    n "\n\n\n\n笑美の唇は微かにイチゴの味がした。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8874
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_213544e2:

    # n "She leans into the kiss, and her arms tighten around the back of my head, making sure that I don't pull away."
    n "笑美はキスで俺に寄りかかって、腕を俺の頭の後ろにきつく回している。俺が身体を引き剥がさないように。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8876
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_4e41d44e:

    # n "Not that there was any danger of that."
    n "そんなことをするはずがない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8878
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_7451043b:

    # n "There's a churning feeling in my gut."
    n "身体の中がかき回される感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8880
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_a4b33ca9:

    # n "The world falls away."
    n "世界が崩れる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8882
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_969c8008:

    # n "There's just me, and her, and this bench."
    n "ここにあるのは俺と、笑美と、このベンチだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8884
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_8b59709b:

    # n "My arms tighten, drawing her waist closer, entranced by the feel of her."
    n "抱く腕を強めて笑美の腰を引き寄せると、笑美の感触に自分を忘れた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8886
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_fd6b90bf:

    # n "I inhale her scent, my mind trying desperately to memorize everything about how she tastes, how she smells, how she feels."
    n "笑美の香りを吸い込んで、俺の意識は笑美の味も、匂いも、感触も、そのすべてを記憶しようと必死になる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8891
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8902
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_656d65f8:

    # "The ringing of the bell snaps us both back to reality, and we break the kiss."
    "ベルの音が俺たちを現実に引き戻し、俺たちは唇を離した。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8904
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_19e5aa47:

    # "Emi's cheeks are slightly flushed, and she seems to be catching her breath. In her defense, so am I."
    "笑美は頬が少しだけ赤くなって、息を整えているみたいだ。笑美の名誉のために言うと、俺もだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8906
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_53718fa5:

    # "We stand there for a few moments, trying to wrap our heads around what we've just done."
    "今したことを頭の中で整理しようとして、俺たちはしばらくそのままでいた。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8908
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_69e6ad1a:

    # "Emi is the first to break the silence."
    "沈黙を最初に破ったのは笑美だった。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8914
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c91b29de:

    # emi "So…"
    emi "それで……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8919
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_f8a6e88c:

    # emi "…Wanna grab dinner after I'm done with practice?"
    emi "……練習終わったら一緒に晩ご飯食べよっか？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8921
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_f4eea275:

    # hi "What a coincidence."
    hi "偶然だな"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8923
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_40962c5f:

    # hi "I was about to ask you the same thing."
    hi "俺も同じこと聞こうとしてた"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8925
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_58b78ce4:

    # "Well, actually I suppose it was going to be some kind of proper date on the weekend or something. But the thought was there, I think."
    "まあ、実際には週末かそのくらいにちゃんとしたデートっぽいことをするんだろうけど、今夜のことも聞こうと思った、と思う。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8929
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_16c298bf:

    # "Emi gives me a playful shove."
    "笑美はふざけて俺を押す。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8934
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_363354e0:

    # emi "Yeah right."
    emi "嘘つき"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8939
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_43220c8d:

    # emi "You were still in shock from how incredibly awesome I am at kissing."
    emi "まだそっちはあたしのキスがすごかったことに驚いてたじゃない"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8941
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_88c72d98:

    # "We begin to head down the stairs back to our respective classrooms."
    "俺たちはそれぞれの教室に向かうために階段を降り始める。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8949
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_02a54b10:

    # hi "Hey, I didn't see you talking immediately afterwards either."
    hi "おい、そっちだってしばらく喋らなかったじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8954
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_bb9a36c7:

    # emi "That I didn't."
    emi "わざとだもん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8959
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_ac33b63d:

    # emi "See you after practice, Hisao."
    emi "じゃ、練習のあとでね、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8967
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_2b33c9de:

    # "She leans in quickly and gives me a quick kiss in the middle of the hallway, sending me into another brief state of mental freefall."
    "笑美はすっと俺にもたれて廊下の真ん中で素早くキスしてきて、俺はまたしばらく呆然とさせられる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8972
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_03ab9b36:

    # "As I head into my classroom, a giggling Misha greets me."
    "自分の教室に向かうと、ミーシャが笑って出迎える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8977
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_29e08af9:

    # mi "Why Hicchan, you romantic, you~!"
    mi "ひっちゃんたら～、ロマンチックなんだから～、この～！"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8979
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_da258309:

    # mi "Did you confess on the rooftop? Did you~?"
    mi "屋上で告白してたんでしょ？　でしょ～？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8981
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_f818e814:

    # hi "Er, actually I think it was the other way around."
    hi "えと、実はその逆だったっていうか"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8986
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_32a9e29d:

    # "This sends Misha into a fresh fit of laughter."
    "この発言にミーシャはまた笑いの発作を起こす。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8991
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c45572a6:

    # mi "Young love is so unpredictable, isn't it~?"
    mi "若い子の恋愛はほんと何があるかわかんないよね～？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8993
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_c64708e2:

    # "This being Misha, I suppose I should have expected her to tease me over this."
    "ミーシャのことだから、からかわれるのを予想するべきだったかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:8995
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_82ae3054:

    # hi "I guess…"
    hi "かもな……"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9000
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_4a007376:

    # "Before I can really respond, Mutou's entered the room and Misha skips off to her seat, giggling all the while."
    "なにか言い返せる前に武藤先生が教室に入ってきて、ミーシャはずっと笑いながら自分の席に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9002
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_3800286d:

    # "I suspect that I'll get a lot of that sort of conversation now, especially seeing as how Emi kissed me right in the middle of the hall."
    "笑美が廊下のど真ん中でキスしてきたことを考えると、この先こんな感じの会話が増えるんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9004
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_b90f4089:

    # "But somehow, I don't care about that."
    "でもとにかく、そんなことはどうでもいい。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9009
translate jp a2_emi_the_real_beginning_5de3dbed:

    # "For the first time since arriving here, my heart feels light."
    "ここに来てから初めて、心が軽く感じる。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9017
translate jp a2ec1o1_74623df0:

    # hi "Hey, I'll run with you."
    hi "なあ、俺も一緒に走るよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9019
translate jp a2ec1o1_68af942e:

    # hi "I might as well, right?"
    hi "その方がいいだろ？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9024
translate jp a2ec1o1_54271c6d:

    # "Emi shakes her head emphatically."
    "笑美はきっぱりと首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9026
translate jp a2ec1o1_a659f4c0:

    # emi "No you won't, Hisao. Rest is critical for you, remember?"
    emi "だめだよ、久夫くん。休養は大事でしょ、忘れたの？"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9028
translate jp a2ec1o1_468f56f4:

    # emi "I won't allow you to push yourself too hard."
    emi "無理をするのは禁止だよ"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9030
translate jp a2ec1o1_74e43e5b:

    # "I guess she's better at giving advice than taking it."
    "笑美はアドバイスを受けるよりは与える方が得意みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9032
translate jp a2ec1o1_ed8f73af:

    # hi "Whatever you say, Emi."
    hi "笑美がそういうなら"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9034
translate jp a2ec1o1_39e12092:

    # "I think it's probably best not to press the issue."
    "これ以上は踏み込まないほうがよさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9039
translate jp a2ec1o2_f0a64c37:

    # "Come to think of it, she looks like she'd rather be alone right now."
    "そういえば、今の笑美はむしろ一人になりたそうに見える。"

# game/script-a2-emi.rpy:9041
translate jp a2ec1o2_b0a5e746:

    # "I decide to keep my offer to myself."
    "付いていくのは止めることにする。"

translate jp strings:

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5046
    old "Dear Hisao,\n\nHow are you? I hope you are well and happy at your new school. Everyone here misses you. Almost all of our second-year class got put together in class 3-1 for the final year, so we are pretty comfortable right from the beginning of the year. I'm sure you would've been assigned to this class as well."
    new "久夫くん、\n\nお元気ですか？　新しい学校で、元気に楽しくすごしているといいな。みんな寂しがってます。２年のクラスのほとんど全員が３年になって３－１にクラス分けされたので、最初からみんなとても気楽にしています。きっと久夫くんもこのクラスに入ってたんじゃないかな。"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5048
    old "The mood among the third-years seems to be very anxious about the final exams, even though they are so far away. The teachers are badgering us about it all the time - even old Mr. Tachibana who is, by the way, our homeroom teacher this year. Would you believe it? I was sure that he'd retire after our second year, but here he is, nagging everyone about studying for exams.{vspace=30}"
    new "３年生になって、みんな卒業試験のことで頭がいっぱいになっています。まだずっと先の話なのにね。先生たちはいつもその話を持ち出してます――おじいちゃんの橘先生まで。そうそう、橘先生は今年の担任です。信じられる？　私たちが２年生から上がったら絶対に定年退職すると思ってたけど、結局残っていて、みんなに試験のことを口うるさく言ってるんだよ。\n"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5050
    old "I think things like that are the main reason why the mood among the third-years is so nervous. I must admit that I'm somehow losing confidence in myself as well, even though I've always fared reasonably well in exams.{vspace=150}"
    new "そういうことがあるので、３年の雰囲気がすごくピリピリしているんだろうなって思います。正直に言うと、試験でいつもそれなりにいい成績を取ってはいるけど、私もなんだか自分に自信がなくなってきています。\n\n\n\n\n"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5052
    old "It's so weird to think we are already seniors, isn't it? Time has really flown past. I wonder where it went. The new first-years seem so young and somehow really innocent. I keep wondering if I was like them in my first year. I've been feeling nostalgic like this for the whole first trimester.{vspace=90}"
    new "私たちがもう最高学年だっていうのが、とても変な感じだと思わない？　月日は本当にあっという間に過ぎてしまった。どこに行っちゃったんだろう。新しく入ってきた１年生はとっても初々しくて、なんだかすごく純真に見えます。私も１年の時はあんな風だったのかな、なんていつも考えてます。１学期の間ずっと、そんなノスタルジックな気持ちを抱いてました。"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5054
    old "There are other things I want to say. I'm writing to you because I felt that there are things I should've said after the incident back in winter. I really regret that I wasn't able to say them in person, and I have no excuse for it…{vspace=150}"
    new "他にも言いたいことがあります。冬のあの時から、言わなくちゃいけなかったことがあると思って、こうして手紙を書いています。直接伝えることができなかったのを、本当に後悔しています。言い訳のしようもありません……\n\n\n\n\n"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5989
    old "What?"
    new "えっ？"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:5989
    old "Huh?"
    new "なに？"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6156
    old "Still, I feel like I should at least offer to run with her…"
    new "それでも、俺は笑美と一緒に走ると申し出るべきなんじゃないか……"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6156
    old "Offer to run with Emi."
    new "一緒に走ると言う"

    # game/script-a2-emi.rpy:6156
    old "Keep quiet."
    new "黙っておく"

